# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:12
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_bf506199:

    # "I woke up, took my pills, had a nice shower, quickly slipped on my uniform, ate a tasty breakfast, grabbed my bag, and headed off, all as per my usual daily routine."
    "目を覚まし、薬を飲み、シャワーを浴びて、素早く制服に着替え、おいしい朝食を食べたら、鞄をひっつかみ、登校する。すべていつもどおりだった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:14
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_3b1e297c:

    # "It was only after arriving in class that the normality of the day was thrown off."
    "その日常が壊されたのは、教室についた後のことだった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:16
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_4a099d6f:

    # "After taking my seat, I watched my classmates trickle into the room over the next hour, until every empty seat was eventually taken, other than Hanako's."
    "席についた俺は、それから１時間、ぽつりぽつりとクラスメイト達が教室に入ってくるのをながめていた。空っぽだった席が１つ１つ埋め尽くされていくが、華子の姿はなかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:30
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_9d7a9b18:

    # "I can never get used to the idea that she just doesn't show up to class every now and again. It feels all the more worrying now as well, given that Lilly's left."
    "ときどき華子が授業に出てこないことがあるのには慣れることができない。リリーがいないことを考えると、なおさら心配だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:32
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_eb3491dc:

    # "As Mutou continues to drone on, I find my gaze flicking every so often over to her seat, as if she might appear there any moment now. Nobody else seems to care at all about her absence, but they have little reason to."
    "武藤先生が単調な話を続ける間、ときおり華子の席へ視線をさまよわせている自分に気づく。まるでもうすぐ華子が現れるかのように。他の生徒が華子の欠席を気にしている様子はないけど、不思議なことじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:34
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ed0b65aa:

    # "Hanako being absent from class, after all, is perfectly normal. Or at least, it was. Her attendance hasn't been all that bad from what I've seen in my time here, but it was apparently much more spotty beforehand."
    "華子が授業を欠席するのは、結局ごく普通のことなんだから。少なくとも、今まではそうだった。ここにきてから見てる限りでは、華子の出席率はそこまで悪くないけど、その前はもっとまばらだったようだし。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:36
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_97544f20:

    # "This is also an ominous time for her to be gone. It's the day before her birthday, and my suspicions are starting to rise, after the breakdown she had in class when it was mentioned."
    "華子がいなくなることが不吉に思える時期でもある。明日は華子の誕生日だ。誕生日の話題が出たときに華子が教室でおかしくなったあとでは、頭の中に疑惑が芽生え出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:38
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_06a182cc:

    # "An increasing amount of my thoughts is taken up by how I can help her, but in the end, I feel like I can't do anything."
    "どうすれば華子を助けてやれるか、ということがどんどん思考を埋め尽くしていくけど、結局最後には、俺には何も出来ないんじゃないかという気がしてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:44
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_3e5be0d3:

    # "The bell heralding the beginning of lunchtime rings out, shaking me out of my thoughts. A collective sigh of relief can be heard from the class, though Mutou looks quite put off."
    "昼休みの始まりを告げるベルが鳴って、俺は思考から引き戻される。クラスのみんなの安堵の溜息が聞こえてくるけど、武藤先生は面白くないようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:46
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8bfd2e71:

    # "He dislikes being interrupted in the middle of his exciting lectures, after all."
    "なんだかんだで武藤先生は自分の面白い講義を遮られるのが嫌いなんだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:48
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_57c2cd0a:

    # "Just when I'm wondering what I should do on lunch break, given that Hanako and Lilly aren't here, the solution presents itself."
    "華子もリリーもいないことだし、昼休みはどうしたものかと思っていると、その解決策が自らご登場してくれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:63
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_68e457e7:

    # mi "'Afternoon, Hicchan~!"
    mi "こんにちは、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:68
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:70
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e0faf254:

    # hi "'Afternoon Misha, Shizune. You both look as bright as ever."
    hi "よお、ミーシャ、静音。いつもどおり元気だな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:75
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:80
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_790cbbca:

    # mi "Shicchan wants to know if you'd like to have lunch with us today~?"
    mi "しっちゃんがね、よかったら今日一緒にお昼食べないかって～！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:82
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_a4006c05:

    # hi "Sure. It'll be good to have some company."
    hi "もちろんいいさ。誰かと食べるほうがいいしな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:91
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_c9a5d6b1:

    # "The cafeteria hums with activity, much like my old school's did. Yamaku is different, though, in how… strangely civilized the lunchtime rush is."
    "前にいた学校と同じように、食堂は活気づいている。ただし山久には違うところがあって、なんていうか……昼食時の混雑すら奇妙なほど上品だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:93
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1bdb3b4a:

    # "What one would expect to be an unruly mob chomping at the bit to get to the serving area is, rather, a neat and organized line."
    "普通想像されるような、我先にカウンターへ行こうとする手の付けられない暴徒たちはそこにはなく、綺麗に統率された列を作っている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:95
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_50782a23:

    # "There's a small amount of jostling, and people's heads are often craning around to check on what's happening up ahead, but it's pretty subdued."
    "少しくらいは押し合いへし合いもあるし、前の様子を見ようと列から首を出す人もいるけど、とても落ち着いたものだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:97
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_67d7e945:

    # "This is due, no doubt, to the very serious rules regarding such matters in this school. The same strict discipline is observed when students move in the hallways, or come to and from their dormitories and the school gate."
    "間違いなく、そういったことに関するこの学校の厳格な校則のおかげだろう。生徒たちが廊下や寮と校門を行き来するときも、同じように厳しい規律を守っている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:99
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_3c5ec5da:

    # "While the reasons for it may be slightly off-putting, I've come to quite like this sense of order that's enforced in the school."
    "そんな校則がある理由は愉快なものではないけど、この学校のそういう秩序感はかなり好きになってきた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:114
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_d4d4da08:

    # "I didn't really like being told by Shizune and Misha to get their lunches, though. I feel a little used as I take a seat at the table where they're sitting, plunking their food down in front of them."
    "静音とミーシャの分の昼食まで取ってくるように言われたのは気に入らなかったけど。いいように使われた気分で二人のいるテーブルに座ると、俺は二人の目の前にドスンと食事を置く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:116
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ae6b7db7:

    # "Sweet bread and strawberry milk for Misha, a bowl of ramen and juice for Shizune. I heave a sigh of relief as I put it all down, after the significant difficulty I had carrying it all in addition to my own lunch."
    "ミーシャは菓子パンと苺ミルク、静音はラーメンとジュース。それをテーブルの上に置き終えると、俺は安堵の溜息をつく。自分のぶんと合わせて運ぶのはかなり難しかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:121
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_6995e597:

    # mi "Thank you~!"
    mi "ありがと～！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:126
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_926f33bc:

    # "Misha claps her hands together before popping open the wrapper and digging into her bread ravenously. Shizune simply gives an appreciative nod before giving her steaming ramen a stir and blowing on it a little to cool it down."
    "ミーシャは勢い良く手を合わせてから、パンの包みを解いてガツガツとすごい勢いで食べ始める。静音はただ感謝するようにうなずくと、湯気のたつラーメンを一度かき混ぜてフーフーと少し冷ます。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:128
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_b0f7def6:

    # "I open my own lunch, another packet of sweet bread, and take a bite before washing it down with some juice. The bread is very sweet, so much so that I end up forcing myself to stomach it just to get the experience over with."
    "俺も自分の昼食の菓子パンの封を開けると、一口かじってジュースで流しこむ。とても甘いパンだ。甘すぎて、早く片付けるためだけに無理やり我慢して食べる羽目になる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:130
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_7bff6a0f:

    # "Midway through, I decide to take a break from the difficult task and ask what's on my mind."
    "途中で、俺はいったんこの苦行を一休みして、気になっていることを聞くことにする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:132
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_45d76e20:

    # hi "So, I'm guessing you two had a reason to drag me down here? You two seem to always have an ulterior motive, after all."
    hi "なあ、俺をここに連れてきたのには何か理由があるんだよな？　お前ら二人とも、いつだって下心があるみたいだしな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:137
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_94e00372:

    # mi "What are you faying, Hiffan~! We mon't hafe any uffer mofiffe~."
    mi "何言っふぇるのよ、ひっふぁん～！　ふぃふぁごころなんてあるふぁけないでひょ～"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:142
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_78fe05e4:

    # "Her mouth is full of sweet bread as she speaks. It's a pretty unpleasant sight. Shizune looks a little grossed out, before going back to eating her ramen."
    "ミーシャは菓子パンを口に詰めたまま喋っている。とても見苦しい光景だ。静音も少しうんざりとした顔をして再びラーメンにとりかかる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:148
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_43974f9e:

    # "I wait until Misha swallows what she has in her mouth before speaking again."
    "俺はミーシャが口の中のものを飲み下すのを待ってから、話を再開する。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:150
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_2464e669:

    # hi "You're not buttering me up to make me work with you after school?"
    hi "放課後に俺を働かせるために機嫌を取ってるんじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:155
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_a9919b7c:

    # mi "Nope!"
    mi "いいえ！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:157
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_34d540de:

    # hi "Not trying to extract information from me that I might not want to give?"
    hi "俺が言いたくない情報を引き出そうとしてるんじゃ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:162
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8e4a66b0:

    # mi "Nuh-uh!"
    mi "んーん！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:164
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e9bca73d:

    # hi "…Fine. You win. I guess you just wanted to eat lunch with someone as intelligent and handsome as me, then."
    hi "……わかったよ。そっちの勝ちだ。きっと単純に俺みたいに知的でハンサムなやつと昼食を取りたかっただけなんだろうな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:169
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_4af75150:

    # mi "That's it, Hicchan~! You got it~!"
    mi "そうだよ、ひっちゃん～！　そのとおり～！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:171
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_fead0a76:

    # "Shizune looks unimpressed as Misha finishes signing our conversation, and sucks in the last of a long noodle as she signs her own thoughts."
    "ミーシャが俺たちの会話を通訳し終えても静音は動じない様子で、最後の麺をすすると自分の考えを手話で伝える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:176
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:181
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ec0c0a98:

    # mi "Shicchan says you shouldn't be so suspicious of us~. She's just doing her duty as a class representative, after all~."
    mi "しっちゃんがそんなにわたしたちを疑うんじゃないって言ってるよ～。しっちゃんは学級委員としての仕事をしてるだけなんだから～"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:183
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e9d6b45e:

    # hi "How is she… err… are you doing that?"
    hi "静音……じゃない……お前はどうやってその仕事をしてるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:185
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_fdb98709:

    # "As much as I hate to admit it, it looks as if I still have trouble communicating with Shizune."
    "認めたくはないけど、俺はまだ静音と上手くコミュニケーションを取れないようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:187
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_7b25d45f:

    # "It should be a simple matter of keeping eye contact with her and addressing Shizune instead of Misha in my speech, but when somebody else is doing the talking for her, it's a surprisingly difficult task."
    "静音と目を合わせて、ミーシャではなく静音に話しかけるという簡単なことのはずだけど、静音が話すときは別の誰かが肩代わりしているおかげで、それが驚くほど難しくなる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:192
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:197
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e1331296:

    # mi "It's the class representative's job to ensure everybody's doing all right in class, isn't it~?"
    mi "クラスの全員が問題なく過ごせてることを確認するのが学級委員の仕事でしょ～？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:199
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_c5b2ab3f:

    # hi "Not… really…"
    hi "いや……そこまででは……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:201
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_eb37b9fd:

    # hi "Wait, how is making me get your food ensuring that I'll go well in class?"
    hi "待てよ、俺に食事を持ってこさせることが、どうして俺がクラスで上手くやってることの確認につながるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:206
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_77aba546:

    # "Shizune huffs and adjusts her glasses disapprovingly."
    "静音はムッとして、不満そうに眼鏡を直す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:211
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:216
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_202e1d72:

    # mi "So this is the thanks we get for giving you companionship during lunchtime?"
    mi "お昼につきあってあげたお礼がこれなの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:220
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_14119a65:

    # "That's a total dodge of the question. Wait, hang on…"
    "完全に質問をはぐらかしてる。いや、待てよ……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:222
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_9b2ae79c:

    # hi "How did you know that I…?"
    hi "なんで知ってるんだ……？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:227
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:232
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_c8dbc7c8:

    # mi "Lilly's away and Hanako is absent, and since those two are the only people you hang around with…"
    mi "リリーは出かけていて華子は欠席、そしてひっちゃんがいつも一緒に過ごしてるのはこの二人だけ……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:237
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:242
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_af6e2574:

    # mi "You also made it kind of obvious to see~…"
    mi "それに見ててわかりやすかったしね～……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:246
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e3a083ef:

    # "Ouch. I may well have done so, but she didn't need to rub it in. Maybe this is payback for before."
    "いたた。確かにそうだったんだろう。でもそんなに当てつけっぽく言うことはないのに。さっきの仕返しなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:248
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_95c19d47:

    # hi "Right. Well, thanks. I appreciate it, and that isn't sarcasm."
    hi "確かに。その、ありがとう。助かるよ。皮肉じゃなしに"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:254
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_5f5daf43:

    # "The two nod, and we get back to finishing our meals. It feels a little embarrassing to be accompanied just because they noticed I was lonely, but it isn't as if they're strangers either."
    "二人がうなずいて、俺たちは残りの食事にとりかかる。ただ単に俺が一人ぼっちだったのに気づいたから付き合ってくれたというのは少し気恥ずかしいけど、別に見知らぬ仲というわけでもないしな。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:256
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_31818ba9:

    # "It isn't long before I finish the last of my bread and start on the last of my juice, and as I do so, I find my mind wandering back to what I'd been thinking about before the two interrupted my train of thought."
    "すぐにパンを食べ終えて残りのジュースに取り掛かりはじめると、二人に割って入られる前の考え事を再開している自分に気づく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:258
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_68f90db8:

    # "It feels like I'm the only one in the class that so much as acknowledges Hanako not being there. It felt like this the other times she skipped class, but now it's even more acutely annoying."
    "華子がいないということに気づく程度のことすら、クラスメイトの中で俺しかしていないような感じがする。華子が前に授業を休んだ時もそうだったけど、今回はもっとはっきり気に障る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:260
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_4d2bb38a:

    # "Does nobody care if she's happy or not? Have they just written off any possibility of helping to make her better? Even Mutou doesn't try to keep her in class, and I'm still not wholly convinced by his reasoning."
    "華子が幸せじゃなくてもみんなどうでもいいのか？　華子の助けになれる可能性を見限ってしまっているのか？　武藤先生ですら華子を教室に居させようとはしない。その根拠にも俺は完全には納得できていない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:265
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_a27195aa:

    # mi "Hey Hicchan, is your juice past its expiry date?"
    mi "ねえひっちゃん、そのジュース賞味期限切れてたの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:267
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:272
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_0371b32e:

    # mi "You were pulling a weird face, like this~."
    mi "変な顔してたよ、こんな風に～"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:278
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_2d9921e2:

    # "As if it were needed, Misha mimics my own expression. Her exaggeration makes me grimace, though Shizune at least takes some amusement from it."
    "必要なことでもあるまいに、ミーシャはわざわざ俺の表情を真似る。その誇張っぷりに俺は顔をしかめるけど、少なくとも静音は少し面白がっているようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:280
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_42a96eb3:

    # hi "I was just thinking about Hanako."
    hi "華子のことを考えてたんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:285
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_cf3afc71:

    # mi "Oh?"
    mi "あら？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:290
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_79a34086:

    # "Misha's interest is piqued, and so is Shizune's, once my words are interpreted for her."
    "ミーシャは興味を惹かれる。俺の言葉が通訳されると、静音も興味を惹かれたようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:292
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1c4f781d:

    # hi "I'm just worried about her being absent so often. Especially now, though, what with her birthday coming around."
    hi "あんなに頻繁に欠席するのは心配だよ。特に今は、華子の誕生日が近づいてるし"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:298
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_35b82a5f:

    # "The memories of that incident in class are still fresh in their minds. Their faces alone are telling that much."
    "クラスでのあの出来事の記憶は静音とミーシャの脳裏にも未だ新鮮に残っている。それは二人の顔を見るだけでもわかる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:300
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ed7407d4:

    # hi "Do you know anything about Hanako? Anything that might help?"
    hi "華子のことをなにか知らないか？　なにか役に立ちそうなことは？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:306
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_eae58656:

    # "Misha shrugs and looks to Shizune, who mulls on this for a while."
    "ミーシャが肩をすくめて静音のほうに向き直ると、静音はしばらく考えこむ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:311
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_7:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:316
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_28dcc7ec:

    # mi "The only people she's ever talked to for more than a sentence or two are you and Lilly."
    mi "華子がほんの一言、二言以上しゃべったことがある相手って、ひっちゃんとリリーだけだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:318
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8ea4ca37:

    # "Shizune may not be able to convey Lilly's name in a derisive tone of speech, but I feel as if it comes through in her sign language. The effect is lost, however, after Misha's interpretation."
    "静音はリリーの名前を冷笑的な口調で伝えることはできないかもしれないけど、手話からそれが伝わってくるような気がする。とはいえミーシャが通訳した後にはそんな印象はなくなっているのだけど。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:323
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_8:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:328
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_a69ce622:

    # mi "There are a couple of things we know about Hanako as Student Council members, thanks to the records that pass through our hands, but we can't say anything about what's in them."
    mi "生徒会のメンバーとして華子について知ってることはいくつかあるわ。たまたま目を通した書類とかでね。でもそこに書かれてたことについては言うことはできないの"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:330
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_14ebf8ee:

    # hi "Understandable."
    hi "わかるよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:332
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_020c3253:

    # "It sounds a lot like the nurse's 'patient confidentiality.' Every time I find someone that knows something about Hanako's past, it turns up being a dead end."
    "それはナースの言う『医者の守秘義務』みたいに聞こえる。華子の過去について何か知ってる人を見つけてもいつも結局手詰まりになってしまうな。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:334
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_939ba2d1:

    # "The only way I'll ever find out is by asking her. I don't know if she'll let me know such things, but if it's for her sake, I have to at least try."
    "唯一の方法は華子に直接聞くことだろう。そんなことを教えてくれるかどうかはわからないけど、それが華子のためになるなら少なくともやってみるべきだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:339
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ef2b123c_9:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:344
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_fad97deb:

    # mi "Don't worry about it, Hicchan~. It happens every year, after all~."
    mi "心配することないよ、ひっちゃん～。毎年のことなんだから～"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:346
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_961fb7a8:

    # "That doesn't remove my sense of worry at all. I still feel a little at fault for what happened in class, but this feels like it goes further, even without their confirmation of that fact."
    "そう言われても心配な気持ちはまるで楽にならない。教室でのあの出来事に俺はまだ少し責任を感じているけど、これはあれだけで終わる問題ではない気がする。静音とミーシャに確かめるまでもなく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:352
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_78cd45d7:

    # "Misha notes my troubled expression, her own usually happy and reassuring face dropping."
    "ミーシャは俺の悩んでいる表情に気づくと、いつもの陽気で安心させるような笑顔が消える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:354
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8e74903f:

    # mi "Everyone has problems they have to deal with, right, Hicchan?"
    mi "誰だって自分でなんとかしないといけない問題を抱えてるよね、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:356
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1b0ae1fd:

    # hi "Yeah. I just wish I could help Hanako more with hers."
    hi "ああ。俺はただ、華子の問題についてもっと力になれたらいいのにって思ってるだけだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:358
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e31ff9e3:

    # "With that, the conversation trails off on a depressing note."
    "俺がそう言うと、陰鬱な雰囲気のまま会話は途切れる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:365
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_643d9322:

    # "Eventually Misha manages to pick the mood back up through her usual bright and bubbly antics, but my mind remains focused on Hanako."
    "ミーシャのいつもの明るく陽気な振る舞いがやがて元の雰囲気を取り戻すけど、俺の頭はまだ華子のことから離れずにいる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:367
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_7fd15538:

    # "I'll go check on her later."
    "あとで様子を見に行こう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:374
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_fb58a8f5:

    # "I make sure my door is locked after dropping off my school bag."
    "学校の鞄を部屋に下ろしてから、ドアの鍵を閉めたことを確認する。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:376
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_736160b6:

    # "The dorms are quiet. Mutou kept me occupied longer than I expected, discussing my studies after classes ended and pressing on me some worksheets to give to Hanako almost as an afterthought."
    "寮は静かだ。武藤先生との話が思ったよりも時間を取った。授業が終わったあと俺の勉強のことについて議論を交わしてから、ほとんど思い付きのように華子に渡すワークシートを押し付けてきた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:378
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_9b80b94a:

    # "Absorbed in thought, I'm late in registering the shadow that appears in front of me. Looking up reveals the owner of said shadow."
    "思考にとらわれていると、目の前に現れた影に気づくのが遅れる。顔を上げると、その影の主があらわれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:385
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8ff5de62:

    # ke "Hey, man. Haven't seen you in a while."
    ke "よお。久しぶりじゃん"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:387
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_fd088bd6:

    # hi "Oh. Hi."
    hi "おお。よお"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:392
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_2e3b8744:

    # ke "What's with that response?"
    ke "何だよその反応は？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:394
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_4e467a46:

    # "My absentminded greeting visibly annoys him. I'd probably have had the same reaction."
    "俺の上の空な挨拶が気に障ったらしいのは明らかだ。俺でも同じような反応を返したかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:396
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e19367b6:

    # hi "Sorry, just thinking about a lot of stuff."
    hi "悪い、色々考え事をしててね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:398
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_3102cf21:

    # ke "'Thinking' is a pretty poor excuse to not be aiding the war effort."
    ke "『考え事』だなんて戦争費用を援助しない言い訳としちゃあ出来が悪すぎるな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:400
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_3240c1d8:

    # hi "And how goes the war?"
    hi "へえ、戦争の調子はどうなんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:405
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_6ad8c102:

    # ke "I am preparing. Right now I need money to help with those preparations."
    ke "準備中だ。今はその準備のために金がいるんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:407
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_70545cc8:

    # hi "If you want me to loan you money, just say it."
    hi "金を貸して欲しいならそう言えよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:412
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_86768c1b:

    # ke "No man, I'm good."
    ke "いんや、俺は大丈夫だ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:414
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_7186710c:

    # hi "You're… good? You don't want my money?"
    hi "大丈……夫？　俺の金が欲しいわけじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:419
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_5b7576bc:

    # ke "Hey man, don't look so surprised. It's insulting."
    ke "おいおい、驚いた顔すんなよ。失礼だぞ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:424
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_f6ecf254:

    # ke "I'm pretty big in the competitive bowling scene, but yesterday, I found some guys who didn't know that."
    ke "俺は賭けボウリングの世界では大物なんだけどな、昨日それを知らない奴らを発見したんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:426
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_462c411b:

    # hi "I'm fairly sure that betting would be against the school rules…"
    hi "賭け事は校則違反だろ……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:431
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_c8a6fb4c:

    # ke "School rules don't matter; this is a war situation. People these days, they have no appreciation for what war means."
    ke "校則は関係ねえよ。これは戦争なんだ。最近の奴らは戦争って言葉の意味を知らねえよな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:433
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ddcb1615:

    # hi "So what do you need this money for, dare I ask?"
    hi "それでその金が何のために必要か聞いても？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:438
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_4b1c34b9:

    # ke "Non-perishable canned food. Building materials; mostly corrugated iron and wood panels. First aid kit. Camping heater. Portable radio. Sleeping bag. Flashlight. Mechanical clock."
    ke "腐りにくい缶詰食品。建築用材……だいたいが波形鉄板と木のパネル。応急処置用品。ポータブルヒーターにラジオ。寝袋に懐中電灯に機械式時計"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:440
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_40d8f934:

    # "At first it strikes me as a rather random assortment of objects and materials, but after a few seconds, it clicks."
    "最初は適当な物品の詰め合わせに聞こえたけど、数秒後、俺にはピンとくるものがあった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:442
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_3cfe1c11:

    # hi "Isn't that a list of materials for a fallout shelter?"
    hi "それって核シェルターの材料じゃないか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:447
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_69fce8fa:

    # ke "Ah, so you've read a Protect and Survive booklet. It's good to see someone so knowledgeable about how to protect themselves."
    ke "ああ、お前も英国内務省の『Protect and Survive』の小冊子を読んだのか。自分の身を守る知識を持ってるやつに会えてよかったよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:449
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1a76a032:

    # hi "You don't seriously think…"
    hi "お前、まさか本気で……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:454
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_d1766e6f:

    # ke "It's a non-zero possibility."
    ke "可能性はゼロじゃない"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:456
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_d1bd0381:

    # hi "No, I'm pretty sure there's zero possibility of that ever happening."
    hi "いや、そんなことが起こる可能性はゼロだと思うぞ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:461
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_cffc1cd5:

    # "He slowly and dramatically raises an eyebrow. Well, as dramatically as one can raise an eyebrow."
    "健二はゆっくりと、しかし大きく片眉を上げる。まぁ、人間が片眉を上げられる範囲でだけど。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:463
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_16fa9b2c:

    # hi "The chance is, I don't know, zero point one to the trillionth place. It's infinitesimal. Besides, where can you build a fallout shelter anyway? Certainly not on campus."
    hi "知らないけど、そんな可能性なんて一兆分の一とかそんなものだろ。限りなくゼロに近い。それに核シェルターなんてどこに作るんだよ？　学校の敷地なんて無理だろ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:468
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8f992b4d:

    # ke "It's my summer holiday project while I'm at home. My dad said I can do it."
    ke "俺が夏休みに実家に帰省してる間の計画だ。親父がやってもいいって言ったんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:470
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ff728ce7:

    # hi "Really?"
    hi "マジかよ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:472
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_fb3e11c4:

    # ke "Yeah. He thought it'll improve my crafting skills and manual dexterity. Or something."
    ke "ああ。俺の工作技術や手先の器用さが鍛えられるとかそういう風に考えてるんだろ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:474
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_87d2229d:

    # "Knowing Kenji, his dad probably just thought it might keep him out of his hair for a while."
    "父親は健二のことをわかっているから、自由にさせればしばらく厄介事を避けられると考えているだけだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:476
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_f6e02219:

    # "Still, it does make me wonder what his parents are like. Maybe they're totally normal, and Kenji is just an aberration. On the other hand, maybe this kind of paranoia and fearful survivalism runs in the family."
    "しかし、この話のせいで健二の親はどんな人なんだろうと気になる。ごくごく普通の人で、健二だけが異常なのかもしれない。その一方で、こんな偏執症や臆病な生存主義が家系に流れている可能性もある。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:481
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_517375ec:

    # ke "Hey, want to help me build it? You look like the type to be handy with tools. If I had your help, we could make a really badass bunker instead of just a fallout shelter."
    ke "なあ、シェルターを作るのを手伝わないか？　お前は器用に道具を使えそうだし。お前の力があれば、ただの核シェルターなんかじゃなくてすげえ掩体壕だって作れそうだぜ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:483
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_7dcf780c:

    # "I doubt that. Playing soccer before my accident gave me good footwork, but I've never really tried my hand at anything approaching real handiwork."
    "そうは思えない。心臓発作の前はサッカーをやってたから足はいいけど、手を使った細工は何もやったことがない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:485
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e58bf70d:

    # hi "I'm not, really. I'm busy over the holidays anyway, I'm afraid."
    hi "俺は器用じゃないよ、ほんとに。どっちみち休み中は忙しいし、悪いけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:490
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_6d7b2b5b:

    # ke "A shame. If the feminists ever get a hold of the launch codes, I fear that so few will be prepared."
    ke "残念だ。フェミニストどもが発射コードを手に入れちまったら、おそらく備えができている奴なんてほとんどいないぞ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:492
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_5eb16b1f:

    # hi "And your fallout shelter will protect you from a nuclear bomb explosion, in the case that this does happen?"
    hi "もしそうなったら核シェルターがお前を核爆発から守ってくれるのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:494
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_d1f8d883:

    # ke "A fallout shelter isn't meant to protect against the blast. That's what a blast shelter is for."
    ke "核シェルターは爆風に耐えるように出来てねえよ。それは防爆シェルターの役目だ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:496
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e9ab747a:

    # ke "I thought you knew better."
    ke "そのくらい知ってると思ってたぞ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:498
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e067e9f4:

    # hi "My mistake…"
    hi "間違ってたか……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:503
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ab88190b:

    # ke "My home's pretty far away from any major military sites, so the fallout following a nuclear exchange is a bigger concern than the blast itself."
    ke "俺の家はどの軍事拠点からも遠く離れてるからな。爆風そのものよりも核兵器を撃ち合ったあとの放射性降下物のほうが心配なんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:508
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e8208fce:

    # ke "What this'll do is keep the dust and other particulates away from me, my food supply, and my sleeping area. It's gotta last me at least fourteen days, though."
    ke "このシェルターの役目はほこりや微粒子を遠ざけて俺や食料や寝床に近づけさせないことだ。これで最低でも１４日間は持ちこたえられなきゃいけないんだがな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:510
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_5ea603e1:

    # hi "Fourteen days is a pretty long time."
    hi "１４日って結構長期間だぞ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:515
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_650fe5fe:

    # ke "It is. I need one liter of water a day for drinking, two optimally so that I can wash as well. Toiletry is easy enough; just garbage bags and a bin placed outside the shelter area. Food means canned supplies, of course."
    ke "ああ。飲み水は１日に１リットルは必要だ。理想的には体も洗えるように２リットルだな。トイレは簡単だ。ゴミ袋とゴミ箱をシェルターの外に置いとけばいいだけだ。食事はもちろん缶詰だ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:517
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_b4ab008a:

    # hi "Of course. And the radio is for outside communication?"
    hi "そりゃそうだ。ラジオは外からの通信のためか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:519
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_b3255a74:

    # ke "Right, right. So I can pick up government alerts on what's going on outside. I need a mechanical clock rather than an electric one in case the electromagnetic pulse from a nuclear airburst fries it, too."
    ke "そのとおりだ。外がどうなってるか政府の警報が聞けるようにな。電気式時計は空中爆発した核の電磁パルスに焼かれちまうかもしれねえから機械式時計が必要なんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:521
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_9362b1d5:

    # ke "There's all the other stuff I need as well, like extra clothing, matches, and candles. I think I still have time to gather it all, though. Maybe."
    ke "他にもまだ必要なものはあるんだ、替えの服に、マッチとロウソク。全部集める時間はあるとは思うけどな。わからねえ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:523
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_a3d69648:

    # "As much as I hate to say it, I'm a little impressed. He's really researched this and thought it through. Then again, I don't know if I want to live in a post-apocalyptic world with only people like Kenji having survived."
    "こんなことは言いたくないが、少しだけすごいと思ってしまう。健二はよく研究して考え抜いている。とはいえ、健二みたいなやつしか生き残っていない終末後の世界を生きたいかと言われるとわからない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:525
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_26a8029a:

    # hi "It sounds like you really know what you're doing."
    hi "本当にぬかりがないって感じだな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:530
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8fa852c4:

    # ke "Damn right I do."
    ke "あたりめえだろ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:532
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_c14dc3cd:

    # "It must be hard, living in constant fear like this. He hardly ever socializes either, so the fact he went bowling with others is in itself something of a surprise."
    "こんな恐怖に常に怯えながら生きるのは大変だろう。健二は人と関わることもほとんどないし、他の奴とボウリングに行ったっていうのはそれだけで驚くべきことだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:534
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_23ac59db:

    # "This mentality reminds me a little of a certain someone. Thankfully, her fear of others doesn't manifest in such a distinctly eccentric way."
    "健二のそういう気質はちょっとあの子を思い出させる。幸運なことに、彼女の他人への恐怖はこんなにはっきりと風変わりな形で現れることはない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:536
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_02e0bec6:

    # "One thing I know for sure is that I certainly can't tell him exactly why I haven't been hanging around with him much recently."
    "一つだけ確かなことは、俺が最近健二とあまりつるんでいない理由をはっきり説明するわけにはいかないということだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:538
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1a135064:

    # hi "It's late. I have stuff to do. I'll think about making a fallout shelter or something, though."
    hi "もう遅い時間だな。やらなきゃいけないことがあるから。核シェルター作りとかのこともまた考えとくよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:543
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_221a1dbd:

    # ke "Yeah, all right, that's cool. A man has to do what he's gotta do, after all."
    ke "ああ、わかった。そりゃいいことだ。男には絶対やらなきゃならねえことがあるからな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:545
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_6ebdd481:

    # ke "You should hang out with me sometime, by the way. You're a cool dude. Cool dudes should hang out together, right?"
    ke "そうそう、また付き合えよな。お前はすごいやつだ。すごい奴らは一緒にいるもんだろ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:547
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_c64a0f52:

    # "For some reason, that compliment actually feels kinda nice. The situation with Hanako being what it is, though, means that I probably won't be able to fulfill his request. For now, at least."
    "なぜかこの賛辞は気分がいい。華子を取り巻く今の状況を考えると、健二の申し出に応えることはできないだろうけど。少なくとも、今はまだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:549
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_9611ff27:

    # hi "That'd be good. I'll talk to you later about it when I can."
    hi "そりゃいいな。暇があったらまた声かけるよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:554
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_35b0a87d:

    # ke "Cool. Later, dude."
    ke "おう。またな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:561
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_2cfa5c4e:

    # "He retreats to his dormitory room."
    "健二が自分の部屋へ引っ込んでいく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:563
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ac7d6ddf:

    # "I had better go see Hanako."
    "華子に会いに行ったほうがいい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:576
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_027c2e85:

    # "I stand outside of the door to Hanako's room, hoping that she isn't in too much of a state as I nervously clutch the worksheets Mutou asked me to pass on to her."
    "華子の部屋へとつながるドアの外に立つ。大変な状態じゃなければいいなと願いながら、俺は武藤先生から渡してくれと頼まれたワークシートを神経質に握りしめる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:578
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_939ba3f9:

    # "It's one more reason to visit her, and it gives me something to talk about, so I suppose I should be thankful to him for giving me the task."
    "このワークシートのおかげで華子をたずねる理由が１つ増えたし、華子と話す話題も１つ増えた。俺にこの役割を任せてくれた武藤先生には感謝するべきかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:582
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_574b70d8:

    # "With a long breath to steady myself, I rap my knuckles on the door in front of me."
    "大きく息を吸って気分を落ち着かせると、目の前のドアに何度か軽く拳をぶつける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:584
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_246e6e0b:

    # "…Silence. I listen intently for any sound of shuffling coming from inside, but I can't hear a thing."
    "……静寂。内側から足音がしないかと一心に耳を澄ませるけど、何も聞こえはしない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:589
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_31119420:

    # "I knock on the door again, slightly harder."
    "今度は少しだけ強く、ドアをもう一度ノックする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:591
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_13a0c68e:

    # "Still no answer. How strange."
    "それでも返事はない。なんとも妙だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:593
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_afbe116f:

    # "Scratching my head, I make one last attempt at getting her to answer as I knock on the door one final time."
    "俺は頭をぽりぽりとかくと、華子よ返事をしてくれと最後の試みにドアをノックする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:595
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_a170e415:

    # hi "Hanako, it's just me. Mutou said to give you some stuff."
    hi "華子、俺だよ。武藤先生が渡してほしいものがあるって"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:597
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_42b6ec9e:

    # "For a while, the attempt seems just as unsuccessful as the last. Just before I slip the sheets under her door, though, I hear the handle rattling."
    "しばらく、この試みもさっきと同じく不成功に見えた。しかし、ドアの下の隙間からワークシートを滑りこませようとすると、ドアの取っ手のカタカタという音を耳にする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:608
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_2170b749:

    # "As the door opens halfway, I quickly try to see how Hanako's faring. It's a task made somewhat more difficult by her oversized gown hiding so much of her body."
    "ドアが半分開くと、俺はすぐさま華子の具合を確認しようとする。大きすぎるガウンが体の大部分を覆っているせいで、意外と難しい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:610
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_6c2e8a07:

    # "She doesn't look sick, or at least not immediately so. To be honest, I'd have preferred that to her expression right now. She looks terribly tired, and appears to be barely acknowledging my presence."
    "華子は病気のようには見えない。少なくともすぐにわかるようなそれはない。正直なところ、今の華子の表情よりは病気のほうがよかったかもしれない。 華子はひどく疲れているようで、俺がいることもかろうじて認識しているだけに見える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:612
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_90e1f836:

    # hi "Hi, Hanako. Mutou wanted me to give you these since you weren't in class today."
    hi "やあ、華子。今日クラスにいなかったから、武藤先生がこれを渡してくれって"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:614
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_8b408ffd:

    # "I hold out the loose sheets, which she tentatively takes in her hands. The way she moves is devoid of thought. Her posture is slumped, in an unusual manner for someone that's so often tense and wound up."
    "俺がばらばらのワークシートを差し出すと、華子はおずおずとそれを手に取る。華子の動きには思考が感じられない。うなだれた姿勢は、緊張して張り詰めがちな華子らしくない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:619
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_aec92980:

    # "Even her eyes keep looking away from mine, doing their best to avoid eye contact. I move my head a little to try and get a better look, but she just ends up turning away."
    "華子の目すら俺を見ようとしない。アイコンタクトを避ける事に全力を尽くしている。俺は少し頭を動かして華子をよく見ようとするけど、華子はそっぽを向いてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:621
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_c39d25cc:

    # hi "Are you… okay? If you're feeling sick or anything, I could go get a nurse."
    hi "大丈夫か？　具合が悪いんだったら、看護師を呼ぶけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:623
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_7c8db4fa:

    # "It feels almost pitiful to put on such a routine 'get well soon' act. I can't think of anything else I could possibly do for her, though."
    "『お大事に』並に定型的な言葉をかける自分がみじめに感じる。だけど他に華子に何をしてあげられるのかも思いつかない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:628
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e8acb5cd:

    # "She seems to collect herself a little at the notion… but only a little. Her head remains turned away, but her eyes move towards me."
    "華子はその考えに少しだけ落ち着きを取り戻したように見える……でもほんの少しだけだ。顔はそむけられたままで、目だけがこちらを向く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:630
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_9a17cabe:

    # ha "I'm fine."
    ha "大丈夫"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:632
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_04894577:

    # "An awkward silence follows. As it lingers, I notice that the sleeves and the cuffs of her gown bear slightly damp stains. Her cheeks are a bit red, too. Has she been crying?"
    "気まずい沈黙が流れる。その中で、俺は華子の着ているガウンの袖が少し濡れていることに気づく。頬も少し赤くなっている。泣いていたのだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:634
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "そっか"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:636
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_5757848c:

    # "I hesitate a little before coming out with the words I really came here to say."
    "俺は少しためらいつつも、これを言うために本当はここに来た、その言葉を口に出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:638
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1b9aee79:

    # hi "Would you like me to stay? I don't have anything urgent to do at the moment, so it wouldn't be any trouble."
    hi "このまま一緒にいたほうがいい？　今急ぎの用事はないから、俺は大丈夫なんだけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:643
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_9e08340f:

    # "Her eyes slide away from me, and I lose any hope for an improvement of her mood. I wait for a response, but she doesn't say anything, nor give any kind of gesture. She just stands there, looking away from me."
    "華子の目が俺からそらされ、俺は華子の気分をよくする望みを失う。俺は返事を待つけど、華子は何も言わず、何の身振りも見せない。ただそこに立って、俺から目をそらしている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:645
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1b02d6e2:

    # hi "Hanako…?"
    hi "華子……?"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:647
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_aa82c4fa:

    # "She slowly shakes her head."
    "華子はゆっくりと頭を横に振る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:649
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_5a2aad8e:

    # hi "Okay. Um… good night, then."
    hi "そっか。んー……じゃあおやすみ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:659
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_41045647:

    # "With that, Hanako steps back and closes her door without a second word."
    "俺がそう言うと、華子は何も言わずに後ずさってドアを閉める。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:661
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_ad0b7271:

    # "More than a little worried, I retreat back to my room."
    "少なからず心配しながら、俺は自分の部屋へと引き返す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:669
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_92f037f7:

    # "Wandering up the hallway, I keep mulling over what happened. It felt like Hanako was only half there, as if I was interacting with a robot that was just doing what it was programmed to without any real thought."
    "廊下をさまよいながら、俺はさっきの出来事を考え続ける。華子はまるで上の空だった。実際には何も考えてなくて、プログラムに沿って動くだけのロボットとやり取りをしているみたいだった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:671
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_09350403:

    # "She was a husk of a person."
    "華子は抜け殻だった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:673
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_1b82ef03:

    # "This is frustrating. I had hoped that meeting Hanako would help the situation, but I feel like it's only made it harder to understand her. How am I supposed to try and help her when she quite literally shuts me out like that?"
    "じれったい。華子と会えば状況が改善するんじゃないかと思っていたけど、むしろ華子を理解するのが難しくなっただけな気がする。文字通り締め出されている状態で、どうやって華子を助けたらいいっていうんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:680
translate jp a4_hanako_truancy_d2ed6d3e:

    # "I don't even bother to turn on the light, opting instead to simply change into my pajamas, quickly choke down my evening pills, and collapse onto my bed."
    "俺は部屋の電気をつけようともせず、そのかわりすぐにパジャマに着替えることを選んで、夜のぶんの薬をさっと飲み干すとベッドに倒れ込む。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:696
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_37024097:

    # "Once again, Hanako doesn't turn up for class. Try as I might to concentrate on other matters, this fact continues to distract me throughout the entire school day, and even as I walk through the school gardens to the dormitories."
    "今日もまた、華子は学校に出て来なかった。他のことに集中しようとしても、そのことが俺の気を散らし続ける。学校にいる間ずっと、そして学校の庭を寮に向かって歩いている今でさえも。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:698
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_7d3ebbdb:

    # "I don't think today being her birthday is a coincidence, either. I don't know the link between the two events though, nor do I have any idea on what she's feeling."
    "今日が華子の誕生日なのも偶然だとは思えない。欠席と誕生日の関連性が俺にわかるわけじゃないし、華子が今どんな気持ちなのか見当もつかないけれど。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:700
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_253a7263:

    # "Were it physical pain, I could at least provide some limited comfort. With something like this though, I have no idea where to start."
    "もしこれが肉体的な苦痛だったなら、ある程度軽減してあげることはできるだろう。でも今の状況は、どこから始めていいのかまったくさっぱりだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:702
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_bd57428a:

    # "I run the people I know through my head, thinking about whether they could help. Shizune and Misha don't know that much about Hanako, and what little they do know they can't tell me. Same for the nurse."
    "誰か力になってくれる人はいないかと思いながら、頭の中で知り合いの顔を並べていく。 静音とミーシャは華子についてあまり知らないし、わずかながら知っていることを俺に教えるわけにもいかない。それはナースも同じだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:704
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_d1db478a:

    # "In the end, there's only one person that knows Hanako well and would be willing to tell me anything."
    "結局、華子のことをよく知っていて俺に何か教えてくれそうな人は一人しかいない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:709
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_35b4fb23:

    # "Entering my dormitory room, I notice something that takes me off guard; it's starting to feel familiar."
    "寮の自分の部屋に入ると、俺は意外なことに気づく。帰ってきたなという感じがし始めている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:711
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_6f2a3b0c:

    # "With everything that's going on around me, I'm thankful that this room's started to finally be somewhere I can relax a little. When I'd first entered Yamaku, it felt immediately foreign in every way, from the untouched neatness to the way it smelled."
    "身の回りでいろんな事が起きているなか、この部屋がついに俺にとって少しリラックスできる場所になりはじめてくれたことをありがたく思う。 俺が最初山久に入学したときは、この部屋はあらゆる意味でなじみのないものに感じられた。使われていない綺麗さから、部屋の匂いまですべてが。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:713
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f5ee0de4:

    # "Focusing back on the task at hand, I throw my bag onto the bed as I open the top drawer of my desk."
    "目先の仕事に集中を戻す。かばんをベッドに投げ出すと、デスクの一番上の引き出しを開く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:715
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_b7b9a1ca:

    # "Before she left, Lilly told me the number to call her on while in Scotland and I wrote it down. In hindsight, I wonder if she knew something like this could happen."
    "リリーがスコットランドに旅立つ前に、向こうにいる間の電話番号を教えてくれたので、それを書き留めておいた。今思えば、リリーはこの状況を予見していたのかなと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:717
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_b1a6f1da:

    # "Now that she's out of reach, I realize just how much both Hanako and I have relied on her for guidance."
    "リリーが手の届かないところに行ってしまってようやく、華子も俺もどれだけリリーの導きに頼っていたのかということに気づかされる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:719
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_e2dd835b:

    # "I dig around drawer after drawer, looking for that damned piece of paper. Eventually, thankfully, I find it nestled under a borrowed library book."
    "ちっぽけな紙切れを探して、引き出しを次から次へとあさっていく。ようやく幸運にも、図書室で借りた本の下に落ちているのを発見する。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:732
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_0eb9e616:

    # "I probably should have just entered it directly into my cell phone, come to think of it. Without further ado, I enter the numbers and anxiously press the call button."
    "考えてみれば、携帯に直接番号を登録しておけば良かったな。俺はさっさと番号を入力し、気もそぞろになりながら通話ボタンを押す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:734
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_8c522459:

    # "Eventually the phone picks up, a feminine voice I don't recognize on the other end. It's probably Lilly's mother."
    "しばらくして電話がつながり、電話の向こう側から聞き覚えのない女性の声がする。たぶんリリーのお母さんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:738
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_ace98ff8:

    # mystery "{image=vfx/garbage.png} {image=vfx/garbage.png} Satou {image=vfx/garbage.png}?"
    mystery "{image=vfx/garbage.png} {image=vfx/garbage.png} Satou {image=vfx/garbage.png}?"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:740
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_7939bce8:

    # "English? Suddenly finding myself unprepared, I realize I can't understand a word she says, either due to my limited vocabulary or her heavy accent. I should have anticipated this, since according to Lilly, her mother is a native Scot."
    "英語？　不意を突かれた気分だ。俺の少ない語彙のせいか、相手の訛りのせいか、この人の言っていることが一言も理解できない。リリーによれば母親は生粋のスコットランド人だから、俺も予想しておくべきだった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:742
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_130fe69d:

    # "I soldier on in the hope that she must know some Japanese, considering it's her daughter's native language."
    "リリーの母語は日本語なのだから、相手も少しは日本語が分かるだろうと期待して、俺は踏みとどまる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:744
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_cf31c2ae:

    # hi "Um, it's Hisao Nakai… speaking…"
    hi "えっと、中井久夫……といいますが……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:746
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_3ac7d1af:

    # "An enthusiastic sound of realization can be heard as she recognizes the language. My feeling of relief is immense."
    "向こうがこちらの言葉を理解したようで、興奮したような声が聞こえてくる。とてつもない安堵感が俺の胸に広がる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:748
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_fc3e6151:

    # "Mrs. Satou" "Ah, you must be one of Lilly's friends from school, correct?"
    "砂藤さん" "あら、あなた、リリーの学校のお友達よね？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:750
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_3cda47f5:

    # "Even so, her accent means I have to concentrate to work out what she's saying."
    "それでも訛りのある口調なので、何を言っているかを聞き取るのに集中しないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:752
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_b201fe5f:

    # hi "Yes, that's right. Pleased to speak to you, Mrs. Satou."
    hi "はい、そうです。はじめまして、砂藤さん"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:754
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_2ea8bf2c:

    # "Mrs. Satou" "It's so nice of her to find someone so polite! Lilly dear, it's for you!"
    "砂藤さん" "こんなに礼儀正しい人がリリーにいるだなんて！　リリーちゃん、あなたによ！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:756
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_fc61db99:

    # "Her mother seems nice, if a little overenthusiastic given the mundane situation."
    "リリーのお母さんはいい人そうだな。ありふれたシチュエーションなのにちょっと興奮しすぎな気もするけど。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:758
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_02b9e8ae:

    # "There's a small silence as Lilly takes her time getting to the phone. In the distance, I can just make out her mother scolding her playfully for just getting up."
    "リリーが電話を取るまで少しの沈黙。遠くの方で、たった今起きたリリーをからかい半分に叱るお母さんの声がする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:760
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_7446da4f:

    # li "Hello, Lilly speaking."
    li "はい、リリーです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:762
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_6d8b5b6f:

    # hi "You sound awful."
    hi "ひどい声してるな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:764
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_b0e810c5:

    # "She makes a sound somewhere between a dying animal and a yawn."
    "リリーは瀕死の動物の鳴き声とあくびの混ざったような声を出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:766
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_0f624fbf:

    # "The one thing I did remember to check before calling was the time zone. It'd be pretty late in the morning over there, so she really has no excuse."
    "電話をかける前に時差は忘れずに調べておいた。向こうでは昼も近いだろうから、リリーには弁解の余地もない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:768
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_40ada99a:

    # hi "Not feeling well?"
    hi "調子がよくないのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:770
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_b0fd1eef:

    # li "Just tired. What time is it there?"
    li "疲れているだけです。そちらは何時ですか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:772
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_9436bb81:

    # hi "Late afternoon. School finished for the day not long ago."
    hi "夕方。少し前に今日の授業が終わった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:774
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_4af13e57:

    # li "Hanako's not well, is she?"
    li "華ちゃんが良くないんですね？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:778
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f471fdce:

    # "That was quick. My assumption that she must have known something like this could happen seems to have been on the mark."
    "速いな。リリーはこうなることを予見していたんだろうという俺の推測は正しかったらしい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:780
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_d82d90a3:

    # hi "How did you know?"
    hi "どうして分かったんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:782
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_b8ab3c4c:

    # li "Because today is her birthday. I'd hoped she might have gotten at least a little better after coming to know you, but…"
    li "それは、今日が華ちゃんの誕生日だからです。あなたと知り合ってからは、少しは良くなっているだろうと思っていたのですが……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:784
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_819f2fdf:

    # li "How is she right now?"
    li "華ちゃんは今どんな様子ですか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:786
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_6b8f0de7:

    # hi "She missed school today and yesterday. I still have to check up on her today. To be honest, after seeing how she was when I talked to her yesterday… I'm pretty anxious."
    hi "今日も昨日も学校に来なかったよ。今日はまだ様子を見に行ってないから後で行かないと。正直なところ、昨日華子に会いに行った時の様子を見ると……すごく心配だ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:788
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_bc882dcb:

    # hi "I really have no idea what to make of it. Has this happened in the past? Is it related to her scarring in some way?"
    hi "どうしたらいいのか本当にわからないんだ。前にもあったことなのか？　華子の傷に何か関係があるのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:790
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f85debad:

    # li "Unfortunately so. Roughly the same thing happened last year when her birthday came up."
    li "あいにくですけど、そうなんです。去年も、華ちゃんの誕生日が近づいたときに同じようなことが起こりました"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:792
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_79f2bd05:

    # li "As far as I can tell, it's because her parents died in the accident that caused her scarring, and Hanako blames herself for their deaths."
    li "私にわかるのは、華ちゃんの傷は彼女の両親が事故で亡くなったことと関係している、それと華ちゃんは二人が亡くなったのは自分のせいだと思っている、ということです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:794
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_66d108b9:

    # "What she says does seem to make sense. If she's blaming herself on her birthday, she may well be ruing that she was ever born."
    "リリーの言うことはもっともだ。華子が自分の誕生日に自分を責めているとすれば、生まれてきたことを後悔しているとしてもおかしくない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:796
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_dd53e8aa:

    # "Hanako had mentioned her stay in the orphanage to me. Maybe I should take some heart that she trusts me enough to tell me such a thing."
    "華子は孤児院にいたことを俺に話してくれていた。そんなことを教えてくれるほど信頼してくれていることに少しは自信をもつべきかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:798
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_14e0cb3d:

    # "Lilly seeming so in the dark about it though, almost to the extent that I am, is a surprise."
    "でもリリーが、ほとんど俺と同じくらいそのことについて知らずにいる、というのは驚きだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:800
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_07a59dcd:

    # hi "So that's why she lives in the student dormitories, as well. Has she told you any more about the accident?"
    hi "だから華子は学生寮に住んでるのか。事故のこと、リリーにはそれ以上話したのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:802
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_2c7ec658:

    # li "As close as we've come… she's very barely told me anything about what happened. What I know about it is largely conjecture."
    li "ここまで親しくはなりましたけど……何が起きたのか、華ちゃんはほとんど話してくれませんでした。私が知っていることの大部分は推測です"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:804
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_910e668c:

    # "She sounds depressed, almost defeated. Considering the trauma Hanako must have gone through, I really can't fault Lilly for not knowing. Nevertheless, she still seems to consider it a personal failing."
    "沈んだ、打ちひしがれたかのような声でリリーが言う。華子が受けたであろう心の傷を考えれば、知らないのも無理はないと思う。それでもリリーはそれを自分の落ち度だと思っているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:806
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_5bb7f668:

    # hi "Don't blame yourself, Lilly. With everything she's gone through…"
    hi "自分を責めるなよ、リリー。それだけのことがあったのなら……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:808
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_739fba08:

    # "There's a long silence from the other end of the line. I begin to wonder if the call cut out before the voice at the other end speaks once again."
    "電話の向こうからの返事はなく、長い沈黙が訪れる。向こうがまた喋りはじめる前に電話が切れてしまったんじゃないかと思い始める。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:810
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_16000a28:

    # li "There is another person, though, that has been a subject of worry for me as of late."
    li "でも、最近はもう１人私が心配している人がいるんですよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:812
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f9075882:

    # hi "Oh?"
    hi "へえ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:814
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_57bd3fda:

    # "I run through the people she could be talking about in my head. The only friends she seems to keep very close are Hanako and me, though there is Akira as well…"
    "リリーが言っているのは誰だろうと思い浮かべてみる。リリーのごく身近な友達は華子と俺しかいない。晃さんもいるにはいるけど……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:816
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_1ce1b357:

    # li "That person is you, Hisao."
    li "あなたですよ、久夫さん"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:818
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_c01205de:

    # "There's another silence on the line, but this time it's caused by me."
    "また沈黙が訪れる。でも今度は俺のせいで起こっている沈黙だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:820
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_fe2a5175:

    # "Making others worry about me is something I've very actively tried to avoid since coming to Yamaku. Indeed, even my interaction with Hanako has helped stave off any major health problems thanks to our relaxed and slow-paced lives."
    "周りに心配をかけることは、俺が山久に来てから全力で避けようとしてきたことだ。実際に華子との交流だって、その気張らずゆったりとした性質のおかげで、大きな健康上の問題を避けるのに役立ってきた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:822
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_3f389174:

    # hi "Uh… huh. What is there to worry about over me?"
    hi "うーん……そうか。俺の何を心配することがあるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:824
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_81275b4e:

    # li "I apologize; I didn't mean any offense."
    li "すみません。気を悪くしないでくださいね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:826
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_e08be9b0:

    # hi "Sorry, I was just taken a bit off guard. Still, isn't Hanako a bigger problem at the moment?"
    hi "ごめん、ただちょっとびっくりしただけなんだよ。でも今は華子のほうが問題じゃないか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:828
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_66382e29:

    # li "For some time now I've thought that the both of you may be feeding into each other's more worrying habits. I tried to amend this before leaving, but it seems to have done little."
    li "ここしばらく、久夫さんも華ちゃんもお互いの心配癖を強め合ってるんじゃないかという風に思っていたんです。こちらに来る前にそれを直そうとしたんですが、あまり効果はなかったようですね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:830
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_21faa283:

    # hi "'Worrying habits?'"
    hi "『心配癖』？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:832
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_7f77427d:

    # li "When I asked you about what you had in mind for the future, your answer was very similar to what Hanako has said in the past when that question was posed to her."
    li "私が久夫さんに将来のことについて聞いたとき、久夫さんの答えは華ちゃんが昔同じ質問に返した答えととてもよく似ていました"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:834
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_7b4ec882:

    # li "It is well and good to want to protect her, but I fear that treating Hanako like this, as if she were a daughter or someone in need of special care, is only going to achieve the opposite."
    li "華ちゃんを守りたいと思うのは悪いことではありませんが、華ちゃんをこういう風に、まるで自分の娘であったり特別な庇護が必要な人のように扱うというのは逆効果にしかならないと思うんです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:847
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_52941782:

    # "I don't want to admit it, but she may have a point. Something else bugs me, though."
    "認めたくはないけど、リリーの言うことには一理あるかもしれない。別なことが気になってしょうがないけど。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:849
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_bc821f28:

    # hi "And you tried to… 'amend' this?"
    hi "それで、リリーが……『直そう』としたっていうのは？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:851
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_dc612ef8:

    # hi "Wait… our outing into the city?"
    hi "待てよ……みんなで街に行ったことか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:853
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_c1a30b95:

    # li "Quite astute. I thought that it might help if I dragged both of you out of Yamaku and into the wider world. I am thankful you became closer for it, though."
    li "ご明察です。二人を山久から広い外の世界に連れ出せば助けになるかと思ったんです。それで二人が親しくなってくれたのはよかったですけどね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:855
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_15c42a13:

    # "So she noticed that. I suppose she may well have been paying attention to us, and her hearing's incredibly good; quite likely good enough to have picked up what we were talking about, if she tried."
    "気づいていたのか。たぶん俺たちに注意を払っていたんだろう。そしてリリーの耳はとてもいい。その気になれば俺たちが何を喋っているのかも盗み聞きできるんじゃないだろうか。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:857
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_13881099:

    # hi "This sounds more and more like you were manipulating us."
    hi "ますます俺たちを操ろうとしてたみたいに聞こえてくるな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:859
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_78427f1e:

    # "Silence. It's a harsh way of putting it, but I have no intention of stepping back from those words."
    "沈黙。かなりとげとげしい表現をしたけど、こういう言葉を避けるつもりはない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:861
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_469f9545:

    # li "I'm sorry. I was just… worried about you."
    li "ごめんなさい。私はただ……心配だったんです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:863
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f445d267:

    # hi "It's fine. I guess there are more important things anyway."
    hi "いいさ。そんなことよりもっと大事なことがあると思うしね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:865
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_ac5d7e1e:

    # "It's not a total surprise that she'd do such a thing. Her motherly nature can be slightly overbearing at times, but she does have the best of intentions."
    "リリーがそんなことをしたのはまったく驚きというわけじゃない。リリーの母性は少し尊大になることもあるかもしれないけど、いつもちゃんと誠意は持っている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:867
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_e5a35a99:

    # hi "So you think I should think about myself more instead of trying to cater to Hanako?"
    hi "じゃあリリーは、俺は華子の要求をかなえようとばかりするんじゃなくて、俺自身のことをもっと考えるべきだと思うんだな？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:869
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_7ca9acf9:

    # li "That largely sums it up. Again, I'm sorry for not telling you this in a clearer way before going behind your back."
    li "まあそういうことです。繰り返しになりますが、はっきりと伝えずに裏切るようなことをしてしまってごめんなさい"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:871
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_92e3c2cc:

    # li "I know I am at least as guilty of being overprotective of Hanako as you, but I fear that you are neglecting yourself in your efforts to give Hanako happiness."
    li "少なくとも私も、久夫さんと同じくらい華ちゃんに対して過保護だという意味では同罪です。でも、久夫さんは華ちゃんを幸せにしようと努力するあまり自分を無視しているのではないかと心配なんです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:873
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_bb7134ba:

    # hi "Do you really think Hanako will be okay?"
    hi "華子は本当に大丈夫だと思うか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:875
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_50d75e61:

    # li "She isn't as fragile as you think. I don't know exactly what experiences she's lived through, or what feelings she has in her mind, but she has managed to work her way through them until now."
    li "華ちゃんは久夫さんが思っているほどやわじゃありませんよ 私には華ちゃんがどんな経験をしてきたのかも、どんな気持ちを抱いてるのかも正確にはわかりませんが、それでも華ちゃんは今まで自分の道を切り開いてきたんです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:877
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f5a6930c:

    # li "It's also my hope that giving her a little space will allow her to decide what she truly wants for herself, and give her the initiative to reach out for it."
    li "これは私の望みでもありますが、少しそっとしておいてあげることで華ちゃんも自分が本当に欲しいものを決めることができて、自分からそれに手を伸ばせるようになるんじゃないでしょうか"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:879
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_950c5a18:

    # li "Please have faith in Hanako. That's all I ask."
    li "華ちゃんを信じてあげてください。お願いしたいのはそれだけです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:881
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_7a0e3697:

    # hi "I'll… I guess I'll think about it for a while."
    hi "俺は……もう少し考えてみるよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:883
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_eef81fdb:

    # li "That's good. Being rash won't get you anywhere."
    li "それでかまいません。焦っても得るものはありませんしね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:885
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_48b2b9bf:

    # li "I know that at times you may doubt your relationship to Hanako, but she does…"
    li "華ちゃんとの関係が心配になることがあるのはわかります、でも華ちゃんは……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:887
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_db9f47e7:

    # "Lilly cuts herself off and takes a moment to reconsider her words."
    "リリーは言葉を遮ると、言う事を考えなおす。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:889
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_4abecb85:

    # li "Please keep in mind that I wouldn't have befriended you if I hadn't thought you a fundamentally good person. You're a good friend, both to myself and to Hanako."
    li "久夫さんが心根の良い人だと思ったからこそ私は久夫さんとお友達になったということは忘れないでください。私にとっても華ちゃんにとってもいいお友達です"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:891
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_91ba273f:

    # hi "Thank you. That helps."
    hi "ありがとう。気が楽になった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:893
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_c18a61b8:

    # "We share some smalltalk to try and lighten the atmosphere, but it feels very stilted. There's a lot I don't know about Lilly's stay in Scotland, but after such a heavy subject, I want to be alone for a bit to think."
    "暗くなった雰囲気を明るくしようと、しばらく雑談をするけど、すごくぎこちなく感じる。 リリーのスコットランドでの滞在について知らないことはいっぱいあるけど、あんな重い話題のあとだから、俺も少し一人になって考えたくなる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:910
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f5519d39:

    # "After a few minutes, we end up saying our goodbyes and I set my phone on my desk."
    "何分か経つころには、さよならの挨拶を交わして電話を机の上に置く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:912
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_25058384:

    # "Compared to Hanako's situation, mine feels utterly mundane. I still have both of my parents, I had a reasonably normal childhood, and unlike many in Yamaku, my condition isn't immediately visible to the public."
    "華子の状況に比べたら、俺の暮らしはまったく平凡に感じる。まだ両親は健在で、まあ普通の子供時代。大勢の他の生徒みたいに、パッと見てすぐにわかるような病気でもない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:914
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_ebef67dd:

    # "But then again… isn't this just an attempt to justify the way I've been acting towards her?"
    "とはいえ……こういう考えだって、俺がこれまで華子にしてきた接し方を正当化しようとしているだけなんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:916
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_9864f810:

    # "That may well be what our pasts were like, but when it comes to the future I still have no idea what I want to do. In school I've just concentrated on each day's work, and I've put off more and more things to cater to Hanako."
    "それが俺たちが今までにしてきたことだったのかもしれない。でも将来のこととなると、自分がどうしたいのかはまださっぱりわからない。 学校では毎日の勉強にただ集中していたけど、華子を楽しませることにかこつけてどんどん物事を先延ばしにするようになっていた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:918
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_a5b1aafb:

    # "I recall the words Mutou told me after Hanako's breakdown; about the purpose of Yamaku and my education. In hindsight, he was probably trying to push exactly the same thing."
    "華子が教室で動揺したときの武藤先生の言葉を思い出す。山久と俺の教育の目的。今思えば、きっと武藤先生はまさにリリーと同じ事を勧めようとしていたんじゃないか。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:920
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_9f032398:

    # "Just what have I been doing in the time since my heart attack? If I ever did manage to get Hanako out of her room and to open up, what then?"
    "心臓発作が起きて以来、俺は一体何をしてきた？　もしいつか華子を部屋から連れ出して心を開かせることができたとして、それからどうするんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:922
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_26041a05:

    # "I look out of my dormitory window as the sun slowly sets. It's a nice sight, but what I really savor is the quiet as the students return to their dormitory rooms."
    "寮の窓から外を眺めていると、太陽がゆっくりと沈んでいく。いい景色だけど、俺が本当に味わっているのは生徒たちが寮の部屋に帰っていくことによる静けさだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:924
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_974909f5:

    # "All I want to do now is think. I'm not sure how much time I have, but I want to work out where I'll go from here."
    "今はただ考えたい。どれだけの時間があるのかはわからないけど、自分がここからどこに向かっていくのかを考えたい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:931
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_432974ef:

    # "I listen carefully to what Lilly has to say, but I can't bring myself to agree with her."
    "リリーの言わんとしていることに俺はじっくりと耳を傾けるけど、リリーに同意する気にはなれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:933
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_e0086ef7:

    # "I want to be with Hanako more. I want to be a better friend to her, to support her when she needs support, and to be there when she most needs people. I think that now is one of those times."
    "もっと華子と一緒にいたい。もっといい友達になりたい。支えが必要なときに支えてあげたい。周りの人の力が本当に必要なときにそこにいてあげたい。今こそがその時じゃないか。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:935
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_0f2c3392:

    # "The memory of the store owner we met in town together still puts me off. Anyone who takes even the slightest glance at Hanako ends up staring, and to fault them for it would be completely hypocritical, given my own reaction."
    "華子と街に行ったときに出会った店主にはまだ腹が立つ。華子をほんのひと目見ただけでみんな凝視し始める。でも俺自身が華子にどんな反応をしたかを考えると、そんな人たちのことを責めるのは完全に偽善だろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:937
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_6a9ec625:

    # "I don't like my own scarring either, but at least I can cover it up with something as simple as a shirt. I can't imagine a life where every day would be spent trying to hide myself as much as possible."
    "俺だって自分の傷跡は好きじゃないけど、シャツのように簡単なもので隠せてしまうものだ。毎日できるだけ自分を隠しながら過ごす人生というのは想像もつかない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:939
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_69c7a937:

    # "And on top of that, Hanako doesn't even have people around her that would support her no matter what she looks like. I live away from my parents, but I can still contact and visit them when I wish."
    "そのうえ、彼女の外見がどうだろうと華子を支えてくれるような人すら華子のそばにはいない。俺は両親から離れて暮らしているけど、それでもその気になれば連絡をとって会いに行く事はできる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:941
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_8a9d22cb:

    # "I mull over the best course of action in my head, and find myself trying to verbally agree with Lilly as softly and as ambivalently as I can."
    "これからどうするのが一番いいか頭の中で考えながら、俺は気が付けば言葉の上ではリリーに同意しようとしている。できるかぎりやわらかく、できるかぎりあいまいに。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:943
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f044533d:

    # "We make some smalltalk afterwards, but the both of us don't really have much stomach for it in the light of recent events. We say our goodbyes before I hang up."
    "そのあと少し雑談するけど、最近の出来事もあってお互いにあまり乗り気ではない。さよならの挨拶をして、電話を切る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:958
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_f1be09b6:

    # "There is at least one thing I can do for Hanako. If I make this small gesture for her, I can only hope that she allows me to come that little bit closer."
    "華子のためにできることが少なくとも１つはある。この小さな誠意を見せて、あとは華子が俺に距離を縮めることを許してくれるのを祈るだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:962
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_432974ef_1:

    # "I listen carefully to what Lilly has to say, but I can't bring myself to agree with her."
    "リリーの言わんとしていることに俺はじっくりと耳を傾けるけど、リリーに同意する気にはなれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:964
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_4d6b7e92:

    # "Hanako is a delicate person at the best of times, and after what happened when her birthday was brought up, I think this is the very last situation where we should be leaving her alone if she's deliberately secluding herself."
    "華子はどんなに調子がいいときでも繊細な子だ。そして誕生日の話題になったときに起こったことを考えても、今は自分から閉じこもろうとしている華子を一人にしておいてはいけない状況だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:966
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_9cc429d1:

    # "It feels like Lilly has a very definite image of how best to deal with Hanako in her mind, though. Not just now, but in all the time that I've known the two."
    "リリーは華子にどう接するのが一番いいか頭の中に明確なイメージを持っているように感じる。今だけじゃない、二人と知り合ってからこれまではずっとそうだった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:968
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_8a9d22cb_1:

    # "I mull over the best course of action in my head, and find myself trying to verbally agree with Lilly as softly and as ambivalently as I can."
    "これからどうするのが一番いいか頭の中で考えながら、俺は気が付けば言葉の上ではリリーに同意しようとしている。できるかぎりやわらかく、できるかぎりあいまいに。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:970
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_219bc0f2:

    # "We make some smalltalk afterwards, but neither of us really has much stomach for it in the light of recent events. We say our goodbyes before I hang up."
    "そのあと少し雑談するけど、最近の出来事もあってお互いにあまり乗り気ではない。さよならの挨拶をして、電話を切る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:985
translate jp a4_hanako_faraway_presence_680eef7b:

    # "I want to talk to Hanako myself, to help her as best I can. The best thing for her right now would be to have someone close to her, not to be left alone."
    "自分で華子と話したい。出来る限りの力になりたい。華子にとっても今一番いいのは、一人でいることじゃなく誰かがそばにいることだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1001
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_2a35ff27:

    # "I rap my knuckles thrice on Hanako's door. As expected, there's no answer. I briefly consider knocking again, but I know full well that I'd get just the same result if I did."
    "華子の部屋のドアを拳で３回叩く。思った通り、返事はない。もう一度ノックしようかと少し考えるけど、そんなことをしても同じ結果になるだろうことはよくわかっている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1003
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_32635415:

    # "Resting my hand on Hanako's door handle, I try and prepare what I want to say to her. Try as I might, I can't really think of anything worth saying. I want to comfort her, yes, but I have no idea how to do that."
    "手をドアの取っ手に乗せたまま、華子に伝えたい言葉を思い浮かべようとする。思い浮かべようとするけど、言う価値があるような事は思いつかない。華子を元気づけたいけど、どうすればいいのか見当もつかない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1005
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_7a0d13f3:

    # "That alone is almost enough to stop me. I told Lilly that I would, though, so I feel I have to follow through, whether I'm confident about it or not."
    "そのことだけでも俺は思いとどまりそうになる。でもリリーにそう言ったし、自信があろうとなかろうと俺はやり遂げなければならないと感じる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1007
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_cfed43c9:

    # "I turn the handle downwards, with a large amount of hesitation. It doesn't move far though, due to the door being locked."
    "大きくためらいつつも、俺はハンドルを下へ回す。しかしロックされていて少ししか動かない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1009
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_6f5dad09:

    # hi "Hanako…"
    hi "華子……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1011
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_8de30f0b:

    # "So she really has locked me out. After everything that happened between us, and the time that we spent together… she's shut me out completely."
    "華子は本当に俺を締め出している。俺たちの間には色んなことがあって、一緒に過ごした時間があったけど……華子は俺を完全に締め出している。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1013
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_179098ff:

    # hi "Um… I don't know if you can hear me, but…"
    hi "あー……聞こえてるかわからないけど……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1015
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_01d3737a:

    # hi "I just want to talk to you a bit. If you can hear me, could you unlock the door?"
    hi "ちょっと話したいだけなんだ。聞こえてたら、ドアを開けてくれないか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1021
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_677223e2:

    # "I wait in silence. Minutes pass, but eventually I hear footsteps coming to the door and the lock being worked."
    "俺はただ静かに待つ。何分も経って、やがてドアに近づいてくる足音と鍵を開ける音が聞こえる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1023
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_8d2bff0b:

    # "At least she's willing to hear me out. That's one good thing."
    "少なくとも華子は俺の話を聞いてくれそうだ。よかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1025
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_0c3cf177:

    # hi "I… I don't really know what to say, but… I just wanted to see you. I wanted to make sure you're all right."
    hi "俺は……なんて言うのかわからないけど……ただ会いたかったんだ。華子が大丈夫だってことを確認したかった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1027
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_1b2395ce:

    # "I take a breath before pushing the handle down and opening the door. If she unlocked it without raising any protest, it should be fine for me to go in."
    "俺は息を吸うと、ハンドルを押し下げてドアを開く。何も言わずに鍵を開けてくれたということは、中に入るのはいいんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1045
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_2e3680dd:

    # "Hanako is sitting on the side of her bed, her face sullen as though deep in thought. Her room is as stark as ever, and right now, she seems to perfectly suit the mood it gives off."
    "華子はベッドの端に腰掛けていて、なにか深く考え込んでいるかのようにぶすっとした顔をしている。 華子の部屋はいつもと同じように殺風景で、でも今は、華子はその部屋の醸し出す雰囲気と完全に調和しているように感じる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1053
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_ef10d2c0:

    # "Eventually, her eyes slowly move to the door. As soon as she notices my presence, she darts off her bed and jumps to her feet, facing me straight-on."
    "やがて、華子の目がゆっくりとドアのほうに向く。俺の存在に気づくと、ベッドから逃げ出すように飛び立って起き上がり、まっすぐ俺に向き直る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1055
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_7028f6c6:

    # "Her oversized gown makes this gesture look all the more sweeping as it freely moves about her light frame."
    "華子が着ている大きすぎるガウンが華子の細い線の周りを好き勝手に動きまわるせいで、ますます大袈裟な動きに見える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1057
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_d5c2d5b3:

    # ha "Wh-what are you…?"
    ha "な、何を……?"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1059
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_e5d687f9:

    # "I quickly regret coming in as I look at her. She looks depressed, but there's a tinge of anger behind it. So, she can make this kind of expression as well."
    "華子を見て、部屋に入ったことをすぐに後悔する。憂鬱な顔をしているけど、その裏には怒りの色がある。こういう表情も出来るんだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1061
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_6600d17a:

    # hi "I… I just wanted to check that you were all right. I thought it would be okay, since you unlocked the door."
    hi "俺は……華子が大丈夫か確かめたかっただけなんだ。鍵を開けてくれたから入ってもいいかと思って"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1066
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_e68d1f2c:

    # "Hanako opens her mouth to speak, but quickly closes it again before looking away."
    "華子は口を開いてなにか言おうとするけど、すぐにまた口を閉じて目をそらす。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1073
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_3851675d:

    # "We stand in silence for a while, before she steps back and sits down on the side of her bed. I'm not sure whether she's frustrated with me and resigned to the fact that I'm here, or genuinely okay with me being in her room."
    "俺たちは黙ったまましばらく立ち尽くす。やがて華子は後ずさってベッドの端に腰掛ける。 華子が俺に腹を立てているけどもう既に部屋に入ってしまったことに諦めているだけなのか、それとも本当にこの部屋にいてもいいということなのか、俺は計りかねている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1075
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_6cff674b:

    # "Once again, I find myself completely unable to work out how she feels. It's annoying."
    "またしても俺は華子の気持ちがまったく分からなくなっている。じれったい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1077
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_b2afa3c9:

    # "I end up walking to her desk chair and taking a seat. I do it slowly, to allow her time to raise any issue she might have with me sticking around, but she doesn't say anything. All she does is stare at the ground, not moving a muscle."
    "結局、俺は机まで歩いていって椅子に腰掛ける。華子が周りをうろつく俺に問題を感じているなら異議を唱えられる時間を持てるよう、ゆっくりと。でも華子は何も言わず、身じろぎ一つせずにただ床を見つめている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1079
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_5969fd51:

    # "After sitting with my front to the chair's back, I take a better look at Hanako. She appears pale, but her cheeks look red. I'm not sure she's been eating well, either, given how thin her frame looks."
    "俺は逆向きに椅子に座ると、華子をよく見てみる。顔は蒼白としてるけど、頬は赤い。本当に細い体つきだけど、ちゃんと食べてるのかもわからない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1081
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_582277be:

    # "Lilly might have said it would be better if I kept more of a distance from her, but it's hard to think of that as the correct way to deal with Hanako when she looks like this."
    "リリーは俺が華子からもっと距離を置いたほうがいいと言うかもしれないけど、こんな華子を見ているとそれが正しい華子への接し方だとはとても思えない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1083
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_21db11b5:

    # "She keeps looking at the ground without a word, as if waiting for me to say something. It's entirely reasonable, since I'm the one who came into her room."
    "華子はまるで俺がなにか言うのを待っているかのように、何も言わずに床を見つめ続けている。そもそも部屋に入ってきたのは俺なんだから、それはもっともだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1085
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_c9d607f0:

    # hi "Want to go out somewhere? Going down the hill to town might be a bit much, but we could at least go for a walk outside."
    hi "どこか出かけたいか？　坂を降りて街までっていうのは行き過ぎだろうけど、散歩するくらいならありだろ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1090
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_d74bf7ec:

    # ha "Why… do you want to do that?"
    ha "なんで……そうしたいの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1092
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_6c1af3a9:

    # hi "I was just thinking that it might help you a bit. You spend so much time inside, your skin's going to get as pale as Lilly's before long."
    hi "それが華子の助けになるかなと思ったからだよ。こんなに家の中で過ごしてたらすぐにリリーみたいに青白い肌になっちゃうぞ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1097
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_485afd5e:

    # "I snort in amusement, expecting Hanako to do the same, but she gives no reaction; she just goes back to looking at the ground."
    "俺は面白がって鼻を鳴らす。華子もそうすると思ったけど、何の反応も示さない。また元通り床を見つめ続けている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1099
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_027c499e:

    # ha "If you don't want to go… I-I don't want to go either."
    ha "久夫くんが行きたくないなら……わ、私も行きたくない"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1101
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_3a724dd4:

    # hi "It's fine. I played soccer and hung out with friends after school a lot before coming to Yamaku, so I like being outdoors."
    hi "行くのは問題ないよ。山久に来る前はサッカーをやってたし放課後も友達と遊んでたから出かけるのは好きなんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1103
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_52a6d0f4:

    # "Hanako shows no visible reaction. It's hard to talk to her when the discussion is so one-sided."
    "華子は目に見える反応を示さない。会話がこうも一方的だと話すのが難しい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1105
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_55594cc0:

    # hi "We could go to the library… uh, if it wasn't closed by about now. The gardens would be fine, though."
    hi "図書室に行ってもいいし……あ、まだ閉まってなければね。学校の庭でもいいけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1107
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_9a52b6fa:

    # "She begins to play with her hair. It's distracting, and strikes me as a little unusual for her."
    "華子は髪をいじりはじめる。気が散る動作だけど、華子がこういうことをするのはちょっと珍しいと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1109
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_d404d6cc:

    # "Then again, since the incident in class happened, I've been tiptoeing around her for fear of hurting her like that again. Actively trying to get her outside might be a good thing."
    "そしてまた、教室でのあの事件からこっち、俺はまたあんな風に華子を傷つけたらどうしようととても慎重に接してきた。積極的に外に連れ出すのはいいことかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1111
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_501ce03c:

    # "I lean forward a bit more in the chair and give her a slightly forced smile, to try and lighten the mood a little."
    "俺は椅子から身を乗り出すと、わずかにでも雰囲気を明るくしようと少し無理をした作り笑いを華子に向ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1113
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_40ee63d0:

    # hi "There wouldn't be anyone around by now, so you wouldn't have to worry about someone getting in our way. It could be a little date or something."
    hi "もう誰もいないだろうし、邪魔するやつがいるような心配もないさ。ちょっとしたデートみたいなもんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1118
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_6dd7c679:

    # "I give a small chuckle, but catch myself as Hanako stops playing with her hair and grips the bed tightly. Hanako's mouth moves, but try as I might, I can't pick out what she's mumbling."
    "俺はそう言って小さく笑うけど、華子が髪をいじりまわすのをやめてベッドを強く掴んだのを見てすぐにやめる。華子の口が動いたけど、その呟きを聞き取ることができない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1120
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_eea78bab:

    # hi "Hanako?"
    hi "華子？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1122
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_ee000cdb:

    # ha "You… don't understand…"
    ha "あなたは……わかってない……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1124
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_11619872:

    # "Even now, I can only barely understand what she says. It feels like she's trying to make her presence as small as possible; that's incredibly natural for her to do in class or around others, but it hurts when she tries it around me."
    "今でも華子の言うことは辛うじてわかるだけだ。まるで華子は自分の存在をできるかぎり小さくしようとしているように感じる。 教室や他の人がいる状況で華子がそうするのはとても自然だけど、俺の周りでもそうされるのは辛い。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1126
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_1c060a67:

    # hi "I told you, it's fine. It's just a little walk, nobody'll notice us."
    hi "だから大丈夫だって。ちょっと散歩するだけだよ。誰も気にもとめないさ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1128
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_8ee2eab3:

    # "I get out of the chair and walk towards the door, turning back to invite Hanako along. Once again, she doesn't respond at all to what I say."
    "俺は椅子から立ち上がり、ドアのほうへ歩いて振り向くと華子を誘う。またしても、華子は俺の言葉にまったく反応を返さない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1133
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_55c7f3b3:

    # ha "I don't…"
    ha "行かない……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1135
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_1b336ae1:

    # hi "Going outside for a bit is good for clearing your head."
    hi "ちょっとくらい外出するのは頭を空っぽにするのにいいって"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1137
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_22e76b8a:

    # ha "Why do you… want to do this…"
    ha "どうして……こんなことをするの……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1139
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_76a6b3eb:

    # hi "Because I want to help you."
    hi "華子の助けになりたいからだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1141
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_7380473e:

    # ha "I don't… want… help. Did you just come here… to try and get me out…?"
    ha "助け……なんか……いらない。まさかここにきたのは……ただ外に連れ出すためなの……？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1143
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_04b71091:

    # hi "I don't mind. I think everyone needs help sometimes. When I was trying to get through my first days at Yamaku, you and Lilly helped me a lot."
    hi "それでもいい。誰だって助けが必要なときはあると思う。俺が山久にきたばっかりの頃は華子とリリーがすごく助けてくれた"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1145
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_22ef636a:

    # hi "Besides, I'm not exactly busy."
    hi "それに、俺は忙しいわけじゃないし"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1147
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_ba37888c:

    # ha "I don't w-want to go. I'm… fine."
    ha "私はい、行きたくない。私は……大丈夫だから"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1149
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_d46d4fcf:

    # hi "I don't really think it's healthy to stay indoors that long. The sun's still got a little life in it, so it's not too late to have at least a little walk."
    hi "こんなに長いあいだ家の中にいるのは健康的とは思えないよ。太陽もまだ明るさがあるし、少なくともちょっと散歩するには遅すぎってことはないさ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1151
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_db5a6596:

    # hi "I could probably use a bit of exercise anyway, to help wake me up. I've got some homework to get done, and it wouldn't be good to fall asleep halfway through doing it."
    hi "それに俺も目を覚ますためにちょっと運動したほうがいいしな。やらないといけない宿題があるけど、やってる途中で寝ちゃったらよくないし"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1156
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_29da5cf0:

    # ha "Then… go."
    ha "じゃあ……行ってきて"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1158
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_cdd1f0bc:

    # hi "By myself?"
    hi "俺だけで？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1160
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "華子はうなずく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1162
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_ce5dade3:

    # hi "Well, I'm not really against that, but… are you sure? I swung by to invite you to come with me."
    hi "まあ、それが嫌なわけじゃないけど……本当に？　華子を誘うために寄ったんだけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1167
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_f7d265f2:

    # ha "I'm fine. You can go."
    ha "私は大丈夫。行っていい"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1169
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_cfbfec35:

    # hi "Come on, just a small walk."
    hi "そう言わずにさ、短い散歩だよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1171
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_8d219698:

    # ha "Please, just go. I-I'm fine here."
    ha "お願い、行って。わ、私はここでいい"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1173
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_22571833:

    # hi "…Hanako?"
    hi "……華子？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1175
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_2f159075:

    # "I try to look at her face to gauge her feelings, but her expression is wooden. As if it was so carefully arranged, that a single movement might cause it to collapse."
    "華子の気持ちを推し量るために彼女の顔を見ようとするけど、華子は無表情で、まるでほんの１つの動作で崩れかねない細工品のようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1177
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_f3e62464:

    # hi "Well, if you want to stay here… maybe we could play a game?"
    hi "ええと、ここにいたいなら……ゲームするのもいいかも？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1179
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_3d768310:

    # ha "Just leave. Please. I don't… want to do anything right now."
    ha "いいから帰って。おねがい。今は……何もしたくない"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1181
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_d6df93bf:

    # hi "Surely there's something you want to do. It must be boring, sitting here in your room alone."
    hi "やりたいことくらいあるはずだ。一人で部屋にじっとしてるなんてつまらないだろ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1183
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_f8af6cce:

    # ha "I want you to go."
    ha "帰ってほしい"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1185
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_b314d792:

    # hi "Come on, you don't have to be like that. I just want to spend some time with you. Lilly and I are worried, so…"
    hi "なあ、そんな風にしなくてもいいんだぞ。ただ一緒に過ごしたいだけなんだよ。俺もリリーも心配してるし、だから……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1190
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_7608f089:

    # ha "You… talked to her?"
    ha "リリーと……話したの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1192
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_33667f77:

    # hi "Uh… yeah. We were… on the phone, just a little while ago. We're both really worried about you."
    hi "ああ……うん。電話で……話したんだよ、ほんのちょっと前に。俺もリリーも本当に心配してたよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1197
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_2541bd78:

    # "Hanako mumbles to herself again. It's increasingly disturbing."
    "華子はまたなにか独り言をつぶやく。ますます不安になってくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1199
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_1b02d6e2:

    # hi "Hanako…?"
    hi "華子……?"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1201
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_93d5b350:

    # ha "I'm telling you… please, go away. You don't understand anything…"
    ha "ちゃんと聞いて……お願いだから、出て行って。なにもわかってない……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1203
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_8ac98e2a:

    # hi "If we just had a talk, you could tell me what I don't understand. I just want to protect you, I don't really see…"
    hi "話をしよう、そうすれば俺が何をわかってないのかも伝えられる。俺は華子を守りたいだけなんだよ。俺にはよくわからないんだ……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1205
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_1c973d46:

    # ha "Get… out, p-please…"
    ha "出て……行って、お、お願いだから……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1207
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_090e45c9:

    # hi "Just locking yourself in your room again isn't going to help anything, Hanako. Please…"
    hi "部屋に閉じこもってても何も解決しないんだよ、華子。たのむ……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1211
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_16b8cb94:

    # "Silence."
    "沈黙。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1213
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_35a5950a:

    # hi "Hanako, I just want to help you—{w=0.3}{nw}"
    hi "華子、俺はただお前を助けたくて――{w=0.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1225
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_66cbb989:

    # "She suddenly storms off her bed, turning to me with an expression that takes me completely off guard."
    "華子は急にベッドから飛び出すと、まったく予期だにしなかった表情を俺に向ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1227
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_4623a48e:

    # ha "Get out of my room, get out of my room, get out of my room…!" with vpunch
    ha "出てって、出てって、出てって……！" with vpunch

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1229
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_bdc3607f:

    # "Hanako yells at me with such force that, for the first time in a long time, I feel genuinely frightened. I… I have no idea how to react to this, and from Hanako of all people."
    "華子がものすごい勢いで俺に向かって叫び始めて、俺は長らく感じていなかった心からの恐怖を感じてしまう。 俺は……こんな反応にどう答えればいいのか、それもよりによって華子から返ってきたこんな反応にどう答えていいのかまったくわからない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1231
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_4bee0144:

    # ha "Leave! I'm telling you, go!" with vpunch
    ha "出てってって言ってるでしょ！　帰って！" with vpunch

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1233
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_19259774:

    # hi "B-but… I was just trying to… help you…"
    hi "で、でも……俺はただ……お前の助けになろうと……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1235
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_40345cf4:

    # ha "I know I need help! I know I'm broken! I don't need you to tell me that!" with vpunch
    ha "私に助けが必要なことくらい知ってる！　私が壊れてることくらい知ってる！　わざわざ言わなくていい！" with vpunch

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1237
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_1b7a0a41:

    # hi "I never said you were broken, or anything like that!"
    hi "お前が壊れてるとかそんなこと一度も言ってないぞ！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1239
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_68cd1823:

    # ha "It's written on your face, it's written on Lilly's face, it's written on everybody's faces!" with vpunch
    ha "そんなの顔に書いてある！　リリーの顔にも書いてある！　みんなの顔に書いてある！" with vpunch

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1241
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_cdea2920:

    # ha "I see a therapist every week, Lilly dotes on me as if I were her child, and now… even you!" with vpunch
    ha "毎週カウンセラーの先生に会ってる、リリーは私を子供みたいに甘やかしてくる、そして今度は……あなたまで！" with vpunch

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1243
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_9c76685b:

    # ha "Nothing's changed, nothing at all! I hate Lilly, and I… I hate you more than anyone…!" with vpunch
    ha "何も変わってない、まったく変わってない！　私はリリーが嫌い、私……私は誰よりもあなたが嫌い……！" with vpunch

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1245
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_9c5baf96:

    # "Her face moves in strange, almost grotesque ways. I've never seen someone completely lose it before, but it looks like the usually quiet and withdrawn girl in front of me is going into just such a destructive cycle before my eyes."
    "華子の顔が見たこともない、ほとんどおぞましいほどの変化を見せる。 今まで誰かが本当にキレてしまうところを見たことがなかったけど、目の前のいつもは静かで内気な女の子は、まさにその破壊的な状態に突入している。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1247
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_1bf10782:

    # "I don't know what to do. I have no idea what I should say or do."
    "どうしていいのかわからない。何を言えばいいのか、何をすればいいのか、まったくわからない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1249
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_e4f87d84:

    # ha "Go! Leave me alone! Get out of here!" with vpunch
    ha "帰って！　一人にして！　出て行って！" with vpunch

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1251
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_7dcf1fb5:

    # "I take a step back, then another, and then another. My retreat is only halted when I feel the door against my back."
    "俺は一歩後ずさる。もう一歩、また一歩。背中にドアが当たったのを感じてようやく後退を止める。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1253
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_e93fa870:

    # "I can't fix this situation. Nothing I say would change anything, now. I feel like I'm in a strange and deeply unsettling foreign world. I don't want to be here any more."
    "俺にはこの状況を変えることはできない。もう何を言っても何も変わらない。俺は自分が見知らぬ非常に落ち着かない別世界に入ってしまったような感覚をおぼえる。これ以上ここにいたくない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1255
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_118dcab7:

    # "The door handle fights my clumsy attempts to open the door without turning my back to Hanako. Eventually, thankfully, the handle moves downwards. I open the door as fast as I can and almost leap backwards through it."
    "華子に背を向けずにドアを開けようとする俺のぎこちない手の動きを取っ手が跳ね返してくる。やがて幸運にも取っ手が下に動く。大急ぎでドアを開けて、ほとんど後ろ向きに飛び込むようにドアを抜ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1257
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_36cb012c:

    # "As I go through, I keep my eyes on the girl in front of me."
    "ドアをくぐるときも、目の前の華子を見続けたまま。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1259
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_3617444a:

    # "She's not broken. Hanako isn't broken. If she was broken, then I'm just as broken as she is after all that's happened to me. Lilly only ever did the best by her, and I only ever tried to protect her as best I could."
    "壊れてない。華子は壊れていない。もし彼女が壊れているというのなら、今まで俺に起こったことを考えれば自分だって同じくらい壊れている。 リリーはずっと最善だけを尽くし続けてきたし、俺も華子を守るために全力を尽くしてきた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1265
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_f1d2f040:

    # "Hanako looks down, all her energy spent. Now that I've stepped out of her room, the worst of her fury is gone."
    "華子はすべての気力を使い尽くして元気をなくしているように見える。俺が華子の部屋から出たことで、最高潮の怒りはもう消えた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1267
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_6f04d72c:

    # "But even now, I can't bring myself to argue with her. It's not just the deep shock at what she said… it feels like something else is stopping me. Something deep, that makes me feel physically sick."
    "ただそれでも、華子と議論する気にはなれない。華子が言ったことへのショックが大きかっただけじゃない……何か別のものが俺を引き止めている気がする。何か深い、肉体的に俺を蝕むものが。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1285
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_f139efb8:

    # "Without a word, I slowly shut the door. The creak of the old hinges sounds almost deafening."
    "何も言わずに、俺はゆっくりとドアを閉める。古い蝶番のきしむ音が耳をつんざく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1294
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_45b511eb:

    # "With a final thud, the wooden door closes. The Hanako that I felt I knew disappears behind it, and only faint orange slivers of light peek around the very edges."
    "最後にバタンという音をたてて、木製のドアが閉まる。その後ろで、俺が知った気になっていた華子は消えてしまった。ぼんやりとした橙色の銀光だけがドアのまさに縁のあたりからのぞいている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1299
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_68f66554:

    # "I feel numb. Without anything else to do, I begin the walk back to my dormitory room, mechanically placing one foot in front of the other while barely registering a thing around me."
    "もう何の感覚もない。他にすることもなく、自分の部屋へと歩き始める。機械的に交互に足を置きながら、自分の周りのものもかろうじて見えているだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1301
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_ce4e3cd4:

    # "My mind keeps ticking, questioning everything that I thought I knew about Hanako."
    "俺の頭は動き続け、華子について知ったつもりになっていたことを次から次へと疑い続ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1303
translate jp a4_hanako_misstep_7e1ef2f9:

    # "But one thing is not questioned; that shutting that door brought a close to more than that single visit."
    "だけど一つだけ疑っていないことがある。あのドアを閉めたときに終わったのは、華子へのこの一回の訪問だけではないということだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1317
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_2c25e4eb:

    # "After talking to Lilly at the end of the school day, I sat at my desk and looked out the window, idly watching students leaving the school building. Usually they left in groups, but even when they left alone, they'd say goodbye to their friends first."
    "学校の終わり際にリリーと話したあと、俺は机のところに座って、窓の外で校舎から出てくる生徒たちの様子をただ眺める。 だいたいは集団で帰っていたけど、一人で帰っている子でさえ、最初に友達に別れの挨拶をしてから帰っていた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1319
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_dea077ea:

    # "It's completely normal. Something that I would have missed completely, had it been any other day, because it's so mundane."
    "ごくごく普通の光景だ。とてもありふれていて、今日という日でなければ完全に見逃していたような光景。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1321
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_0dfd8b71:

    # "But it's also something Hanako has never had in the time that I've known her. As I stand outside of Hanako's door for the second time in as many days, that fact doesn't leave my mind."
    "でも華子がそんな光景の中にいたことは、華子と知り合ってから今まで一度たりともなかった。華子の部屋の前に立つのはこの二日間で二回目だけど、そのことが頭から離れない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1323
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_129aa6e9:

    # "I hold two plates in my hands. On each is… not exactly the most hearty of meals, but I want to be sure that Hanako is at least feeding herself. It may also be a way to gain a little leverage in getting her to let me in."
    "手にはお皿を２つ持っている。その上に乗っているのは……十分な量の食事とは言いがたいけど、華子が少なくともちゃんと食事を取っていることは確認したい。 それに、これがあればちょっとは華子が俺を中に入れてくれやすくなるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1325
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_ad54eaa1:

    # "Lilly and I have tried our best to be there for her. Ever since she broke down in class, I've dearly wanted to protect Hanako. Such a thing happening to her again, or even something worse, is something I don't want to think about."
    "リリーも俺も華子の力になれるよう全力を尽くしてきた。華子が学校で参ってしまったあの日からずっと、心から華子を守りたいと思っている。 華子の身にあんなことがまた起きたり、あるいはもっと悪いことが起きるなんていうのは、考えたくもないことだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1337
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_1cd442ca:

    # "The door gives a solid series of thuds as I knock on it while carefully propping up one plate on my other arm. I doubt Hanako will open it for me, so all I can really hope to accomplish is to attract her attention."
    "皿をもう片方の腕に慎重に乗せながらドアをノックすると、堅いコンコンという音が繰り返される。これで華子が開けてくれるとは思わない、つまり俺が本当に達成を望んでいるのは彼女の注意を引くことだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1339
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_74998cb8:

    # hi "'Evening, Hanako. It's just me."
    hi "こんばんは、華子。俺だよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1341
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_9e4b07bc:

    # "I pause for a moment to see if she will respond, but the fact that she doesn't isn't very surprising."
    "返事が返ってこないかと一瞬待つけど、何も返ってこないことには別に驚かない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1343
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_a2c4b844:

    # hi "I… I have some food for the both of us. Could I come in?"
    hi "ええと……二人分の食事を持ってきたんだ。入ってもいいかな？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1345
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_76770062:

    # "For what feels like a very long time, some muffled voices from the floor below are the only sound to be heard."
    "下の階からのくぐもった声しか聞こえない時間が、とても長く続くように感じる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1349
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_39e47e70:

    # "Then I can hear the sound of bare feet on the floor coming up to the door, and I have to stifle a sigh of relief as I hear the door's lock being worked."
    "やがて裸足で床を歩く音がドアに近づいてくるのが聞こえる。鍵が外される音を耳にして、俺は安堵の溜息をつきそうになるのを抑える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1357
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_c141a5f8:

    # "When Hanako opens the door, I look at her intently."
    "華子がドアを開けると、俺は彼女をじっと見つめる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1362
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_de2f5546:

    # "She looks up momentarily to the plate in my left hand. It's a modest curry dish I quickly made from a packet."
    "華子はすこしの間俺の左手にある皿を見上げる。レトルトから手早く作った質素なカレーだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1367
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_237050e0:

    # "Her eyes move to the plate in my right hand, which holds the same thing, before looking down again."
    "華子は続いて右手の皿に目を向ける。そっちにも同じものが乗っているのを見て、またうつむく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1372
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_3c628e77:

    # "As she shuffles back into her room, I realize that I haven't said a word to her. I glumly follow her in, slightly embarrassed by having been so wrapped up in observing her."
    "華子がすり足で部屋の中へ戻っていくなか、俺は華子に一言も声をかけていないことに気づく。華子を観察することに夢中だった自分に少し恥ずかしくなりながら、うなだれてその後についていく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1387
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_6b032d30:

    # "More than ever, the gray and stark atmosphere of Hanako's room feels like a reflection of her personality. The voices from outside become completely inaudible, and the silence inside oppressive, once I close the door."
    "これまで以上に、華子の部屋の灰色で殺風景な雰囲気は華子の人となりを反映しているように感じられる。ドアを閉めると外からの声はまったく聞こえなくなり、静寂が押し寄せる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1389
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_74c805d7:

    # "Walking to the far end of the room, I place the two plates on her desk. I'm thankful that she let me in, but as I turn to face her, I can't help having second thoughts about coming to see her."
    "部屋の突き当りまで歩いていくと、俺は２つの皿を机の上に置く。部屋に入れてくれたことには感謝しながらも、華子に向き直ると、会いに来てよかったのだろうかと考えずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1396
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_fcfd7490:

    # "I don't believe Lilly was right, though. Looking at Hanako like this, I can only think that giving her space is the last thing we should be doing. I don't want to imagine it, but she may do something very foolish."
    "リリーが正しかったとは思えないけど。こうして華子を見ていると、彼女をそっとしておくというのは一番してはいけないことのようにしか思えない。 こんな想像はしたくないけど、華子がとても馬鹿な真似をしないとも限らない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1398
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_e55b5712:

    # hi "Um… it's just an instant meal, but it should be filling."
    hi "ええと……ただのインスタント食品だけど、お腹は膨れるはずだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1400
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_8a342a11:

    # "I take a plate in my hand, offering it to her. She wordlessly takes it and sits on the side of her bed. I take a seat in her chair, and the familiar sound of eating rings in the room as we dig in with the forks that were stuck into the rice."
    "皿を手に取って華子に差し出す。華子は黙ってそれを受け取るとベッドの端に腰掛ける。俺も椅子に座る。スプーンでご飯をすくって食べ始めると、耳慣れた食事の音が部屋に鳴り響く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1402
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_09b29675:

    # "The curry itself tastes… okay. I wouldn't expect much more from a packet whose brand I didn't recognize, so it not being horrible is at least something."
    "カレーの味は……まずくはない。聞いたこともないブランドのレトルトに大した期待はしてなかったし、ひどい味じゃないだけで儲けものだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1404
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_c4909d63:

    # "Eating takes the edge off the fact that she isn't talking. Neither of us really likes to talk while we're eating, and this reminds me of the lunchtimes we so often spent together."
    "食べていると華子が喋らないことも気にならない。俺たちは二人とも食事中に喋りたがるタイプじゃないから、こうしているとよく一緒に過ごした昼休みを思い出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1406
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_aac73a85:

    # hi "It's kind of nice, eating together like this."
    hi "こうやって一緒に食べるのっていいな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1411
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_936df2c2:

    # "Hanako looks at me quizzically. It's at least a better expression than what she's been wearing this far."
    "華子はいぶかしげに俺を見る。それは少なくとも、今までずっと浮かべていた表情よりはよほどいい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1413
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_7c859c45:

    # hi "We became friends mainly over sharing lunch breaks, so it's nice to go back to those times a bit."
    hi "俺たち、主に一緒に昼休みを過ごすことで友達になったからさ。ちょっと昔を思い出すのはいいもんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1415
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_7ecdf754:

    # "She hesitates for a couple of seconds, and I find myself grimacing. Did I say something wrong?"
    "華子は少しもじもじして、俺はつい渋い顔になってしまう。何か悪いことを言ってしまったか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1420
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_cf3c810d:

    # "Eventually she smiles and nods. I would normally be very encouraged by this, but her smile looks strange. I can't quite put my finger on why."
    "やがて華子は微笑んでうなずく。いつもならとても自信がもらえる仕草だけど、華子の笑顔は妙だ。だけどどうおかしいのかはよくわからない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1422
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_5214e760:

    # ha "Everything's… the same as before, isn't it?"
    ha "なにもかも……前といっしょ、だね？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1424
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_38a8f8c2:

    # hi "Y-yeah. Of course it is."
    hi "あ、ああ。もちろんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1426
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_7dee560c:

    # hi "You've still got Lilly and me to help you and protect you, and once she gets back, everything will be just like she never left."
    hi "俺もリリーも華子の味方なんだ。リリーが帰ってきたら、いなかったことなんてなかったみたいになるさ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1431
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_6dbb5694:

    # "Hanako nods again, her expression remaining exactly the same as before. She feels like a different Hanako from the one I'd first seen when I entered her room, and it's vaguely off-putting."
    "華子はさっきとまったく同じ表情で、もう一度うなずく。この部屋に入ったときに見た華子とは別人のように思えて、なにか嫌な感じだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1433
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_5da23830:

    # "Both of us go back to finishing off our dinners after the short exchange. Despite Hanako looking happier than before, my eyes keep flicking to her as if to reassure myself of this fact."
    "そんな短い会話の後、俺たちは食事を終わらせにかかる。華子はさっきより幸せそうに見えるのに、俺の目はチラチラと華子のほうを見ることを繰り返す。まるでその事を何度も確認するように。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1435
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_df28061e:

    # "Before long, the last of Hanako's curry is cleared. I finish the last of mine as she puts the empty plate on the desk, and place my own empty plate and used fork on top of hers."
    "間もなく、華子はカレーの最後の一口を食べ終える。華子が空になった皿を机の上に置くころ、俺も食べ終える。空になった皿と使ったスプーンを華子の皿の上に重ねて置く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1437
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_46e833fd:

    # "I briefly wonder what I should say, desperately wanting to avoid another awkward silence or the prospect of leaving her room after so short a time, but Hanako is the one to speak up first."
    "気まずい沈黙に陥ることもすぐに華子の部屋を出ていくことも非常に避けたくて、何を言うべきかすこし考えるけど、先に口を開いたのは華子だった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1442
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_d7372a3c:

    # ha "I… I was wondering… since y-you're here…"
    ha "ひ……久夫くんがきてるし……せっかくだから……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1444
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_ef669656:

    # "She quickly goes to one of her drawers, and after a minimum of fussing around, pulls out her chessboard."
    "華子はすぐにたんすに向かって、ほんの少し引き出しを漁るとチェスボードを取り出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1449
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_55161faf:

    # ha "W-would you… like to play…?"
    ha "よ、よかったら……やろう……？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1451
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_a7f4ec6e:

    # "This time, I can't stifle the sigh of relief that escapes my lips."
    "今度は俺も、口から抜け出る安堵の溜息を抑えることができなかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1459
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_c8264813:

    # "I hastily agree, and Hanako promptly busies herself setting up while I get off the chair and take a seat on her bed."
    "俺があわてて承諾すると、華子はそそくさと対局の準備をはじめる。俺は椅子から降りてベッドに腰掛ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1461
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_1c259584:

    # "Once again, Hanako is willing to let me into her world, with so simple a gesture as a game shared between us. I guess I was just winding myself up for no reason."
    "もう一度、華子は俺を自分の世界に入れてくれようとしている。ゲームを共有するという単純な表現で。俺は理由もなく緊張していただけなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1471
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_c3b6019a:

    # "After the board is laid down on the bed between us, we finish placing our respective pieces on it."
    "ベッドの上の、俺たちのあいだにチェスボードを寝かせると、それぞれの駒を並べ終える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1473
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_b49880ba:

    # "Throughout our friendship, we've never exchanged that many words. When we're like this, though, I see that perhaps we never really needed to. Just a simple book, or board, or meal between us is enough to bridge that distance."
    "俺たちは仲良くなって以来ずっと、あまり多くの言葉を交わしてこなかった。だけどこんな風にしていると、そもそも言葉なんて必要なかったのかもしれないと思う。 ただの本や、チェスボードや、食事があるだけで、俺たちの間の距離を埋めるには十分なんだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1475
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_303a9c76:

    # "I make the first move, just as I've always done. This is the way our friendship was, and this is the way it will probably always be."
    "これまでずっとそうだったように、俺が先手を取る。俺たちの関係はこうだったし、きっとこれからもずっとそうだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1477
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_25d41ec3:

    # "Something definitely feels different about her, though, and I can't quite grasp what it is. I look at Hanako intently, but I can't work out anything from her expression."
    "華子は何かがいつもと明らかに違う気がするけど、それが何なのかよくわからない。じっと華子を見つめてみても、その表情からは何も読み取ることができない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1479
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_0bcd1181:

    # "As physically close as we may be, it feels like we're further apart than ever. Hanako is a fragile person, though, and I would never want to hurt her."
    "こんなに近くにいるのに、今までになく遠く離れている気がする。でも華子はか弱い子で、俺は華子を絶対に傷つけたくはない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1481
translate jp a4_hanako_cut_petals_868e525d:

    # "That was also the way things always were, and the way things between us will probably always be."
    "今までもずっとそうだったし、これからもずっとそうなんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1499
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_52a0ceed:

    # "Since talking to Lilly yesterday, I've wanted to try and move on from the listlessness I've felt ever since coming to Yamaku."
    "昨日リリーと話してから、俺は山久にきて以来ずっと感じている無気力さを乗り越えて前へ進む努力をしたいと思っている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1501
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_f220ae2f:

    # "But even if I try to concentrate on the book in front of me, Hanako's empty seat at the back of the classroom looms larger than life. Every time I start getting focused, my eyes flick over to her desk again and my mind starts spinning."
    "でも目の前の本に集中しようとしても、教室の後ろの華子のいない席がいつもより大きな存在感をはなってくる。ちょっと集中してくるたびに、俺の視線はまた華子の机のほうへ向かい、思考が空回りしてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1506
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_0814bae0:

    # "Once more my eyes drift over to it, but this time my vision is blocked by a certain other classmate."
    "またしても俺の視線が漂うけど、今度はクラスメイトに視線を遮られる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1508
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_a4506935:

    # hi "Oh, hey Miki."
    hi "お、やあ美貴"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1513
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_1e5be698:

    # mk "Maybe you should just have lunch. I can hear your stomach growling from my desk."
    mk "お昼食べたほうがいいんじゃないかな。私の席までお腹の鳴る音が聞こえてくるよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1517
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_4987c405:

    # "I let my head drop in disappointment. She seems to take some amusement from my reaction, and hops up onto my desk. Her grin as she sits on it reminds me of the Cheshire Cat."
    "俺はがっくりとうなだれる。美貴は俺の反応を面白がってるようで、俺の机まで飛び跳ねてくる。にやつきながら机に腰掛けるさまはチェシャ猫を連想させる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1522
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_54b95408:

    # mk "So, whatcha' workin' on?"
    mk "で、何解いてるの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1524
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_ed4cf22b:

    # hi "Some math. I have a decent handle on it, but I just wanted to revise."
    hi "数学の問題だよ。数学はけっこうわかるんだけど復習しときたくてさ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1529
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_b8ee67ea:

    # mk "Oh really? Lemme see that."
    mk "へえそうなの？　見せてよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1531
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_4f247ded:

    # "Before I can object, she grabs my mathematics book with her hand. She scans the page I was on, holding it open with the one hand she has, her left arm sitting uselessly on her lap."
    "反論する間も与えずに、美貴は俺の数学の本を片手でつかみ取る。その手でページを開いたままにして俺が見ていたページに目を通していく。左腕は何もできずに膝の上でじっとしている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1533
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_c3da1179:

    # "In my time here at Yamaku, I've noticed that the other students have a wide range of adjustment to their disabilities, on a purely practical level. Miki is one of those who seem to have some trouble."
    "山久で過ごしていて、他の生徒たちはみんな自分の障害に対して、単なる実用面でもさまざまな適応の仕方をしていることに気づいた。美貴も障害を抱えている一人のようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1535
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_3eb66cd6:

    # "The stump of her left arm tends to be either hanging by her side, slipped into a pocket, or otherwise put out of the way. Sometimes she has a difficult time doing common tasks, which makes her visibly quite frustrated."
    "途中までしかない美貴の左腕は、脇でぶらぶらしているか、ポケットに突っ込まれているか、邪魔にならないようにしていることが多い。 時にはありふれた作業をするのに難儀してしまい、目に見えていら立っていることもある。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1537
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_64e4efff:

    # "I feel a little bad for thinking this way, but I'm thankful that Hanako and I don't have disabilities affecting our freedom of movement to that extent."
    "こんな風に考えるのはちょっと悪い気がするけど、華子や俺の障害は自分の体の動きをそこまで制限するようなものじゃなかったのはよかったなと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1539
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_4347a186:

    # "Then again… if Miki's problem worsened, at least she wouldn't have a real possibility of dying."
    "とはいえ……美貴の障害はたとえ悪くなったとしても、少なくとも本当に死ぬような危険性はないだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1544
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_bc52ec5f:

    # "My attention is refocused as she thumbs through a few pages, skimming their contents. With such casual interest in the subject matter, it's clear by now that she won't be any help."
    "美貴がページをぱらぱらとめくって中を見ているときに俺は我に返る。美貴はなんとなく見ているだけといった感じで、勉強の助けになりそうにないのはもう明らかだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1546
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_9b8fc2ca:

    # hi "I'm guessing you're not too interested in this stuff?"
    hi "あんまり興味なさそうだな？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1551
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_a887fb8e:

    # mk "Screw math. It's boring as hell."
    mk "数学だいっきらい。超つまんない"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1553
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_8a7ee205:

    # "She puts the book back in front of me with indifference. Her eyes move to the notebook beside it that I'd been working out practice equations on."
    "美貴は感慨もなく本を俺の目の前に返すと、その横にある俺が練習問題を解くのに使っていたノートに目を向ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1558
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_09ccb76a:

    # mk "Wait, you're actually able to work that stuff out?"
    mk "ん、待てよ。あんたこれ解けんの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1560
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "おう"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1565
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_f9e81de6:

    # mk "Wow. I've never talked to a computer with legs before."
    mk "おぉ。歩くコンピューターと話したのは初めてだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1567
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_11f13edf:

    # hi "Thanks… I think. At least I'm doing better in this than history."
    hi "ありがとう……なのかな。少なくとも数学のほうが歴史よりは得意だからな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1572
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_6673bd51:

    # mk "Think it's worth asking that librarian for help? I heard she's shooting for uni."
    mk "司書さんに手伝ってもらえないか聞くのもいいんじゃない？　大学でやりたいことがあるって聞いたよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1574
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_48c7616a:

    # hi "Ah, Yuuko? Maybe. I don't know what she wants to study, though."
    hi "ああ、優子さん？　いいかも。何を勉強しようとしてるのか知らないけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1576
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_5a2ff4b8:

    # hi "So what about you? Got anything you're thinking of doing after you graduate?"
    hi "美貴はどうなんだ？　卒業したあと何するか考えてるのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1581
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_0d1edcbe:

    # mk "Me? Nah, not really. Just enjoying it while it lasts."
    mk "私？　いや、特にないよ。今のうちに楽しんどこうって感じ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1583
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_2267ca93:

    # "She looks a little awkward when asked about her future, and absentmindedly rubs her left forearm. I kind of want to ask her about it, but I don't think I know her well enough to do so."
    "将来について聞かれた美貴は少し居心地が悪そうで、ぼんやりと腕をさすっている。もっと話を聞いてみたい気がするけど、そんなことができるほど美貴のことをよく知らないなと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1588
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_3c6693ea:

    # "The conversation peters out, and I lean back in my chair, giving up on the prospect of studying. Miki notices my tired expression and looks oddly serious."
    "会話が途絶えて、俺は勉強することを諦めながら椅子にもたれかかる。美貴は俺の疲れた表情に気づいて、妙に真剣な顔をする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1590
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_5799a0a3:

    # mk "Thinking about Hanako?"
    mk "華子ちゃんのこと考えてるの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1592
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_0a502455:

    # hi "It's that obvious?"
    hi "そんなにわかりやすいのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1597
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_a129ba47:

    # mk "You've been glancing at her seat, and you've been pretty quiet. Not too hard to connect the dots."
    mk "華子ちゃんの席をじっと見てたし、やけに静かだし。難しい推理じゃないねえ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1599
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_a68def8a:

    # hi "I'm just worried about her."
    hi "心配なだけだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1604
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_4659c606:

    # mk "Yeah, I can see why you would be. She can get… weird, sometimes."
    mk "うん、わかるよ。華子ちゃんは……時々変わったことをするしね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1606
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_bc37583f:

    # "She sounds put off, but I can't blame her. Hanako was a hard person to interact with before she warmed up to me, even with Lilly around to help. I haven't known her for that long either, so some of her habits would still be unknown to me."
    "不快そうに聞こえたけど、そのことでは美貴を責められない。俺だって華子が俺に慣れてくれるまでは、リリーの助力があっても話をするのが難しかった。 華子と俺はそんなに長い仲というわけでもないし、俺がまだ知らない習慣だってあるだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1608
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_4da8db55:

    # "My face becomes troubled. If I hadn't developed feelings for her, this would be at least a little easier to deal with."
    "俺は悩んだ顔をしてしまう。もし俺が華子を好きになっていなければ、少なくともこういう事に、もうちょっと対処しやすかったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1613
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_8dda896d:

    # mk "Ah, I mean, no offense. She isn't a bad person, I know that much."
    mk "ああ、その、そんなつもりじゃないの。悪い子じゃないってことはわかってるしね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1616
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_1c9bbcd7:

    # hi "I know, I didn't take it that way. It's just harder to deal with when, well, you know. You have feelings for someone."
    hi "わかってる、そういう風に捉えたわけじゃないんだ。なんていうか、ただ単にこういうことへの対処が難しくなるじゃない、好きな人がいるとさ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1621
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_887f040b:

    # mk "Yeah, I can imagine that. It's hard to forget something like what happened to her during class, too."
    mk "うん、そうだろうね。授業中にあんなことが華子ちゃんの身に起こって、それを忘れるのも難しいしね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1623
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_37e75ad6:

    # "I wish she hadn't reminded me of that. She just confirmed that it was clearly noticed by others in the room as well."
    "その事を思い出させないでくれたらよかったのにと思う。教室にいた他の生徒にもはっきりわかっていたんだと証明されてしまった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1628
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_f6d7fb07:

    # mk "Come on, don't get that down. She's done this before, you've just gotta wait it out."
    mk "ほら、そんなに落ち込まないの。前にもこんなことあったし、ただ待ってればいいのよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1630
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_3b334943:

    # "She locks herself in her room and acts like an empty husk of a person for a sizable amount of time, ever since she entered Yamaku if not before then as well, and I'm not supposed to be concerned about that?"
    "長い間部屋に閉じこもって抜け殻のように振る舞っている華子を、しかもそれが山久に入ってからも、そうでないなら山久に入る前からもあったことなのに、俺は心配するべきじゃないっていうのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1632
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_57a6c64a:

    # "Well, I might think that, but there's nothing that I can do. I can't force her to come out, and she does see a therapist, so it's not like she isn't getting any help for her issues."
    "まあ、そうは思っても俺に出来ることはなにもない。 無理やり外に連れ出すわけにもいかないし、華子はちゃんとカウンセラーの先生に診てもらってるんだから、華子は自分の問題に対して何の助けも得られていないわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1634
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_339dd762:

    # "Maybe it's natural to think that way when you're so powerless to help someone. 'That's just the way she is, and you just have to deal with it.'"
    "誰かを助ける力がないときに、そういう風に考えるのはごく自然なことなのかもしれない。『彼女はそういう人なんだし、それに折り合いをつけるしかない』。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1642
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_920a7cbb:

    # "As I mull things over, I notice a movement out of the corner of my eye. I glance to see who it is, and end up doing a doubletake."
    "いろいろと考えこんでいると、視界の隅で動くものに気づく。誰だろうと一瞥して、結局二度見してしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1651
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_360f6d45:

    # "Sure enough, it's Hanako. She walks through the door just as she would any normal school day, and begins to move towards her seat in her usual silent and humble manner."
    "確かに華子だ。普段と変わらない様子で教室のドアを通り抜けると、いつもの静かでつつましい姿勢で自分の席に向かっていく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1656
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_275fb6f9:

    # "She looks at me for a moment before blushing and looking away in embarrassment, which makes me realize that I was staring at her. I feel sorry for that, but not doing it is hard after all that's happened."
    "華子は俺を少し見ると顔を赤らめて恥ずかしそうに目をそらす。そこで俺は自分が華子を見つめていたことに気づく。すまないとは思うけど、今日までのことがあったのにそうしないというのも難しい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1667
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_a3571679:

    # "The girl sitting on my desk looks to me, grinning."
    "俺の机に座っている美貴がニヤついた顔を向けてくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1672
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_8b388f3f:

    # mk "See? Your sweetheart's back already. What did I tell ya?"
    mk "ほらね？　カノジョがもう帰ってきたじゃん。言ったとおりでしょ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1674
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_6fb5e1a2:

    # hi "You be quiet."
    hi "やかましいっ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1676
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_d63e647c:

    # "It might only be meant as a joke, but she hits close enough to make me quite uncomfortable."
    "ただの冗談なのかもしれないけど、なまじ外れてもいないだけに心穏やかではいられない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1681
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_9d6acdd5:

    # "As we talk, someone calls Miki's name from the door. She jumps down from her vantage point on my desk before turning to me."
    "話をしていると、誰かがドアのところから美貴の名前を呼ぶ。美貴は見晴らしのいい俺の机の上から飛び降りると、俺に向き直る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1686
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_eaacd3e8:

    # mk "Gotta go, Hisao. Remember to eat sometime, will ya?"
    mk "おっと行かないとね。ちゃんと食事はしなよ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1688
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_93781e82:

    # hi "Fine, I will. See you."
    hi "ああ、そうするよ。またな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1693
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_92519705:

    # "She gives a casual salute before jogging over to the door, where a male student in gym uniform is waiting for her. Probably someone from the track and field club."
    "美貴は軽く敬礼してからドアへ小走りで駆けていく。そこには体操服姿の男子生徒が美貴を待っている。陸上部の誰かだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1698
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_7ce7eb37:

    # "Seizing the opportunity, I get up and make my way to Hanako's desk."
    "ちょうどいいチャンスだ、俺は立ち上がると華子の席へ向かう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1705
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_ea305f45:

    # ha "H-hello…"
    ha "こ、こんにちは……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1707
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_c333ac03:

    # hi "Hi, Hanako. What's up?"
    hi "やあ、華子。元気か？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1712
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_631a96af:

    # ha "N-nothing…"
    ha "か、変わりないよ……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1714
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_f5ecee92:

    # "Maybe talking to her this soon after she came back to class was a bad move."
    "学校に戻ってきたばかりの華子にこんなにすぐ話しかけたのは間違いだったかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1716
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_83b84a5f:

    # hi "Want to go come with me and grab something from the cafeteria? I'm pretty hungry."
    hi "一緒に食堂行って何か食べないか？　お腹ペコペコでさ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1721
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_c8c223de:

    # ha "But… I thought you were studying."
    ha "でも……勉強してたんじゃ……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1723
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_31ab42e9:

    # "Studying can wait. Turning up for class after all this time must have taken some courage for Hanako, so the least I can do is stay with her."
    "勉強はいつでも出来る。これだけ時間が空いたあとに学校に出てくるには勇気が必要だったはずだし、今はせめて一緒にいてあげたい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1725
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_dff269d0:

    # "'That's just the way she is, and you just have to deal with it' is the way Miki, and probably the class as a whole, views Hanako. I can do more for her, though. I want to do more for her."
    "『彼女はそういう人なんだし、それに折り合いをつけるしかない』。それが美貴や、そしておそらくクラス全体の華子への見方だろう。だけど俺は華子のためにもっと何かしてあげられる。もっと何かしてあげたい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1727
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_fb15c6b5:

    # hi "After being distracted by Miki, I don't think I'm going to get any work done. Come on, let's go."
    hi "美貴に邪魔されちゃったし、もう勉強できる気がしないよ。ほら、行こうぜ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1732
translate jp a4_hanako_continuing_melody_24e61f88:

    # "She hesitates, but eventually gets up and joins me as we begin walking. These may be small steps for her, but the fact that she's finally out of her room of her own volition lifts a large weight off my shoulders."
    "華子はためらうけど、やがて立ち上がって俺と一緒に歩き始める。華子にとっては小さな一歩一歩かもしれないけど、華子が自分自身の意思でついに部屋の外に出てきてくれたことで、俺の肩から大きな荷が降りた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1750
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_b9daecb7:

    # "My pen busily scrawls onto a slowly filling page of my notebook. My other hand remains on the page of a reference book I borrowed from the library, marking my spot as my eyes flicker to and fro."
    "俺のペンがせわしなくノートの上を走って、少しずつページを埋めていく。もう片方の手は図書室で借りてきた参考書のページに留まって、目を動かすたびにどこまで進んだかを見失わないようにする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1752
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_a037bdcf:

    # "As I work, I occasionally mark red circles or underlines onto the photocopied sheets of paper that lie on the table in front of me."
    "勉強を進めながら、目の前のテーブルに乗せた資料のコピーにときどき赤丸や下線を引いていく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1754
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d5e4d053:

    # "Wanting a change of scenery from the library and to avoid the distractions of the classroom, I decided to make use of the Shanghai for some quiet study time."
    "図書室とは違う景色と、教室のように邪魔をされることもない場所を求めて、俺は静かに勉強できる時間を得るために上海を利用することに決めた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1756
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d43ee064:

    # "It ended up being nice and quiet as expected, and being able to get coffee while I study is a nice bonus."
    "上海は思った通りとても居心地がよく静かで、勉強しながらおまけにコーヒーまで飲める。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1758
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_a8e1e25c:

    # "Hanako may have returned to her normal self since she came out of her room, but I've done quite the opposite. Daily routine may have returned to us, but I feel as if I'm a different person."
    "華子は部屋から出てきてから元の華子に戻ったかもしれないけど、俺はまるで逆だ。俺たちの日常は戻ってきたかもしれないけど、自分は別人になったような気がする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1760
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_71c2b343:

    # "Maybe I'm not. It's only been a few days, after all, since I decided I wanted to try and get out of the rut I'd found myself in after my accident. But I want to change, and I'm now actively working towards that goal."
    "気のせいかもしれない。大体、俺が最初の発作のあと陥るようになった考え方から抜け出そうと決意してから、まだたったの数日だ。だけど俺は変わりたいし、その目標に向かって今も積極的に行動している。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1762
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_954a7848:

    # "Or at least, I would like to think that I am."
    "少なくとも、そうだと信じたい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1764
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_3a8d06e6:

    # hi "Ugh, this is impossible. Brute-forcing this isn't going to work."
    hi "うう、こんなの無理だろ。力押しじゃダメだあ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1766
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_150a0888:

    # "What's more, I have another piece of writing I have to do after this. I fear that's going to be no easier."
    "それに、この後にはもう１つ書かないといけない作文がある。これより楽な課題だとも思えない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1768
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_780939d2:

    # yu "Um…"
    yu "ええと……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1770
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_a62c8b08:

    # "I look up in mild surprise to the source of the tentative voice."
    "そのためらいがちな声の出どころに、少し驚いて顔を上げる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1775
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_569da7d3:

    # "Yuuko stands at the head of the table with a damp towel in hand, clearly having taken the opportunity to clean the tables while no other patrons were around. She looks curious, her eyes as much on my work as on me."
    "優子さんはテーブルの上座に立って、湿ったタオルを手に持っている。他に客がいない今のうちに、テーブルを拭こうとしているに違いない。優子さんの目は俺と俺の勉強道具に向いていて、何か聞きたそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1777
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_76b73413:

    # hi "What's the matter?"
    hi "何ですか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1782
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_23ac5c85:

    # yu "I was just wondering… what sort of work are you having so much trouble with?"
    yu "すごく苦労してるみたいだったから……何の勉強をしてるのかなあ？　と思って"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1784
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_509fb7ad:

    # hi "Oh. It's just history. I'm fine with science and math, so I'm trying to get my other subjects up to par."
    hi "ただの歴史ですよ。理科目と数学は大丈夫なんで、他の科目を底上げしようと思って"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1789
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_2e5c9ae4:

    # "Yuuko looks positively delighted at this development. I feel like I just chose the right answer on some big quiz show."
    "明らかに、優子さんはこの会話の流れを喜んでいるみたいだ。俺は大きなクイズ番組かなにかで正しい答えを選んだような気分になる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1794
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_f39ee648:

    # yu "Oh! I think I can help you with that!"
    yu "あっ！　それなら手伝えるかもしれない！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1799
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_7ba7d2d0:

    # yu "Um, if you don't mind… of course…"
    yu "あ、もしよければだけど……もちろん……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1801
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_241a0298:

    # "I briefly consider turning down the offer in order to not cause her too much trouble, but she looks too excited about this for me to do it. It would be mean to shoot her down like that, after such a reaction."
    "あまり迷惑をかけないように断ろうかともちょっと考えるけど、優子さんがとても乗り気なのを見るとそういうわけにもいかない。あんなリアクションを見せられて断るのは意地悪だろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1803
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_7e9f1b70:

    # hi "If you're willing to help, I'd really appreciate it."
    hi "手伝ってくれるなら本当にありがたいです"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1811
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_f470ca22:

    # "She claps her hands together and quickly deposits her towel on the counter, before returning and taking a seat across from me."
    "優子さんは手をポンと合わせると、さっとカウンターにタオルを置いてから戻って来て俺の向かいの席に腰掛ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1822
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_4aa75313:

    # "I take my notebook off the top of the textbook and hand it over for her to peruse."
    "教科書の上に乗っているノートをどけて、優子さんが調べられるように手渡す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1827
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_58748ca3:

    # yu "So you're studying the Edo Period?"
    yu "じゃあ江戸時代を勉強してるのね？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1829
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_c0d06b07:

    # hi "Yeah. I'm not really much good at this, though."
    hi "ええ。まああんまり得意じゃないんですが"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1834
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_132643f7:

    # "She takes the textbook and reads a few pages from a random section near the middle for a bit, but the aura of enthusiasm she'd been radiating previously is rapidly sapping away."
    "優子さんは教科書を手にとって、真ん中あたりの適当なところから数ページをしばらく読んでいるけど、さっきまで放っていた熱意のオーラは見る見るうちに弱まっていく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1836
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_6633f022:

    # hi "I'm guessing this isn't the kind of history you were expecting?"
    hi "思ってたのと違う分野でしたか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1841
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_fa0ee9b0:

    # yu "Unfortunately not. My main area is European history, especially in the classical era. Sorry."
    yu "残念だけど。私の分野はヨーロッパの歴史で、それも古代なの。ごめんなさい"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1843
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_49d119b0:

    # "She looks a bit downcast, but as she carefully closes the book and lays it back down on the table, her face perks up again."
    "優子さんは少しがっかりしたみたいだけど、丁寧に教科書を閉じてテーブルの上に置くと、また顔に元気が戻る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1848
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_9c6b5693:

    # yu "Would you like another cup of coffee?"
    yu "コーヒーのおかわりはいる？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1850
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_c981b4e9:

    # hi "Hmm? Oh, yeah, sure."
    hi "え？　ああ、はい。もちろんですよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1857
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_e6d4e131:

    # "I reach forward and get my book back as Yuuko gets up, takes my mug, and slowly walks to the counter to make another brew."
    "俺は前に手を伸ばして自分の教科書を手に戻す。優子さんは立ち上がると、俺のマグカップを手にゆっくりとカウンターに向かっておかわりを淹れる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1859
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_ce848246:

    # "As usual, she's absolutely silent as she does this; every ounce of her concentration is focused on not tripping over or dropping the plain white mug."
    "いつもの通り、そうしている間は優子さんは一言も口をきかない。集中力という集中力を、つまずいたりマグカップを落としたりしないことに注ぎ込んでいる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1861
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d0386228:

    # "I take the opportunity to lay back and relax for a bit, the hum of the coffee machine filling the otherwise quiet air."
    "ちょうどいいので俺もしばらく椅子に寄りかかってリラックスする。コーヒーメーカーの動く音だけが静かな空間を埋めていく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1863
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_becbbb3f:

    # "It's small details like that which make me realize how much I've come to appreciate the little things in life."
    "こういうほんの小さなことこそが、俺がどれだけ人生のささいなことに感謝するようになったかを実感させてくれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1865
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d2c04666:

    # "The peace and quiet of the local town, the discipline and order of Yamaku, the green of the trees that were so rare in my home city, the relaxed pace at which the aging residents live their lives…"
    "田舎の街の平和な静けさ、山久の規律と秩序、俺の生まれた街では珍しい木々の緑、お年寄りの住人たちのゆったりとした人生の送り方……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1867
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_e09e90f3:

    # "Everything feels so… certain. It's comforting."
    "すべてがとても……確かなものに思える。心が安らぐ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1869
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_86d39c81:

    # "I can feel myself beginning to nod off, when the sound of the mug coming to rest on the table grabs my attention. Seems like it arrived not a moment too soon."
    "自分がうとうとしているのを感じていると、テーブルにマグカップの置かれる音が俺の注意を引く。タイミングよくおかわりがきたようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1880
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_61ab9e54:

    # "Yuuko takes her previous seat once again as I pick myself up and bring a hand around the mug to check its temperature. It's just a little too hot to drink right away, so I blow on it a little."
    "優子さんはさっき座っていた場所にまた腰掛ける。俺は意識を立ち上げると、マグカップの周りに触れて温度を確かめる。すぐに飲むにはちょっとだけ熱すぎるみたいだから少し息を吹きかける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1885
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_66f0a16b:

    # yu "It's a shame you don't like history all that much. I sort of guessed you might be more into science."
    yu "中井くんが歴史をあまり好きじゃないのは残念だな。理科の方が好きなんだろうなってことはなんとなくわかってたけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1887
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_67df5e31:

    # hi "How so?"
    hi "どうしてです？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1892
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_644043b4:

    # yu "You've nearly read out the science fiction section of the library already. It wasn't hard to notice."
    yu "図書室のＳＦコーナーはほとんど読んじゃってるじゃない。すぐわかったよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1894
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_3211e2bf:

    # hi "You do have a good point, there. Well, what can I say? You've pegged me just about right."
    hi "それはもっともですね。もう返す言葉がないです。見事に言い当てられちゃったな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1899
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_3e926934:

    # hi "You sound like you really take an interest in history though, especially considering how specific you were about it. Do you study in that area, or something? Go on digs overseas?"
    hi "でも優子さんはほんとに歴史に興味があるんですね。特に、優子さんの分野がすごく具体的だったから。その分野を研究してるとかですか？　海外に発掘に行っちゃったり？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1904
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_f02a3f27:

    # "She giggles nervously at the thought."
    "それを聞くと、優子さんはそわそわしたように笑う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1909
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_f8f02a31:

    # yu "I'd like to visit the Mediterranean sometime and see the old architecture and art for myself, but I don't think I could trust myself to handle such delicate things."
    yu "いつか地中海に行って、建物や美術品を自分の目で見てみたいって思うな。でもそんな壊れやすいものをちゃんと扱えるほど、自分を信じられるとは思えないけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1914
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_2ffc4e53:

    # yu "I'm saving up to formally study it in university, although I also read up on it whenever I have free time outside of work."
    yu "ちゃんと大学で勉強するためにお金を溜めてるんだ。仕事がない自由時間はいつでも本で勉強したりもしてるけどね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1916
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_8d24b75e:

    # "So Miki was right about her university aspirations. Considering how she fares as a waitress, a more theoretical path may suit Yuuko better. It's nice to hear that she has some ambitions though, considering how hard she works."
    "優子さんの大学で学ぶという志について、美貴は正しかったってわけだ。優子さんのウェイトレスとしての仕事ぶりを考えると、もっと理論寄りの分野のほうが合っている気がする。 でもあんなにがんばって働いている優子さんが目標を持っているということを聞けてよかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1918
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_8e079b71:

    # "I nod and take a careful sip of my coffee. By now it's cooled to the right temperature, so I begin to drink while keeping an eye on the book below, trying to read at the same time."
    "俺はうなずいて、注意深くコーヒーをすする。もうちょうどいい温度に冷めているので、俺はコーヒーを飲み始め、同時に、本に視線を落としたまま読もうとする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1920
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d4155aed:

    # "A few minutes pass quietly, Yuuko looking out the window and watching the world go by while I have my coffee and study."
    "静かに数分が経つ。俺がコーヒーを飲みながら勉強をしているあいだ、優子さんは窓の外を見て、流れゆく世界を観察している。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1925
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_a5769200:

    # "A movement catches my eye, and I look up to see Yuuko smiling and waving to someone outside. Following her gaze surprisingly reveals the someone to be Hanako."
    "視界で何かが動いて、顔を上げると優子さんが笑顔で外の誰かに手を振っている。何事かと視線をたどると、驚いたことにその人物は華子だとわかる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1927
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_0174dab5:

    # "She is looking at us from the side of the street across from where we are. Her usually all-too-visible timidity is largely absent, probably thanks to there being so few people around right now."
    "華子は通りの向こうから俺たちを見ている。いつものあまりにもわかりやすい臆病さはほとんどない。たぶん今は周りにほとんど人がいないからだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1929
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_f41d5af8:

    # "Evidently she decides to join us, as after a little wave, she gives a quick glance up and down the street and crosses towards the side that the café is on."
    "どうやら俺たちに合流することに決めたらしい。小さく手を振り返してきたあと、通りの左右を確認して上海のあるほうへ道を渡ってくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1945
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_77b95aca:

    # "The familiar doorbell to the Shanghai rings out as Hanako enters and makes her way to the table we're sitting at."
    "聞き慣れた上海のドアベルが鳴り、華子は店に入ってくるとそのまま俺たちが座っているテーブルへやってくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1952
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_ea305f45:

    # ha "H-hello…"
    ha "こ、こんにちは……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1957
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_ae64a285:

    # yu "Good afternoon."
    yu "こんにちは"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1959
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_c333ac03:

    # hi "Hi, Hanako. What's up?"
    hi "やあ、華子。元気か？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1964
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_f07d696b:

    # ha "N-nothing… just… g-going for a walk… since the weather was nice."
    ha "か、変わりないよ……ちょっと……散歩しようと思って……天気がいいから"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1966
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_4c4fb449:

    # hi "Yeah, I get what you mean. I'm glad I decided to study here instead of the library."
    hi "ああ、わかるよ。俺も図書室じゃなくてここで勉強することにしてよかったなと思ってる"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1968
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_2035ff0c:

    # "It's comfortable in here thanks to that, better than the sometimes quite stuffy library. I look to Yuuko, who nods in response."
    "天気のおかげでここは居心地がいい。ときどき空気がよどんで蒸し暑くなる図書室よりも。優子さんのほうを見ると、うなずき返してくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1973
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_11d294ad:

    # yu "It's nice. It's just a shame that summer can't last forever."
    yu "いい天気だよね。夏がいつまでも続くわけじゃないのが残念だな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1978
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_59d74a38:

    # yu "Oh wait, sorry, um, would you like a drink?"
    yu "ああっ、ごめんなさい、えっと、飲み物はいかがですか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1986
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_a19646f9:

    # "Hanako shakes her head. Thankfully, it's enough to calm Yuuko back down."
    "華子は首を振る。それだけで優子さんは落ち着きを取り戻したみたいだ。よかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1991
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_5c77b1b3:

    # ha "H-how are you going with studying?"
    ha "べ、勉強はどう？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1993
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_58582b46:

    # hi "Okay… ish."
    hi "まあなんとか……かな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:1995
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_c1d3dea0:

    # hi "Oh yeah, have you talked with Lilly?"
    hi "あっそうだ、リリーとは話したか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2000
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_02f2cf23:

    # yu "I'm interested too; how is she doing?"
    yu "私も知りたいな。どうしてるの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2005
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_0e98cfa6:

    # ha "Sh-she's enjoying it… I think."
    ha "た、楽しく過ごしてるよ……たぶん"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2007
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_65f31615:

    # "I… think that's all we're going to get out of her. Being around Yuuko is tensing her up."
    "これ以上は……華子から話を引き出すことはできないだろう。優子さんがいることで硬くなっている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2012
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_65e6d1ab:

    # yu "Ah, it would be so nice to travel to Scotland."
    yu "ああ、スコットランドへの旅って良いでしょうねえ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2017
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_5e2f8160:

    # yu "Green fields, castles, lovely small towns, men in kilts, interesting history…"
    yu "草原に、お城に、素敵な小さい街々に、キルト衣装の男の人に、面白そうな歴史……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2019
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_f20de6b2:

    # "I can't say I see the appeal of men in kilts, myself. It does seem like a picturesque place, though."
    "俺にはキルト衣装の男の魅力はよくわからないけど、景色の素敵なところではあるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2027
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_3c25c99a:

    # "As we talk, the jingle of the doorbell rings again. Hanako is startled, noticing Yuuko's panicked expression at the prospect that she might leave customers to wait a handful of seconds, due to her chatter with us."
    "話を続けていると、ドアの鈴が再びチリンとなる。俺たちと話していたせいでお客様を何秒か待たせてしまうことになると分かってうろたえている優子さんの表情に、華子が驚いてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2037
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_904be0ff:

    # "Yuuko gives us a quick bow, then hastily skitters over and greets the new customers, an elderly man and his wife. I watch her for a bit, craning my head around to get a good view."
    "優子さんは俺たちにサッとお辞儀をすると、軽やかに店内を横切って新しいお客様に挨拶する。年配の夫婦だ。俺は見やすいように首を伸ばしてしばらくその様子を見ている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2042
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_58f9fc31:

    # "Hanako is staring at me with her one visible eye."
    "華子は隠れていないほうの目で俺をじっと見ている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2053
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_013d7b1d:

    # "She averts her head in embarrassment as I turn to make eye contact."
    "俺が目を合わせようと振り向くと華子は恥ずかしそうに顔をそらす。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2055
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_33936ecf:

    # hi "I was just thinking that it's nice to have ambitions for the future. Yuuko was telling me a little about her university aspirations before."
    hi "将来の目標を持つのっていいもんだなあと思ってたんだ。さっき優子さんが大学で成し遂げたいことがあるって話をちょっとしてくれたんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2060
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_2607fbcf:

    # ha "Oh."
    ha "そ、そう"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2062
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_b4252498:

    # hi "It's a shame. If she wasn't so neurotic and overworked, I think she could be a really happy person."
    hi "残念だよ。あんなに神経質で働き詰めじゃなければ、本当に明るい人になれそうなのにな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2064
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_70b7c0ce:

    # "As much as I'd like to play host to Hanako and entertain her a bit, I do need to study as well. To be honest, I don't think the distraction from Yuuko helped either."
    "華子の相手をしてちょっとでも楽しませてあげたいけど、勉強もしないといけない。正直なところ、優子さんとの雑談も役には立たなかったと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2066
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_3387aca4:

    # hi "Sorry if I'm a bit distracted. I need to try and get this done, otherwise I'm going to flunk the history exams pretty hard."
    hi "話を聞き逃してたらごめん。これやらなきゃいけないんだ。このままだと歴史の試験は完全に落第だよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2068
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_7ccf4fe6:

    # "I'm left running my hand through my hair in frustration. That letter needs doing as well, once I get back to my dormitory room."
    "イライラして頭をかきむしる。寮に帰ったら、あの手紙もなんとかしないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2070
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d6a06af8:

    # hi "I hope I have more luck with that than this. Damn."
    hi "あっちは上手くいけばいいんだけど。くそっ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2075
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_74a2b215:

    # ha "W-what with?"
    ha "な、なにが？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2077
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_fd910d8b:

    # hi "Oh, uh… I was going to… write to Iwanako. Right now though, this is more important."
    hi "うっ、いや……後で俺……岩魚子に手紙を書かないといけないんだ。今はこっちのほうが大事だけどな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2079
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_7e583630:

    # "All I've done is rattle myself. I can't focus on the work in front of me when my stomach is slowly turning at the prospect of actually attempting to write her back, after all this time."
    "俺がやったことはただ自分を慌てさせただけだ。これが終わったら本当に岩魚子に返事を書かないといけないと思うと、胃がじわじわと痛んで目の前の勉強に集中できない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2081
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_9f78d6a1:

    # "I force myself to concentrate on the book, picking up my pen once I have a quick sip of coffee."
    "俺は無理やり教科書に集中する。コーヒーを素早く一口飲むと、すぐにペンを手に取る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2086
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_935d0a3c:

    # "After a few seconds, Hanako stops silently watching me and leans back in her seat, relaxing as much as she ever seems to be able to, looking out the window to pass the time."
    "数秒後には、華子は俺を黙って見つめることをやめて背もたれに体を預ける。華子にできる範囲で力を抜いて、窓の外を眺めて過ごす。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2091
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_cc14ce3c:

    # "We stay like this for a long time before leaving for the dormitories together. I'm surprised she had the patience to wait me out."
    "そんな感じで長い時間を過ごしてから、一緒に寮へ帰る。ずっと俺を待ってくれていた華子の辛抱強さには驚いた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2098
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_c378b340:

    # "Iwanako's letter lies on my desk beside a blank sheet of lined paper and an unused envelope. The tapping of my pen is the only thing to be heard this late at night."
    "机の上には岩魚子の手紙、その横には何も書かれていない罫線の入った紙と未使用の封筒がある。もう夜も遅く、自分のペンをコツコツと机に当てる音しか聞こえない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2100
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_fdd99b27:

    # "As I feared, my second task for the day turns out to be just as difficult as the first, if not harder."
    "俺が恐れたとおり、本日二つ目の仕事は一つ目の仕事と同じくらい、あるいはそれ以上に難しかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2102
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_2ebe338a:

    # "It's been so many months since we even saw each other. Even so, I can still remember what she looked like, what she sounded like, and what she acted like. By now, though, the little details are beginning to slip away."
    "最後に会ったときから何ヶ月も経っている。とはいえ岩魚子がどんな顔をしていたか、どんな声をしていたか、どんな風に振る舞っていたかはまだ思い出せる。だけどもう、細かい記憶は消え始めていた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2104
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_8e5e3ab1:

    # "When I first saw her letter, I barely recognized her handwriting at all. Even the pink pen she always used was forgotten until her writing reminded me of it."
    "最初にこの手紙を見た時、岩魚子の筆跡がどうだったかほとんど思い出せなかった。岩魚子がいつも使っていたピンクのペンのことでさえ、岩魚子の字を見てようやく思い出せた始末だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2106
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_1864c04d:

    # "I wonder why she didn't use it for the letter; she used to write everything with it. Maybe she thinks it's too immature now."
    "どうしてこの手紙にはあのペンを使わなかったんだろうか。岩魚子は何でもピンクのペンで書いていた。もう子供っぽいと思うようになったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2108
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d756a84f:

    # "I should be thinking about myself, and about what I want to communicate to her. My mind can't stop concentrating on her, though. On the past we shared before it was taken away so suddenly."
    "俺は自分のことと自分が何を伝えたいのかを考えているべきだ。なのに俺の頭は岩魚子のことや、突然に奪われる前に共有していた過去のことばかりを考えている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2110
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_1e6d303a:

    # "The bright and slightly garish decorations suit her sense of aesthetics. Picking up the letter to take a closer look at it, I give a long sigh."
    "この明るくてちょっとゴテゴテとした手紙の装飾は、岩魚子のセンスに合ってる。手紙を持ち上げてよく観察すると、俺は長い溜息をつく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2112
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_b8421ebe:

    # "This is the last link binding me to my past. Iwanako didn't suddenly cease to exist when she left my hospital room for the last time, but I needed this letter to remind me of that."
    "これは俺と俺の過去をつなぐ最後のつながりだ。岩魚子は別に最後に俺の病室を去っていったときに急に存在しなくなったわけじゃない。だけどそのことを思い出すのにもこの手紙がなくてはならなかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2114
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_63068315:

    # "I had all those feelings neatly filed away. I felt as if I didn't need them, that I could just begin life completely anew. It was easier that way."
    "俺はこれまでこういう気持ちをきれいにしまい込んでいた。こんなものは必要がないというかのように、完全に新しい人生を始めることができるのだと感じていた。そのほうが楽だったからだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2116
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_c52ec2ef:

    # "In the end, I suppose that was a rather naive thing to think. Sooner or later, my past would have caught up with me one way or the other."
    "結局それはかなりナイーブな考えだったんだろう。遅かれ早かれ、俺の過去の影は何らかの形で俺に追いついてくるんだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2118
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d1389b0d:

    # "But what am I supposed to say to her? 'Thank you for bringing me closure?' All the letter did was end the sense of closure I'd previously felt."
    "でも岩魚子に何を言えばいいっていうんだ？　『終わらせてくれてありがとう』？　この手紙が果たしたのは、俺が既に感じていた終わったんだという気持ちを確かなものにしただけにすぎない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2120
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_afd398a9:

    # "Try as I might, I can't write so much as a single word down on the paper in front of me. I can't even think of what exactly I want to say."
    "どう頑張っても、目の前の手紙にほんの一言書くことすらできない。俺が正確に何を言いたいのかも思いつかない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2127
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_e31a81f3:

    # "Putting the letter down on top of the blank sheet, I gather the materials together and file them away in my drawer."
    "白紙の上に手紙を乗せると、紙束をまとめて引き出しにしまい込む。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2129
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_7344c151:

    # "The clunk the desk makes as it closes makes me momentarily tense in frustration, before I get up to go grab a drink from the vending machine on the first floor."
    "引き出しを閉めたときのガタンという音が、俺の体をいらつきで一瞬こわばらせる。俺は立ち上がると１階の自動販売機に飲み物を買いに行く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2134
translate jp a4_hanako_shanghai_studiousness_d2b77be4:

    # "I tried, but I couldn't do it. After all the time that's passed, I still don't know how to deal with Iwanako."
    "頑張ってみたけど、だめだった。これだけ時間が経ってしまったのに、俺はいまだに岩魚子にどう接していいのかわからない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2150
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_0901c9d9:

    # "The library, while not humming with activity, is noticeably more busy than usual. Exams are not far away, and that's reflected in the number of students burying their noses in textbooks at the tables around us."
    "図書室は大盛況とまではいかなくとも、明らかにいつもより人が多い。試験も遠くないから、俺たちの周りで机に向かって教科書に鼻をうずめている生徒達の数が増えている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2152
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_d7d9ae78:

    # "I've been studying quite a lot in the past few days, just like them, in hope of doing well in the exams. This also means that Hanako and I have been playing games less, so she's begun studying as well just to fill in the time."
    "俺自身も同じように、試験でいい点を取ろうとここ数日は勉強漬けだ。それは華子とチェスをする回数が減っているということでもあり、その時間を埋めるために華子も勉強を始めた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2154
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_7be379cd:

    # "Nevertheless, I've found myself forsaken by her on this particular day."
    "何にせよ、今日は華子に見捨てられてしまったようだった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2156
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_383ef1a7:

    # "The textbook in front of me has remained on the same page for some time. After so much reading on subjects I couldn't care less about if not for the exams, my mind is beginning to wander."
    "目の前の教科書のページはしばらくめくられていない。試験さえなければ興味などかけらもないものを読み続けた俺の頭はついに別のことを考え始めている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2158
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_d7392098:

    # "I find my eyes flicking over to where Hanako would usually be, just like on the days she wasn't in class. Her usual beanbag in the corner of the room is conspicuously unoccupied."
    "ちょうど華子が学校を休んでいた頃にしていたように、華子がいつもいる場所に目を動かしている自分に気づく。華子がいつも使っているクッションは、部屋の隅で誰にも使われていないのが明らかだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2160
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_53b974d6:

    # "It was here that we first really met. I tried to start a conversation with her, she got skittish, and eventually bolted from the room altogether."
    "俺たちが最初にちゃんと出会ったのはここだった。俺が話しかけようとしたら華子は驚いてしまって、やがてものすごい勢いで逃げていった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2162
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_f7a9670a:

    # "I probably shouldn't smile about it, but it was kind of amusing, in hindsight. Nowadays, it's more and more difficult to imagine her doing such a thing. Even with Lilly gone, she's been doing well now that she's come out of her room."
    "多分それは笑ってはいけないことだけど、今思うとなんだか面白かった。もう今では華子がそんなことをしてしまう姿はどんどん想像できなくなっている。 最近はリリーがいなくてもちゃんとやっているし、部屋からも出てきてくれた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2164
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_2e51e362:

    # "I want to talk with her, or at least play another game of chess. I'm tired of studying, and it's been a few days since we've really done anything together."
    "華子と話したい。そうじゃなくても、チェスをやるくらいはしたい。勉強に嫌気が差してきたし、最後に一緒に何かをしたのはもう何日も前のことだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2166
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_7c577864:

    # "The question of where to find Hanako isn't a particularly difficult one. If she's not in the library, chances are that she's either in the tearoom for some peace and quiet, or in her dormitory room."
    "華子がどこにいるか当てるのはそれほど難しくない。図書室にいないなら、紅茶の部屋で休んでいるか、寮の部屋にいるかだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2168
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_d31aae24:

    # "Deciding to check them in that order, I pack up my books and make my way out of the library."
    "俺は順番にチェックしていくことに決めて、本をまとめあげると図書室を出る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2175
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_a704bd90:

    # "I stretch and give a loud groan as I walk down the hallway. Studying may be frustrating at times, but with the progress I feel I've made, there is also some sense of pride in getting it done. It's a good feeling."
    "廊下を歩きながら大きな声でうめいて伸びをする。勉強しているとストレスが溜まることもあるかもしれないけど、最近はその成果が出ている気がして達成感もある。いい気分だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2182
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_f422f5bc:

    # "There isn't a sound to be heard from inside as I stand in front of the door to Hanako's room. I guess that isn't very indicative of whether she's inside or not, given how quiet she usually is."
    "華子の部屋の前に立ってみても中からは何の音もしない。だけど華子が普段どれだけ静かな人間かを考えると、華子が中にいるかどうかの判断材料にはあまりならないと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2184
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_d996d3fd:

    # "Still, she wasn't in the tearoom. I try knocking lightly to make my presence known, but am surprised when I find the door unlocked and yielding at my touch."
    "それでも、華子は紅茶部屋にはいなかった。自分がここにいることを知らせようとドアを軽くノックしてみる。でも鍵はかかっていなくて、ノックに押されてドアが開いたので驚いてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2203
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_bdee4d9b:

    # "With a small creak, the door opens. It looks like my suspicions were correct; Hanako is indeed here. "
    "小さく軋む音をたててドアが開く。どうやら俺の推測は当たっていたらしい。華子は確かにそこにいた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2205
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_5253d86b:

    # "She's sitting at the table with an open book in front of her, but pays it no heed as she keeps looking out the window. She looks utterly oblivious to my presence."
    "華子は目の前のテーブルに本を開いて座っているが、読もうとせずに窓の外を見続けている。俺にもまったく気がついていないようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2207
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_0a8e8a0b:

    # "With her head thoughtfully resting on her hand, she looks calm and collected. It's a shame she can't look like this more often."
    "なにか考えこむように頬杖をついているけれど、よく落ち着いているように見える。華子がいつもこんな表情をしていないのが残念だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2214
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_6eee94ab:

    # "Smiling a little, I walk up to the table and softly speak to her."
    "俺は少し微笑んで、テーブルのところまで歩き進んで優しく話しかける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2216
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_932eac6f:

    # hi "Good evening, Hanako."
    hi "やあ、華子"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2221
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_2f696630:

    # "Hanako's head turns a little to see me, but she's still only half there. I put a hand on the table and lower my head to better look at her face, mildly curious about what mood she's in."
    "華子は俺のほうに少し顔を向けるけど、途中で止まる。どんな表情をしているのか少し気になった俺は、テーブルに手をついて華子の顔を覗き込もうとする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2223
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_3156ccff:

    # hi "What's up?"
    hi "どうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2228
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_ffecea56:

    # "She gasps a little, finally acknowledging my presence in the room for the first time."
    "華子は小さくハッとすると、ようやく今俺がいることに気がついたようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2230
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_480ceeb7:

    # "Hanako's blushing really heavily. Her mouth is open just a little, as if paused midsentence. Most striking, though, is what she's doing."
    "華子の顔がカッと赤くなる。何かを言おうとしたみたいに、口を少しだけ開けている。なにより印象的なのは、華子のしていることだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2238
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_db2677a8:

    # "She's looking directly at me. Her eyes are pinned on my own, from such a close distance that I can almost see my reflection in them. They don't turn away, nor move at all. They're absolutely still, just looking into mine."
    "俺をまっすぐ見つめていて、その目は俺の目に釘付けになっている。華子の目に俺の目が映っているのが見えそうなくらいの近さだ。目をそらさないし、ぴくりとも動かさない。ただ静かに俺の目を見つめている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2240
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_58ee49e4:

    # "They're dark, and give her an almost analytical air. Even when reading on subjects she has no interest in, she would appear to be rapt in her work to a casual observer. She absorbs information very well, and even now, I can feel that."
    "真っ黒な目が華子に分析的な雰囲気を与えている。華子は全く興味がないものを読んでいる時でも、事情を知らない人が見れば熱中しているように見えるだろう。 華子は情報をとてもうまく吸収する。今でさえそれが感じられる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2242
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_e2ef30c2:

    # "I feel like I'm seeing something behind those eyes that I never saw before. I don't know what it is, though."
    "その目の奥には今まで見たことがないものがあるような気がする。それがなんなのかはわからないけど。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2244
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_1b02d6e2:

    # hi "Hanako…?"
    hi "華子……?"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2246
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_e289dbcf:

    # "Her lips move just a little, silently mouthing something. She looks like she's on the verge of saying something, but won't say it."
    "華子の唇が少し動いて、声を出さずに何かを喋っている。華子は何かを言おうとしているみたいだけど、何も言わない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2248
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_99b5eea8:

    # "But that's the way Hanako always is. On the verge of saying something, but never quite doing it. As I look intently into her eyes, I realize something."
    "でも華子はいつもそうだ。何かを言おうとするけど、必ずしも言うとは限らない。華子の目をじっと見つめているうちに、ふと気づく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2250
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_b8bce7a7:

    # "Everyone has their own thoughts, things they want to say, their own worldview. But I can't work out what Hanako wants to say, and I can't work out what she's thinking. I never have been able to."
    "誰にだって自分の考えがあり、言いたいことがあり、物の見方がある。でも華子の言いたいことが俺はわからないし、華子の考えていることが俺はわからない。これまでもわかったことは一度もなかった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2252
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_0f1a1942:

    # "It's frustrating. It feels like I don't know her at all, despite all the time we've spent together."
    "もどかしい気分だ。あれだけ一緒に過ごしても、まるで自分が華子のことをまったく知らないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2254
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_dacc51a3:

    # ha "Hi… sao…"
    ha "久夫……くん……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2262
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_ad590b24:

    # "It's only now that I find myself blushing. I've been looking directly into Hanako's eyes from such a short distance with absolutely no regard for her, and she's been looking into mine without shirking away."
    "俺はようやく自分の顔が赤くなっていることに気づく。なんの気遣いもなく、こんなに近くで華子の目をじっと見つめていた。そして華子も逃げることなく俺と目を合わせ続けていた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2267
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_c1880347:

    # "I quickly look away while covering my face with my hand. Hanako does just the same."
    "すぐさま俺が顔を手で覆いながら顔を背けると、華子も同じことをする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2269
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_216f1072:

    # "Another awkward silence reigns. I hate these. At first I accepted them as just being a fact of life around Hanako, but now all they feel like is an affirmation of how little we're able to communicate."
    "またしても気まずい沈黙が落ちる。まったく嫌になる。 最初は俺も華子の周りではこれが普通なんだと受け入れていた。でも今では、俺たち二人があまりにもコミュニケーションができないという証にしか感じられない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2271
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_1c3ba21d:

    # "Some anger makes its way in the complex mixture of emotions I'm experiencing right now. I want to bridge that gap between us. Friends shouldn't have to tiptoe around each other like this."
    "今感じている複雑な感情の中で怒りが首をもたげてくる。俺は華子との間にある溝を埋めたい。友達は友達の周りでこんな風にびくびくするものじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2273
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_388b4488:

    # "I speak before I can argue myself out of what I'm going to do. My scarring isn't as bad as Hanako's, and I can't possibly compare my life to hers, but I want to show her that she's not alone."
    "俺は思いとどまることができずに喋り始める。俺の傷は華子ほど大きくないし、自分の人生と華子の人生を比較なんてできるものじゃない。だけど華子が一人ではないということくらいは教えてあげたい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2275
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_0344820f:

    # "Doing this in such a blunt manner might be the only way to get my point across."
    "遠慮せずに言うことでしか、俺の言いたいことを伝えることはできない気がする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2277
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_545138d5:

    # hi "Hanako… I want to show you something."
    hi "華子……お前に見せたいものがあるんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2282
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_f7884a4a:

    # "I take a deep breath to prepare myself. This could backfire badly, but I feel as if we've come close enough for this to be okay."
    "深く息を吸って心の準備をする。完全に裏目に出るかもしれないけど、これぐらいしても大丈夫なくらい親しくなったような気はする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2284
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_40240627:

    # hi "I'm not going to strip naked or anything weird, I'm just going to take off my shirt."
    hi "これからやるのはストリップとかそういう変なことじゃないぞ。シャツを脱ぐだけだからな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2289
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_fd67ab8a:

    # "Hanako's eyes grow to the size of saucers. Her face is an amusing mixture of curiosity and nervousness as she stands. It helps take the edge off my own nervousness at doing this in front of another person."
    "華子の目が皿のように大きくなる。立ち上がる華子の顔は好奇心と緊張が入り混じっていて面白い。そのおかげで人前でこんなことをすることへの緊張がやわらぐ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2293
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_6cc332e7:

    # "Slowly, with my entire body feeling tense, I unknot my tie and begin to loose the first of the buttons. I'm trying to mentally block out Hanako to make this easier, but it's not really working."
    "体中を緊張させたまま、ゆっくりとネクタイを解くと最初のボタンを外す。やりにくいから華子のことを意識しないようにしようとするけど、あまり効果はない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2295
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_a8286013:

    # "As I work my way down, I expect to hear some form of protest from her. She remains silent, though, which just makes this feel even stranger."
    "上から下へボタンを外していきながら、華子も止めようとしてくるだろうと思う。だけど華子は黙ったままで、よけいに今の状況が奇妙に感じる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2297
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_f18aac13:

    # "With the last of my shirt unbuttoned, I take a breath and look at her."
    "シャツのボタンをすべて外し終わると、息を吸って華子を見る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2305
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_6bafab3c:

    # "Hanako's gaze is fixed on my scarring, as expected, and once I nod to say it's okay, she steps forward and tentatively places her hand on the vertical line running down my chest."
    "思ったとおり、華子の目は俺の傷に釘付けになっている。俺が大丈夫だという風にうなずくと、華子は俺に近づいてきて俺の胸を縦に走る線におそるおそる手をやる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2310
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_79fbc48a:

    # "The scarring on her hand, a pattern of damaged skin across its surface, contrasts with the single uniform line that makes up mine. Her hand isn't trembling at all, unlike what I predicted."
    "華子の手の傷ついた皮膚がおりなす模様は、俺の胸の均一な線とは対照的だ。意外なことに、華子の手はまったく震えていない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2312
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_ef3ef292:

    # ha "This is…"
    ha "これって……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2314
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_8edd8ed5:

    # hi "The scar from the surgery that followed my heart attack. The surgeons had to cut open my chest to operate on my heart."
    hi "心臓発作のあと手術をして出来た傷だよ。医者が俺の心臓を手術するために胸を切る必要があったんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2319
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_b84c8b2a:

    # ha "I never knew…"
    ha "知らなかった……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2321
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_3554d417:

    # "Hanako's words are calmer and softer than usual. The soft feeling of her fingers moving from my scar to my breast makes me hesitate a little before continuing on."
    "華子の言葉はいつもより落ち着いていて優しげだ。俺の傷から胸に向かって撫でる華子の指のやわらかな感触に、俺は少しためらってから話を続ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2323
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_af0d918d:

    # hi "You're the first person to see this since I left the hospital."
    hi "病院を出てから誰かに見せるのはこれが初めてだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2331
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_43fa1c3b:

    # ha "But… why are you showing this to me?"
    ha "でも……どうして私に？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2333
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_eb0fbb91:

    # hi "I wanted to prove to myself that I could do this; that I could accept my past and move on. I wanted to show that to you, as well."
    hi "この傷を見せることができるって自分自身に証明したかったんだ。過去のことを受け入れて前に進むことができるんだって。華子にも見せたかった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2335
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_00770cc8:

    # "She nods. From her reaction, she seems to know how difficult this is for me. More than anything, this scar represents a visible reminder of my condition. A reminder that I'm not 'normal' any more."
    "華子はうなずく。反応を見るに、これが俺にとってどれだけ難しいことだったかわかっているみたいだ。この傷ほど自分の病気のことを思い出させるものはない。自分がもう『普通』ではないことのしるしだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2337
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_4d5b9853:

    # "That's something that, until now, I had tried my hardest to ignore."
    "それは今まで俺が、必死に考えないようにしていたことだった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2339
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_6cf6a62e:

    # "As the minutes tick by, Hanako's gaze lingers. Her eyes look less focused on my scarring than before. The situation feels a bit different than it previously did, and makes me feel slightly uncomfortable."
    "時間が刻々と過ぎるなか、華子は俺を見つめたままだ。その目はさっきほど俺の傷に集中してはいない。さっきとちょっと状況が変わったように感じて、少し居心地が悪い。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2345
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_5a9f4fd9:

    # "Her hand retreats, and I draw my shirt closed and begin to button it up. Her blushing face suddenly returns to its typical tense and timid state as she looks away."
    "華子が手を引っ込めると、俺はシャツを引き寄せてボタンを留めていく。華子は顔を背けると、紅潮した顔が急にいつもの張り詰めた臆病なものに戻ってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2347
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_c0a9df89:

    # "The room is completely silent as I fix my shirt and tie, feeling put off after such an unexpectedly intimate moment."
    "そんなつもりはなかったのに、まるでいやらしい事をしているみたいになったことにどぎまぎしながら、俺がシャツとネクタイを直している間、部屋は完全に沈黙に包まれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2349
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_a5d21712:

    # hi "So… I guess you're not the only one that's scarred."
    hi "だからさ……体に傷があるのは華子だけじゃないってことだな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2354
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_f561e732:

    # "Hanako smiles a little at the joke, thankfully lightening the atmosphere a bit."
    "俺の冗談に華子は小さく微笑んで、ありがたいことに雰囲気が少しだけ明るくなる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2356
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_fa3478df:

    # ha "Thank you… H-Hisao. I think… I understand."
    ha "ひ、久夫くん……ありがとう。わかるような……気がする"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2358
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_4351386e:

    # "I give a long sigh of relief. I really didn't know how she'd take it, but I'm glad everything seems to have worked out as I hoped. Hanako's smile only proves that further."
    "俺は長い安堵の溜息をつく。華子がどう捉えるかはまったくわからなかったけど、俺が願ったとおりの結果になったのなら嬉しい。華子の笑顔がさらにその自信を確かなものにしてくれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2360
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_48b57ace:

    # "I'm finding the path I want to follow now, and what Hanako needs to do is to find her own. It's something I can't help her with, and it's something that she needs to overcome her past in order to do."
    "俺は自分が進みたい道を見つけつつある。華子もそれを見つける必要がある。それは俺が手助けできることじゃないし、まず自分の過去を乗り越えないとできることじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2365
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_8c2fb2fc:

    # "Hanako checks her watch. It's getting late by now."
    "華子は時計を見る。もうすでに遅くなりつつある。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2370
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_7fc1a655:

    # ha "Hisao… um…"
    ha "久夫くん……その……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2372
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_72f06412:

    # hi "Yeah, I'd better be going. I'll be thankful for some sleep. It's been a long day, after all."
    hi "ああ、そろそろ行ったほうがいいな。ちょっと寝たいしね。今日は長い日だったからな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2374
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_62239925:

    # hi "Good night, Hanako."
    hi "おやすみ、華子"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2379
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_cfb7eda2:

    # ha "G-good night."
    ha "お、おやすみ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2386
translate jp a4_hanako_his_past_ad9af9d0:

    # "I make my way out of her room and into the hallway, remaining silent as I do so. I think both of us have gone through a few emotions today."
    "俺は静かに部屋から廊下に出る。今日は華子も俺もいろんな感情を抱いた日だったと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2404
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_fd545815:

    # "The heat of the summertime sun beats down on my sweating brow. Dabbing with a handkerchief doesn't help too much in making me any more comfortable."
    "すでに汗が噴き出している俺の額に夏の太陽が照りつける。ハンカチで拭ってもあまり快適にはならない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2406
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_d179f752:

    # "Giving up on the idea of getting more done today, I stop and lean against one of the overpass fences, resting my bag on the ground."
    "今日はもう頑張れないなと諦めると、鞄を地面に置いて立ち止まり歩道橋のフェンスに寄りかかる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2408
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_ee077edd:

    # "The stores in the town below Yamaku are well-stocked and offer enough variety for me to get by, but at least an occasional shopping trip to the city is something that can't really be avoided."
    "山久の下の町にある店も品揃えは豊富だし、生活には十分なだけの商品の幅があるけど、それでも少なくとも時々は市街まで遠出して買い物する必要がある。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2410
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0d47539a:

    # "I've been here a few times, now. The city's layout is getting more familiar, and the nostalgia from its atmosphere is beginning to wear off."
    "ここにはもう何度かきたことがある。地理にもどんどん慣れてきているし、街の雰囲気に郷愁を感じることもなくなり始めている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2412
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_7831825d:

    # "I realize that I've begun to wheeze. I sound like an old man that's overexerted himself, and having to connect that to the fact that I'm the source is a bit disturbing."
    "自分がぜえぜえと息をしていたことに気づく。無理をした後の老人みたいな声の主が自分だということが嫌でもわかって心穏やかではいられない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2414
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_8939f9dd:

    # "I put a hand on my chest and concentrate for a bit to make sure I haven't gone far enough to cause any further problems."
    "片手を胸に当てて少し意識を集中し、これ以上何も起きなさそうなことを確かめる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2416
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_cecf5349:

    # "Thankfully, my heart is acting normally. There's no dull pain, and the beating is regular, albeit fast-paced, as I recover from overdoing things in this kind of heat."
    "幸いなことに、心臓の挙動に変なところはない。鈍い痛みもないし、脈も速いかも知れないけど規則的だ。暑い中無理をした疲労から回復してきている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2418
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_61ec3759:

    # "I hate my body. It's frustrating to be held back, even more to be held back by fear of my life being ended, when doing something as simple as walking around the city for a while."
    "俺は自分の体が嫌いだ。行動の自由を阻まれるだけでもじれったいけど、しばらく街を歩き回った程度のことで死の危険を感じて自由に動けなくなるのだからさらにじれったい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2423
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_99f82922:

    # "As I ponder on my health, I feel my pocket vibrating. By the time my phone's begun to ring, my hand is already fishing for it."
    "そうして自分の体のことを考えていると、ポケットが震えるのを感じる。着信音が鳴り始めるのを待つまでもなく、俺はすでにポケットを探っている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2425
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_eb581d84:

    # "A glance at the screen shows a caller number I don't recognize. Strange."
    "画面を一目見ると、見覚えのない番号が表示されている。妙だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2441
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_68f5d5c8:

    # "Shrugging, I press the button to answer the call and bring the phone to my ear."
    "俺は肩をすくめると、通話ボタンを押して携帯を耳に持っていく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2443
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5a3cec6a:

    # hi "Hello, Hisao Nakai speaking."
    hi "もしもし。中井です"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2445
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_27f7e019:

    # mystery "…"
    mystery "……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2447
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_67cb3b37:

    # "The sound of a couple of short breaths can be heard, but no actual speech is forthcoming."
    "短い息の音が何度か聞こえるけど、言葉は発されそうにない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2449
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_c3029e41:

    # hi "Hello?"
    hi "もしもし？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2451
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_eae2a53e:

    # ha "H… Hisao?"
    ha "ひ……久夫くん？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2453
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b8611814:

    # "It's Hanako. Her voice is really easy to place, even if I've never heard it over a phone before."
    "華子だ。華子の声なら簡単にわかる。今までに電話越しに聞いたことがなかったとしてもだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2455
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5f809d46:

    # hi "Hanako? Sorry, I wasn't expecting you to call. What's up?"
    hi "華子か？　ごめん、意外だったから。どうしたの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2457
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_1a3ab496:

    # ha "U-um… I… um…"
    ha "えっと……その……うう……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2459
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_09dbd2d9:

    # ha "If… if you're not busy… I-I was wondering if y-you would… l-like to… m—"
    ha "あのもし……もし忙しくなかったらだけど……よ、よかったら……わ、私と……あ――"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2461
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_a0c8dc63:

    # hi "Meet up?"
    hi "会う？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2463
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_8fe29e76:

    # ha "Yes! U-um… I mean…"
    ha "はい！　あ、あの……っていうのは……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2465
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_593f4508:

    # "She sounds really wound up about this. I can hear muffled voices in the background, and it's about time for afternoon tea, so I guess she'll want me to meet her at the Shanghai or something."
    "やたらと緊張しているようだ。電話の向こうからくぐもった声がいくつか聞こえる。今はちょうどおやつ時だし、上海で会いたいとかそんな感じだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2467
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_76fdb9f8:

    # hi "That sounds fine. Are you at the Shanghai?"
    hi "いいよ。上海にいるのか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2469
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_bc0a803b:

    # ha "I-I'm in… the city…"
    ha "い、今……街にいるの……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2471
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_53aca549:

    # "Hanako's here? Alone? That's a surprise. It's little wonder she's like this, if she's surrounded by people and entirely by herself."
    "華子もここにいるのか？　それも一人で？　驚きだ。華子がこんな風に緊張しているのも無理はないなと思う。周りが人だらけの中に一人ぼっちなんだから。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2473
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_2e3a8435:

    # hi "That works out well; I'm just wandering around there now. Where are you?"
    hi "それはいいな。俺も今その近くでぶらぶらしてるんだよ。どこにいるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2475
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_4e903374:

    # "Hanako manages to stammer out the street name, address, and some basic directions to where she is. Luckily it's not too far, so I agree to see her soon before hanging up."
    "華子は通りの名前と住所、だいたいの道案内をどもりながらもなんとか伝える。幸いにもあまり遠くはなく、俺はすぐに行くと答えて電話を切る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2495
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_766a3895:

    # "I look up to the sky. The summer heat is beating down."
    "俺は空を仰ぐ。夏の暑さが照りつけてくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2497
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_ac218400:

    # "This is the first time Hanako's asked for us to do something together beyond a simple board game, and the first time, at least since I've known her, that she's come to the city by herself. Maybe this means that Lilly was right."
    "華子から一緒に何かをしようと誘ってきたのはチェスなんかを除けばこれが初めてだ。そして華子が一人だけで街にきたのも、少なくとも俺が華子と出会ってから初めてのことだ。リリーは正しかったのかもな。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2507
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_3c7baab3:

    # "By the time I manage to stagger up to the café where Hanako is, I've started to wheeze again. I'm sweating so much that I feel like a melting popsicle, and can barely hold the bag in my hand."
    "ふらふらと華子のいるカフェにたどり着く頃には、俺はまたしてもぜえぜえと息を切らしていた。 汗をかきすぎて、自分がまるで溶けていくアイスキャンディーのような気になってしまう。なんとか鞄を落とさずに抱えている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2509
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_88269d56:

    # "I need to sit down, badly."
    "早く座らないとたまらない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2511
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_6fb8f599:

    # "The tables outside are all occupied by busily chatting couples and girls gossiping between themselves. The contrast between the different age groups and fashions of the people here and the people from the town near Yamaku is striking."
    "屋外のテーブルはすべて、がやがやと話しているカップルやうわさ話をしている女の子たちに使われている。山久のそばの町とこの街とでは、年齢層やファッションのギャップは著しい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2513
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_fc35697b:

    # "I scan over the people sitting at the tables, but I can't see Hanako. She did say she was sitting outside, so I must just be missing her. Not difficult, given how small she usually tries to make her presence."
    "テーブルを見渡すけど、華子はいない。華子は確かに外に座っていると言っていたから、俺が見過ごしているに違いない。華子が普段どれだけ目立つまいとしているかを考えると、無理のある可能性じゃない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2515
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_010eb012:

    # "I look around again, more slowly this time, taking particular care to see if I can find Hanako's hat. It's pretty distinctive, and I'd be very surprised if she wasn't wearing it."
    "もう一度あたりを見回す。今度はゆっくりと、華子の帽子を探すように入念に。あの帽子はわかりやすいし、華子があれを被っていないとしたらそのほうが驚きだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2517
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_229b5f1b:

    # "There she is. Sure enough, her head is kept low and the table she's sitting at is right beside the building in an inconspicuous corner."
    "いた。やっぱり華子はうつむき続けていて、座っているテーブルも建物のすぐそばの目立たない片隅にあった。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2521
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_32559496:

    # "I walk up to where she is and make sure that I have her attention before I sit, lest I give her a scare. She notices me, and gives a small wave as I arrive at her table."
    "俺は華子のところまで歩いていくと、驚かせないように華子が俺に気づいたことを確認してから腰を下ろす。華子は俺に気づくと小さく手を振る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2528
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_811403d8:

    # ha "A-are you feeling okay?"
    ha "だ、大丈夫？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2530
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_c071de07:

    # "I try my best to laugh it off, but doing so just makes me more out of breath."
    "俺は頑張って笑い飛ばそうとするけど、ますます息が切れてしまうだけの結果になる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2532
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_feb9fb77:

    # hi "Not very fit these days. Don't mind me."
    hi "最近あんまり調子がよくないんだ。気にしないでくれ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2537
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_3397fd50:

    # "Hanako nods, but still looks a bit put off."
    "華子はうなずくけど、まだ気にしているようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2539
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_c1e166c2:

    # "Now that I can get a good look at her face, something about her seems a bit different. I'm not sure if my eyes are playing tricks on me, but she looks kind of nice."
    "華子をよく見てみると、今日の華子はどこか少し違う気がする。ただの見間違いかもしれないけど、なんだか素敵に見える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2547
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_c7c8da45:

    # "Her eyes move upwards to look at me, before quickly flicking down again. I begin to think this is going to be a rather quiet meeting, but a waitress thankfully arrives and sets down a cup of tea in front of Hanako."
    "華子の目が持ち上がり俺を見たかと思うと、すぐに下にそれてしまう。ずいぶん静かな時間になりそうだと思い始めたところで、ありがたいことにちょうどウェイトレスがやってきて華子の前にお茶を置く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2552
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_e69928b4:

    # "Hanako almost automatically turns slightly away and lowers the side of her head. It's an amazingly practiced motion, and does a good job of its intended purpose - hiding her scars from someone who's leaning in close."
    "華子はほとんど反射的に顔を少し背けながら首を傾げる。驚くほど慣れた動作で、しっかりと目的を果たしている――近くに屈んでくる人からやけど痕を隠すという目的を。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2554
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_97f974ff:

    # "Her right arm is still laying on the table though, with the scarring on the back of her hand quite visible. It catches the waitress's eye, and I move to quickly distract her."
    "だけど華子の右手はまだテーブルの上に置かれたままで、手の甲のやけど痕がはっきりと見えている。それがウェイトレスの目に止まったのを見て、俺はすぐに気を引くために口を開く。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2556
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_80bbf916:

    # hi "Excuse me, may I place an order?"
    hi "すみません、注文していいですか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2558
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_92528ae0:

    # "The waitress nods and gives me a couple of seconds to look at the menu."
    "ウェイトレスはうなずいて、俺がメニューを見るのを待ってくれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2560
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_05e4fa1b:

    # hi "Could I have a mango smoothie, please?"
    hi "マンゴー・スムージーを１つください"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2562
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_40f4fc20:

    # "She gives a nod before almost enthusiastically bouncing inside. Everything is so different in the city, in more ways than one."
    "ウェイトレスはうなずくと、ほとんど喜び弾けるようにして店の中へ戻っていく。街ではなにもかも色んな意味で大違いだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2567
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_880b65b2:

    # "Hanako looks back up towards me and adjusts her hat a little. If she noticed the waitress staring at her scars, she doesn't show it."
    "華子は顔を上げて俺のほうを向くと、かぶっている帽子の位置を少しいじる。ウェイトレスが見つめていたことに気づいたとしても、華子はそんな様子を示さない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2569
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5135fa36:

    # ha "N-not coffee…?"
    ha "コ、コーヒーじゃないんだ……？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2571
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5b6e2124:

    # hi "I think I'd die from this heat if I had something like coffee right now."
    hi "今コーヒーなんか飲んだら暑さで死んじゃいそうだからね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2576
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_4ad4accd:

    # "Resting my head in my hand, I look to my quiet companion. She seems taken aback; a very unexpected reaction to my lame joke. An unwelcome emotion bubbles up inside me as I realize her reason why."
    "俺は頬杖をついて静かな華子を見る。華子は面食らっているようだ。俺のくだらない冗談にまったく予想外の反応が返ってきた。その理由に思い至って、嫌な感情が沸き上がってくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2578
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_012f9d48:

    # "Unlike most in Yamaku, indeed, unlike anyone there that I'm aware of, my condition goes beyond limiting the activities I can do. Or to be more precise, breaching those limits could have much more grave consequences."
    "大抵の山久の生徒、というか俺が知っているどの山久の生徒とも違って、俺の病気は自分の活動を制限するだけでは終わらない。より正確に言えば、制限を破ってしまったときの結果がはるかに重大なものになる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2580
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_fb41e07e:

    # "Thankfully, it's something that's very rarely come up since I entered Yamaku. I thought that it was so rare that Hanako and Lilly might not think of it at all. It turns out that I was wrong."
    "幸い、山久に入ってからそういうことはほとんど起きていない。だから華子とリリーも気にしないんじゃないかと思っていたけど、それは間違いだったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2582
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b57bded1:

    # "Hanako silently drinks her tea while I wait for my drink, confirming that it's the right temperature with a small sip before she begins in earnest."
    "俺が自分の飲み物を待っている間、華子は静かに自分のお茶を飲む。まずは少しだけ口をつけて温度を確認してから、真剣に飲み始める。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2584
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_866a709a:

    # "I feel guilty for being the cause of an uncomfortable silence, since in the past I've been kind of hard on Hanako for those."
    "気まずい沈黙を引き起こしてしまったことに申し訳なさを感じる。特に今まで華子が沈黙を引き起こすことには厳しい目を向けていたからなおさらだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2586
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_ae3fc808:

    # "Eventually the same waitress as before bounces up, handing me my drink. I gather change from my pocket and drop it into her waiting hand, before she goes off to attend to another customer. My eyes linger on her as she walks away."
    "やがてさっきと同じウェイトレスが俺の飲み物を持ってくる。俺がポケットから小銭を集めて彼女の手の平の上にそれを落とすと、ウェイトレスは他の客の応対に向かう。俺の目はそのまま立ち去る彼女を追う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2591
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_031e5773:

    # ha "Do you think that she looks… pretty…?"
    ha "あ、あのウェイトレスさんのこと……かわいいと思ったり……？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2593
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_4811ef56:

    # "Hanako is following my gaze, her eyes taking in the waitress that served us. I can feel my blood slowly going to my cheeks as I rest my smoothie back on the table."
    "華子は俺の視線を追って、さっきのウェイトレスを見ている。俺はスムージーのグラスをテーブルに置きながら、自分の頬に血が登っていくのを感じる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2595
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_cf95ba1a:

    # hi "Nah, can't really say that I'm really into that look. She just looked a lot like an old friend I knew before my heart attack."
    hi "いや、あんまり好みとは言えないな。心臓発作が起きる前の古い友達にすごく似てたってだけだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2600
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5f53108d:

    # ha "Did you… have many friends?"
    ha "友達が……多かったの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2602
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b29e1919:

    # hi "I had a few at my previous school, though I wouldn't say a lot. The four of us just hung around together after school and stuff."
    hi "前の学校では何人かいたけど、多かったとは言えないかな。4人組で放課後によく遊んでたくらいだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2607
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_717104a5:

    # ha "Do you still talk to them?"
    ha "今でも話すの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2609
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_6a20a80d:

    # "I shake my head."
    "俺は首を横に振る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2611
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b8812c2e:

    # hi "No. We gradually lost contact while I was stuck in the hospital."
    hi "いいや。病院に閉じ込められてる間にだんだん連絡が途絶えていったよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2616
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_bba4520d:

    # ha "You're not… saddened by that? Or angry?"
    ha "久夫くんは……それで悲しくならないの？　腹が立たないの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2618
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_2e25fbeb:

    # "Hanako looks genuinely surprised. I guess it's the right reaction."
    "華子は本当に驚いているみたいだ。普通はそういう反応になるだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2620
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_fce1460e:

    # hi "Well, life did move on for them while I was stuck in the ward. I was pretty sore about it at the time, but now it's just a bunch of nice memories."
    hi "まあ、俺が病棟にいる間にあいつらの生活も変わったんだよ。その時はかなり傷ついたけど、今となってはただの楽しい思い出だよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2622
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b1617d50:

    # hi "Besides, once I came to Yamaku I found new friends as well."
    hi "それに、山久にきてからは新しい友達も見つかったしな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2624
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_978a0dbe:

    # "That's quite a whitewash of what my feelings were back then. I went through some dark times during my stay at the hospital, and I really am glad that Hanako and Lilly were around to help me after I left it."
    "俺はあの時の気持ちを相当ごまかして説明している。病院にいたときは相当苦しいときもあった。病院を出たあと華子とリリーが支えてくれたことはほんとうに有難い。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2629
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0a61548d:

    # "Hanako blushes as we both get down to enjoying our drinks. She seems to have calmed down since I arrived, and I've started to feel a little better now that I've had the chance to rest a bit, so this is getting to be a nice outing already."
    "華子が顔を赤らめて、俺たちは飲み物に手をつけ始める。俺がきてから華子は落ち着いたようで、俺もまた少し休憩できたおかげで気分が良くなった。楽しい外出になりつつある。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2631
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_9c892dac:

    # "Even if she's calmer than before, though, she's still fidgeting a bit. She runs her hand down one of her bangs as I try to think of something to say."
    "でも華子は電話のときより落ち着いているにせよ、まだ少しそわそわとしている。俺が何か言うことを考えている間、華子は前髪をいじっている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2633
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_f32fe676:

    # hi "That's right. I was going to ask…"
    hi "そうだ。さっき聞こうとしてたんだけど……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2638
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_3334ce35:

    # "Hanako tilts her head quizzically."
    "華子は首を傾げる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2640
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_de8c3f5d:

    # hi "I didn't know you had a mobile phone. How'd you get my number?"
    hi "華子が携帯持ってるって知らなかったよ。どこで俺の番号を？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2645
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_61dc2341:

    # ha "L-Lilly… gave it… to me."
    ha "リ、リリーが……教えて……くれたの"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2647
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_914e3e4b:

    # "I should have guessed."
    "そりゃそうか。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2649
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0b5c8e37:

    # hi "You know, you could have just asked; I'd have given it to you."
    hi "そんなの言ってくれたら教えたのにな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2651
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0aff9afb:

    # hi "Want to exchange email addresses?"
    hi "メールアドレスも交換しとく？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2656
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_951aa4ad:

    # "Hanako nods, setting down her drink and fishing out her phone from her pocket as I do the same."
    "華子がうなずいてお茶をテーブルに置くと、俺たちはポケットから携帯電話を引っ張り出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2668
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_71e6d83f:

    # "It's, surprisingly, the same model as mine. Pink, though."
    "驚いたことに、俺のと同じモデルだ。色はピンクだけど。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2670
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_39a754c7:

    # hi "Nice phone."
    hi "いい携帯だな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2683
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_c6f79402:

    # "She looks to me with a curious expression, before noticing my phone and giggling. It's one of the very few times I've seen Hanako let her guard down enough to do such a thing."
    "華子はいぶかしむようにこちらを見ると、俺の携帯に気づいて笑いだす。こんな風に心を開いてくれるのは滅多に見られない瞬間だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2688
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_09b34849:

    # ha "I didn't pick it out myself, though."
    ha "自分で選んだわけじゃないんだけど"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2690
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_f9075882:

    # hi "Oh?"
    hi "へえ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2695
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_e52c7477:

    # ha "It was a present, from Lilly."
    ha "プレゼントなの、リリーからの"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2700
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_05e9487d:

    # ha "I never really needed a phone, and I couldn't afford one. She bought me one for Christmas, though, saying that we could use it to keep in touch."
    ha "携帯電話が必要になることってなかったし、自分で買う余裕もなかったんだけどね。リリーがこれで連絡が取り合えるねってクリスマスに買ってくれたの"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2702
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_087f2f05:

    # "They see each other basically every day anyway, both in and out of school…"
    "まあ学校の中でも外でも二人は基本的に毎日会うわけだけど……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2704
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_cc475ccb:

    # "Then again, Lilly does have her class representative duties and other friends that she talks with. It'd probably help for situations like this, too, when she's gone away for a while."
    "とはいえ、リリーには学級委員の仕事もあるし華子以外にもおしゃべりする友達がいる。それに今みたいにリリーがしばらくここを離れるような時にも役に立つだろうし。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2706
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_7e0922b0:

    # hi "Lilly's a very special person to you, isn't she?"
    hi "リリーは華子にとって特別な人なんだな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2711
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_d1e32825:

    # ha "She is. I… love her… very much."
    ha "うん。リリーのこと……大好きだから"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2713
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0236da77:

    # "Hanako looks down and smiles as she thinks of her. None of my friendships were as deep as theirs, and I have to admit to myself that I'm a little jealous of their relationship."
    "華子はうつむいて、リリーのことを考えながら微笑む。俺はこの二人ほど深い友情を築いたことはない。少し嫉妬している自分がいることは認めざるをえない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2715
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_a6ec9743:

    # "We tell each other our email addresses and thumb them into our respective phones, and I get Hanako's number from earlier and put it into my contacts list."
    "俺たちは互いのメールアドレスを教えあってそれぞれの携帯に入力していく。俺は華子がさっきかけてきた番号もアドレス帳に登録しておく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2720
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_7924eeae:

    # ha "…Done. That makes three, now."
    ha "……できた。これで３つだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2722
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_592aba13:

    # hi "Three?"
    hi "３つ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2727
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b8eb6b82:

    # ha "Lilly, Akira and you."
    ha "リリーと、晃さんと、久夫くんだよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2729
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_87ab6cb8:

    # hi "Ah, Akira. She's an interesting person, isn't she?"
    hi "ああ、晃さんか。面白い人だよね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2734
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_e71a95f2:

    # ha "She is. She's also really nice, though. Her suit makes her… look a bit cool."
    ha "うん。それに、ほんとにいい人なんだよ。スーツを着てると……ちょっとかっこいいし"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2736
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0c8ea95a:

    # hi "I'm a little surprised you know each other well, what with her job taking up so much of her time."
    hi "華子と晃さんがお互いを知ってるのはちょっと驚きだなぁ。晃さんって仕事が忙しいみたいだし"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2741
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b016d884:

    # "Hanako looks down a little and takes another sip of her drink. If I wasn't looking intently at her face, I'd miss the small smile perched on it. I guess when she knows so few people, those she knows must mean a lot to her."
    "華子はうつむいて、お茶をもう一口飲む。じっと見つめていなければ、その顔が小さくほころんでいることに気づかなかっただろう。友達が少なければ自然とその友達がとても大事になるはずだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2743
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_3af0466b:

    # ha "How many… do you have?"
    ha "久夫くんは……どれくらいいる？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2745
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_83e586e5:

    # hi "Me? About nine or ten."
    hi "俺か？　９人か１０人くらいかな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2747
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_cdc3434b:

    # "I hesitate to go into them for fear of rubbing in the fact that Hanako doesn't have parents, or apparently even close relatives. Two of those are Shizune and Misha, too, which is another can of worms."
    "両親もなく、近い親戚もいなさそうな華子を傷つけたくなくて、内訳を詳しく言うことはためらう。このうち二人が静音とミーシャだというのも、また厄介だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2749
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_f8058879:

    # hi "I imagine that Lilly would have more than both of us put together, probably."
    hi "俺ら二人分を合わせてもリリーのほうが多そうだな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2754
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_e506e7e7:

    # "Hanako gives a childish giggle, and I can't help smiling. It's a good feeling that she's gotten this comfortable around me; at times like this, I feel like I'm getting close to talking to her true self."
    "華子が子供っぽく笑って、俺も笑いを抑えられない。俺のそばでこんな風に自然体を見せてくれる華子を見るのはいい気分だ。こういう時、俺は自分が本当の華子に近づいているような気がする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2756
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b59e32b4:

    # hi "Do you mind if I ask something that I've been wondering?"
    hi "気になってることがあるんだけど聞いてもいいか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2761
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_da6f2b09:

    # "Hanako shakes her head as she takes a last sip of her tea, finishing it off."
    "華子はうなずくと、最後の一口を口に含んで紅茶を飲み終える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2763
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_59a0906e:

    # hi "You don't seem very jealous of Lilly having lots of friends. Don't you want to make some more friends yourself, or get to know some of hers?"
    hi "リリーに友達が多くてもあまりうらやましそうじゃないなと思って。友達を増やしたいとか、リリーの友達と話してみたいとか思うことはない？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2768
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_b1ce8872:

    # ha "I'm not jealous. I… don't like people, so I don't mind not having many friends."
    ha "うらやましくはならないよ。私は……人間が好きじゃないし、友達が少なくても気にしないから"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2770
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_17386369:

    # "That's… really not the answer that I was expecting. She doesn't look fearful or sad as she says this, but rather, quite serious."
    "その答えは……まったく予想外だった。華子はびくびくと言うわけでも悲しそうに言うわけでもなく、とても真剣な顔をする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2775
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_68fc7b90:

    # ha "I…"
    ha "私は……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2777
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_30cc7a36:

    # "Hanako rubs her arm awkwardly, having taken my quietness as a reason to continue. I'm not really sure what I should say, so I end up simply giving her my attention in silence."
    "華子は気まずそうに腕をさすると、静かな俺を見てそのまま話し続けようとする。俺は何と言っていいのかよくわからなくて、ただ黙って華子の話に耳を傾ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2779
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_9d8b0e80:

    # ha "In middle school, I got bullied… a lot. I was called names, and got excluded from work groups and sports teams. There were… worse things, too."
    ha "中学校の時、いっぱい……いじめられたんだ。罵られたり、グループから仲間はずれにされたり。もっとひどいことも……あった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2781
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_92958a26:

    # hi "And that's what made you not like other people?"
    hi "だから他人が好きじゃなくなった？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2783
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0e493581:

    # "She shakes her head."
    "華子は首を横に振る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2788
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_4fd67aef:

    # ha "That was… elementary school."
    ha "それは……小学校のころかな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2790
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_2fd1693c:

    # "I feel bad for bringing this up now. Adults have enough problems dealing with Hanako's scarring; children would be all the worse."
    "こんな話題を持ちだして申し訳ない気分になる。大人でも華子のやけど痕に困惑するのに、子供ならなおさらだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2792
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_d5017ea7:

    # "I had assumed that the way she tried to make her presence not felt was just to avoid people staring at her, or because she was afraid of them; certainly not because she genuinely didn't want to interact with them in the first place as well."
    "華子が自分の存在感を薄めようとするのは人にじろじろ見られるのを避けるためか、人を怖がっているのだと単純に思っていた。そもそも人と関わりたくないなんて思っているわけではないんだと。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2794
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_ef8c636b:

    # "I notice the condensation from my neglected smoothie forming a little puddle around the bottom of the cup, so I take the opportunity to finish it off."
    "スムージーを飲む手が止まっている間にコップの底に水たまりが出来ていたことに気が付いた俺は、今のうちに飲みきることにする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2801
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_ddab0804:

    # "As I drink, she begins to fiddle with her phone. It looks like she's remembered the people around her again, and begun to tense up."
    "その間に華子は携帯をいじくりはじめる。周りに人がいることを思い出してまた体がこわばり始めたようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2803
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_d8293d81:

    # "It isn't exactly a cheap phone - I had to save up for quite a while to afford one when I got mine. If Lilly went to a private school, she probably wouldn't have too much trouble getting one for a present, though."
    "安物の携帯ではない――俺がこれを買ったときはしばらくお金を貯める必要があった。私立に通っていたリリーなら、プレゼントにそれを買うのもそんなに無理な話じゃないんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2805
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_a5e2ead7:

    # "Watching her fiddle with it gives me an idea…"
    "携帯をいじっている華子を見ていて、俺はふとあることを思いつく……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2807
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_4d10dd3c:

    # hi "Hey Hanako, wait for me. I'll be right back."
    hi "ごめん華子、ちょっと待ってて。すぐ戻るから"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2811
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5797b15e:

    # "I put the now empty cup down, slip my phone into my pocket, and begin to move off, carefully stepping around the bag I'd placed beside my feet. Thankfully, sitting around while talking to Hanako has helped me feel a lot better than before."
    "もう空になったコップを置いて携帯をポケットに滑りこませると、足元に置いていた鞄を慎重に避けながら席を立つ。幸いなことに、テーブルに座って華子と話している間に気分はずっとよくなっている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2816
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_4910f43b:

    # ha "Wait, w-what? Wh-where are you going?"
    ha "待って、な、何なの？　ど、どこに行くの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2818
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_96a42d3f:

    # hi "Just stay here, I'll be back in a bit!"
    hi "いいからここで待ってて、すぐ戻るから！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2830
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_55f2fc81:

    # "As much as I'd have liked to have jogged back, I know full well that I couldn't. I end up walking back to the café, a little blue bag in my right hand."
    "駆け足で戻りたいのは山々だったけど、それが無理なことはよくわかっている。結局俺はカフェまで歩いて戻る。右手の中には小さな青い袋がある。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2837
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_aca3c9d6:

    # "Hanako notices me quickly, looking about as confused as she did when I left. I deposit the diminutive bag in front of her and sit back down."
    "華子はすぐに俺に気づくと、俺が立ち去った時と同じくらい混乱した表情を見せる。小さな袋を華子の目の前に置くと、俺は席に掛ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2842
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_a352bc28:

    # ha "Is this…?"
    ha "これは……？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2844
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_8180e0f4:

    # hi "It's for you. You can open it."
    hi "華子へのプレゼントだ。開けていいよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2849
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5e71d5d9:

    # ha "B-but…"
    ha "で、でも……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2851
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_4d826ee9:

    # hi "Go on."
    hi "ほらほら"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2853
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_c7e6e6a8:

    # "She looks very unsure about it, but eventually gives in, slowly opens the bag and picks its contents out."
    "華子はどうすべきか決めかねるような顔をしていたけど、やがて引き下がると、ゆっくりと袋を開けて中身を取り出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2865
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_0795b5cb:

    # "A silver chain phone strap dangles from her fingers, ending in a delicate flower. It isn't exactly a masterwork of jewelry, but it's about as much as I could afford."
    "華子の指の隙間から下へ垂れている携帯ストラップのシルバーチェーンの先には精巧な花がついている。綺麗な宝石ってわけじゃないけど、俺に買えるのはこれぐらいまでだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2869
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_c2dff129:

    # "Hanako's eyes light up when she looks at it. It's the kind of reaction I was hoping for."
    "ストラップを見た華子の目が輝く。それは返ってきて欲しいと願っていたリアクションだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2871
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_899951b5:

    # "The summer sun's light glints off the silver as it twists to and fro a little. It's not too ostentatious, but still looks a little charming. I think it suits her well."
    "ねじれてくるくると回るチェーンの銀色にきらきらと夏の太陽が反射する。派手ではないけど、それでもちょっと素敵なストラップだ。華子に合っていると思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2882
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_08587d86:

    # "Hanako lowers the phone strap to the table and looks to me once more."
    "華子は携帯ストラップをテーブルに置くともう一度俺のほうを見てくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2887
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_f30c0c72:

    # ha "But… it's not… Christmas, or my birthday…"
    ha "でも……クリスマスでも誕生日でもないのに……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2889
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_01865038:

    # hi "It's fine, don't worry about it. I just thought it might be nice to have something to decorate your phone with."
    hi "大丈夫、気にしなくていいよ。何か携帯を飾るものがあったほうがいいんじゃないかと思っただけだから"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2894
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_76ea4714:

    # ha "I-I don't have anything to give to you…"
    ha "で、でも何もお返しするものがないし……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2896
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_f7286ee4:

    # hi "I told you, it's fine. Friends can give things to each other like this sometimes, right?"
    hi "だから大丈夫だって。友達はこんなふうに贈り物することもあるもんだろ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2901
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_2a5c5b9b:

    # ha "Friends…"
    ha "友達……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2903
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_337f97b8:

    # "Hanako lowers her face so much that I can't see her expression. She eventually nods, before taking her phone and fiddling with the strap to attach it properly."
    "華子の顔は大きくうつむいていて表情が伺えない。やがて華子はうなずくと、携帯電話を手にとってストラップをきちんと取り付けようといじりはじめる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2919
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_f3f13a16:

    # "She looks to me and smiles as she holds up her phone, now adorned with a little flower."
    "華子は小さな花に飾られた携帯電話を持ち上げて俺に笑顔を向ける。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2921
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_bb14a05c:

    # ha "Thank you… Hisao."
    ha "ありがとう……久夫くん"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2932
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_28bd438c:

    # "Her smile proves infectious."
    "華子の笑顔がうつってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2934
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_66b0957a:

    # "Out of the corner of my eye, I notice a couple getting up and leaving. That reminds me that the bus back to the town below Yamaku will be coming soon."
    "視界の隅で、席を立ち店を後にするカップルの姿に気づく。それを見て山久の下の町へ戻るバスの時刻がもうすぐだということを思い出す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2936
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_f98b0b78:

    # hi "I guess I'd better be going if I want to catch the next bus back to town. You coming as well?"
    hi "町に戻る次のバスに乗りたかったらもう出たほうがよさそうだな。一緒に行くか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2941
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_5462618b:

    # ha "Ah, y-yes."
    ha "あっ、う、うん"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2950
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_fbbb16e9:

    # "She hastily nods before carefully putting her phone back into her pocket and getting out of her chair. I do the same and pick up the bag I'd left beside me on the way out."
    "華子は急いでうなずくと慎重に携帯電話をポケットに戻して席を立つ。俺も立ち上がると、横に立てかけてあった鞄を手にとって外に出る。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2962
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_6643a198:

    # "We walk side by side as we make our way to the bus station, exchanging no words between us. Hanako's gaze is firmly locked ahead of her, though she looks very happy with herself."
    "俺たちは一言も喋らないまま、肩を並べてバス停へ歩いていく。華子は前を固く見据えたままだけど、とても嬉しそうな顔をしている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2964
translate jp a4_hanako_city_rendezvous_a48d1ca3:

    # "I'm not sure what I should say to her, but I'm also not sure that I need to say anything. The fact that Hanako is happy, and happy because of me, is enough to make the load on my arm feel light as a feather."
    "俺は華子にどんな言葉をかければいいのかわからないけど、そもそも何か言う必要があるのかと言われるとそれもわからない。 ただ華子が喜んでいて、それも俺のおかげで喜んでくれているというだけで、手に持った荷物が羽のように軽く感じる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2982
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_550e1caa:

    # "Finally reaching the classroom after the usual walk from the dormitories, I step inside. My eyes immediately turn to the third seat from the left in the back row; Hanako's seat."
    "いつものように寮から歩き、教室の前にたどり着く。中へ足を踏み入れると、俺の視線はすぐに後ろの列の左から三番目の席に向かう。華子の席だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2984
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_a536f60c:

    # "It's empty, and after glancing around the classroom, it looks like she isn't here yet. The two girls from the newspaper club are here in the two seats to the left of Hanako's, as are Shizune and Misha, but that's about it."
    "席は空っぽで、教室を見渡してみても、まだ華子は来ていないようだ。華子の左隣の２つの席にはそれぞれ新聞部の子が座っていて、静音とミーシャも席についているけど、それだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2986
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_8b512dae:

    # "We exchange morning greetings before I take my seat. I have to admit that this is a bit of a relief. This gives me at least a few more minutes to think."
    "俺は朝の挨拶を交わして自分の席につく。少し安心してしまったことは認めざるをえない。これで何分かは考える時間ができた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2988
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_519a7d47:

    # "Not that I haven't been doing so previously; ever since our trip to town, Hanako's been on my mind."
    "今までだって考えてはいたけど。街に出かけてからというもの、華子のことが頭から離れない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2990
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_72339eaa:

    # "I still don't know what to make of my relationship to Hanako. I like her, I can admit that much to myself. I want to protect and shield her from the pain she feels. I really don't think my feelings are just those of friendship any more."
    "まだ自分と華子の今の関係をどう考えたものかわからない。華子が好きだということまでは認めていいだろう。 華子を彼女自身が感じている苦痛から守ってやりたい。もはやこれはただの友達に抱く気持ちとはいえないと思う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2992
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_940aeb5b:

    # "But that said… I feel like I don't even know her."
    "でもそうは言っても……俺は自分が華子のことを知ってもいない気がする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2994
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_2c4c05d9:

    # "If I made a move on her, how would she take it? Is she in an emotional state that allows her to make a reasonable decision about a relationship? How would she cope with anything that might happen afterwards?"
    "もし俺が華子にアクションを起こしたら、それをどう受け取るだろう？　そもそも恋愛についてちゃんと判断できるような精神状態なのか？　そしてその後のことに華子はちゃんと対処できるのだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:2999
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9d814a5e:

    # "There's also the possibility that I'm just completely misinterpreting Hanako; not a difficult thing to do with someone whose social skills seem to be so underdeveloped."
    "単純に俺が華子のことをすっかり誤解してしまっているという可能性だってある。華子が人との接し方に慣れていないことを考えれば、無理な話じゃない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3001
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_f753899d:

    # "The sound of footsteps comes up to the door, making me perk up."
    "教室のドアへ足音が近づいてきて、俺はハッと顔をあげる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3013
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_796abbe3:

    # "It ends up just being Miki."
    "なんだ、美貴か。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3025
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_6b6df1cd:

    # "She barely acknowledges my existence when I accidentally make eye contact with her. I'm about to look away, but another person comes in not long after she takes her seat."
    "たまたま目が合うけど美貴はあまり気に留めていない。俺はドアから視線を外そうとするけど、美貴が席につくとすぐにまた教室に入ってくる人影がある。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3036
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d4f4e3d0:

    # "I feel myself freeze as I see Hanako enter. This isn't a rational reaction, but I have no idea about how I should act or what I should say to her."
    "入ってきた華子を見て俺は凍りついてしまう。こんなのはまともな反応じゃないのはわかってるけど、どう振る舞っていいのかも何を話せばいいのかもわからない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3041
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_5d08a493:

    # "For a moment, our eyes meet."
    "一瞬、俺たちの目が合う。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3053
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_6ce75caa:

    # "And then, just as quickly, she looks away and moves to her seat without saying a single word."
    "そして華子は同じくらいの速さで目を背けると、 何を言うこともなく席へと向かう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3060
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_0ba12903:

    # "As is now usual for the period following classes, my face is buried deep in a book that I find thoroughly uninteresting."
    "もはや授業の合間としてはいつものことだけど、俺はかけらも面白いと思わない本に顔をうずめている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3062
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_33e41b79:

    # "Studying is not something that comes naturally to me. I didn't study a lot before coming to Yamaku, and until now I've largely managed to coast through on talent alone. It's frustrating that I can't do that any more."
    "勉強は性に合ってない。山久にくるまではあまり勉強していなかったし、 山久にきてからもほとんど努力はせずに何とかしてきた。もう同じようにはいかないのが歯がゆい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3064
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_c3d89511:

    # "Judging by the faces of the other few students in the library, I don't think I'm alone in my distaste for this. Misery loves company, I suppose."
    "図書室にいる他の生徒の顔を見るに、 勉強が嫌いなのは俺だけじゃないらしい。同類相憐れむ、というか。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3066
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_564c9d99:

    # "I decided to spend lunchtime with Hanako, since we haven't had lunch together for a while now. I may as well have spent the time studying, though; aside from pathetically small snippets of smalltalk, there was barely a word said between us."
    "華子とはしばらく一緒に昼食をとれなかったし、昼休みは一緒に過ごすことにした。でも別に勉強をして過ごしてもよかったかもしれない。痛ましいほど細切れの雑談を除いて、ほとんど会話がない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3068
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_e4d65010:

    # "Why does she keep doing this to me? I just want to protect her, to be there for her, but every time I feel like we're coming closer, we end up further away."
    "どうしてずっとこうなんだろうか？　俺はただ華子を守りたくて、華子のために何かしてあげたいだけなのに、仲良くなれたと思うたびに結局さらに距離が遠くなっている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3070
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_5bbf795a:

    # ha "A-are you busy…?"
    ha "い、いま大丈夫……?"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3077
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_b638bbd9:

    # hi "Hanako!?"
    hi "は、華子！？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3079
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9fbdda7d:

    # "My head whips around in surprise, causing her to retreat in fright."
    "俺が驚いて頭をぐるりと回転させるものだから、華子はおびえて後ずさる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3084
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_dc1482fa:

    # "That was bad timing. If I hadn't been thinking about her at that very moment, I probably wouldn't have been nearly so startled."
    "タイミングが悪かった。声をかけられたのがまさに華子のことを考えている瞬間でさえなければ、俺もあんなに驚くことはなかっただろう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3088
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_cf6ea2c1:

    # hi "Sorry, you just startled me."
    hi "ごめん、ビックリしちゃってつい"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3090
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_c25c5da8:

    # "I find myself staring at her longer than I should, so I go back to the text lying on the table in front of me. I feel more like I'm just staring at the words rather than actually reading."
    "華子のことを見つめすぎている自分に気づいて、目の前のテーブル上のテキストに目を戻す。読むというよりは字面を追っているだけという感じだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3092
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_164e9d00:

    # "I get the feeling Hanako can notice this as well, so I sigh and close the book."
    "それくらい華子も気づくような気がする。俺はため息をついて本を閉じる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3094
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_3156ccff:

    # hi "What's up?"
    hi "どうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3099
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_a321685b:

    # ha "I was just… w-wondering what you were r-reading…"
    ha "ただちょっと……何を読んでるのかなって……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3101
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_0fb67f75:

    # "She looks a little downcast after my reaction to seeing her. Giving up on the prospect of getting any more work done, I get up and return the book to its place on a nearby shelf."
    "さっきの俺の反応のせいか華子は少し元気がないように見える。俺はこれ以上勉強を進めることは諦めて、立ち上がると近くの棚に本を戻す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3103
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_6165ed3d:

    # hi "Just an English textbook."
    hi "ただの英語の参考書だよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3108
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_3ea9dc43:

    # ha "H-has it helped?"
    ha "や、役に立った？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3110
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_058a3c61:

    # hi "It helped me realize that I don't like English, yeah."
    hi "ああ、俺は英語が嫌いなんだなと実感する役には立ったよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3115
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d588ebda:

    # "Hanako gives a small giggle. I may muse on the strange state of our friendship, but I do know that such little gestures are things that I wouldn't see were I not at least some distance closer to her than when we first met."
    "華子は小さく笑う。華子との奇妙な関係性に悩むこともあるけれど、こんなささやかな仕草も初めて出会った頃より仲良くなっていなければ見れなかったはずのものだということはわかっている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3117
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_1252956c:

    # "I look at her for a moment, thinking about what I do and don't know about her. It's a slightly depressing topic."
    "俺は少し華子を見つめながら、自分が華子について何を知っていて何を知らないかを考える。少し気分の落ち込む議題だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3122
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_972cd3c0:

    # ha "I-is something… wrong?"
    ha "ど、どうか……したの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3126
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_613efb97:

    # "If I want to know more about her, maybe I should stop being so evasive about it."
    "華子のことをもっと知りたいと思うなら、逃げることはやめるべきだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3128
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_714ee869:

    # "Talking with Lilly as an equal rather than being constantly in fear of causing her to become upset worked fine, so I should just try a straightforward approach with Hanako as well."
    "リリーとの付き合いでは、余計なことを言ってしまわないかとびくびくしながら話すよりも対等な人間として話そうとするほうが上手くいった。だから華子にもまっすぐ正攻法で行くべきだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3130
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_16de5a20:

    # hi "Hey Hanako, do you mind if I ask you a question?"
    hi "なあ、ひとつ聞いてもいいか？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3135
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_0feba7c5:

    # ha "I-I don't mind."
    ha "い、いいよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3137
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d9d20bca:

    # hi "I… want to know what your life was like. Your life before coming to Yamaku."
    hi "俺……華子が前にどんな生活をしてたのか知りたいんだ。山久に来る前のことをさ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3142
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_11856aa7:

    # "She hesitates. I briefly consider backing off, but she seems to be taking the question quite seriously."
    "華子はたじろぐ。俺はすぐに撤回しようかと迷うけど、華子は俺の質問を真剣に考えているようだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3144
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_a43b8849:

    # "I sit and watch her, silently letting her take her time. She's not making eye contact with me, and looks almost as if she's arguing with herself into letting herself open up to me more."
    "俺はただ静かに座って華子を見つめながら待っている。華子は俺と目を合わせようとせず、まるで俺に心を開くべきかどうか自問自答しているように見える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3146
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_5a4c5ef2:

    # "Her answer finally comes in a stiff, almost reluctant nod. She looks far more tense than she did before I'd asked."
    "やがて華子は硬い顔で、ほとんど渋々ながらうなずいて応えてくれる。俺が質問する前よりはるかに顔が強張っている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3151
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d997864a:

    # ha "Okay. B-but in return… you have to t-tell me about your life as well…"
    ha "いいよ。で、でもお返しに……久夫くんの昔のこともお、教えて……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3156
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_32a4761a:

    # "I nod, and follow her as she begins to walk out the library so we can talk."
    "俺はうなずいて、話をするために図書室の外へと歩き出す華子についていく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3164
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_e64aca17:

    # "By now most of the students have already left the main building, so apart from a few people hovering around club rooms, the hallways are largely empty."
    "もう本校舎に残っている生徒はほとんどいない。部室の周りをうろついている何人かを除けば、廊下はとてもガランとしている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3166
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_060f230a:

    # hi "I guess… we'll start with coming to Yamaku."
    hi "そうだな……山久へきた経緯から話そうか"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3168
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_ea5790f9:

    # hi "Let's see… I was in the hospital when my parents first told me about Yamaku Academy."
    hi "ええと……俺が病院にいたときだな、うちの親から初めて山久について聞いたのは"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3170
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_85b6f317:

    # hi "The doctors told me I shouldn't go to my old school any more. My parents agreed and persuaded me to apply for Yamaku, even though it would mean living away from them for the first time."
    hi "医者が前の学校にはもう行かないほうがいいって言ってさ。親もそれに賛成して山久に転校を申請するように俺を説得したんだ。それは俺が生まれて初めて親元から離れて暮らすってことでもあった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3175
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_18fcd1de:

    # ha "It must have… been hard for you."
    ha "大変……だっただろうね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3177
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_db0c4675:

    # hi "Well… yeah, I have to admit that it was. My parents both work long hours and full-time, so having to live reasonably independently wasn't anything new to me. It was the fact that I was going to a school for disabled students that hit hardest, I think."
    hi "まあ……そうだな、それは認めざるをえないよ。でも俺の両親は朝から晩まで共働きだから、ある程度自立することには慣れてたんだ だから、障害者のための学校に転校しないといけないんだってことが一番ショックだったんだろうな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3179
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_46cbdc04:

    # hi "And you?"
    hi "華子は？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3185
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_873284a1:

    # "A small group of chatting girls passes us as we near the stairs, with Hanako pressing herself tightly to my side until we reach the ground floor. She doesn't usually come this close while just walking in the school, so I'm left a little put off."
    "階段に近づいたところで、おしゃべりしている女子の集団とすれ違う。華子が俺に体をぴったりとくっつけてきて、俺たちは一階までそのままの姿勢で降りる。 普段学校の中を歩いているだけのときに華子がこんなに近づいてくることはなくて、少し落ち着かない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3190
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_1a1c9ab8:

    # ha "The staff at the o-orphanage offered me some options on what I could do. Middle school… hadn't been good, so I thought that Yamaku might be better."
    ha "孤児院の先生はいくつか進路を提案してくれたの。中学は……楽しくなかったから、山久のほうがいいかなって思ったんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3192
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_b99e3d03:

    # ha "It was isolated, and I thought it might be easier to get by here with most of the others being disabled."
    ha "山久は外とは隔絶してたし、周りが障害者ばかりのほうが過ごしやすいかなって思って"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3197
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_052d3574:

    # "It's pretty ironic that the reasons Hanako looked forward to Yamaku are the exact reasons I hated the idea. To me, it felt like I was being shunted somewhere away from society, and everyone I knew. To Hanako, that was probably an inviting prospect."
    "まさに俺が山久を嫌がっていた理由が、華子にとっては山久に惹かれた理由だったなんてとても皮肉だ。 俺にとっては、社会や知り合いから隔離されてどこかに島流しにされるような感じがした。でも華子にとってはきっと、それこそが魅力的な部分だったんだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3199
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_eac9ddb0:

    # hi "What was life like at the orphanage?"
    hi "孤児院での暮らしはどうだったんだ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3204
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_7dd0b798:

    # ha "It was… okay. The staff there were nice, and they took care of us. The children there didn't talk to me much, but I didn't really want to talk with them either, so I didn't mind."
    ha "悪くは……なかったよ。先生は優しかったし、私たちの面倒を見てくれたし。他の子が話しかけてくることはあまりなかったけど、私もあまり話をしたくなかったから、それでよかった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3209
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_8cd03c8b:

    # ha "The orphanage had a little library, so I started to read to pass the time. The staff didn't mind it, because it made me easier to handle than many of the other children."
    ha "孤児院にはちっちゃな図書室があって、本を読んで過ごすようになったの。本を読んでれば他の子たちより扱いやすくなるから孤児院の先生も何も言わなかった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3211
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_dd90518f:

    # hi "You didn't make any friends there?"
    hi "友達は作らなかった？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3216
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_1556a6e9:

    # ha "No. I think… my life was on hold… during that time. I knew that, but I didn't mind."
    ha "うん。あの頃は……人生を保留にしてるみたいだった……と思う。それは自分でもわかってたけど、それでよかった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3218
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_46c8e8be:

    # "To think her life was on hold for all that time, though… depending on when the fire happened, that was a huge chunk of her life. No parents, no friends, apparently no relatives…"
    "孤児院ではずっとそんな風に過ごしてたと考えると……いつ火事があったのかにもよるけど、人生の大部分じゃないか。両親もいなくて、友達もいなくて、親戚もいないみたいで……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3223
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_090d35f6:

    # "We walk through the door into the courtyard. I expect to need to avert my eyes from the sun, but by now it's well into sunset."
    "俺たちはドアを抜けて中庭へ出る。太陽の光から目を逸らそうと構えていたけど、もうすでにかなり日が沈んでいる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3228
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d4a01b1b:

    # "Hanako's eyes keep flicking to me, so I look away from her for a bit."
    "華子の目がチラチラとこちらを見てきて、俺は少し目をそらす。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3230
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_f42288ae:

    # ha "What was it like in the hospital?"
    ha "久夫くんが病院にいたときは、どうだったの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3232
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_58c07e2f:

    # "I quickly clear my thoughts and try to refocus them."
    "俺はすぐに自分の頭を空っぽにすると、集中しなおす。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3234
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_934534ca:

    # "I hesitate for a bit, but I know that I have to tell her. We're close enough for her to feel comfortable telling me this, so it's only fair that I reciprocate."
    "俺は少しためらう。だけど話さなきゃいけないのはわかってる。華子がこんな話をしてもいいと感じてくれるほど仲良くなれたんだから、俺もそれに報いなきゃフェアじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3236
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9495fafd:

    # hi "It was okay at times, but at others, it was pretty bad. At the beginning, everyone sent their sympathies, and came to visit often. It was just like breaking an arm or something."
    hi "大丈夫なときは大丈夫だったけど、そうじゃないときはかなり辛かったな。最初のころはみんな共感してくれたし、よくお見舞いにきてくれたよ。まるで腕を骨折したとかそんなかんじだった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3238
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_5fbe2580:

    # hi "Meeting all my friends was one of the good times. Iwanako came in often as well; more often than anyone else."
    hi "友達に会えるときはいつも楽しかった。岩魚子もよくきてたな。一番頻繁にきてたよ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3240
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_8c509319:

    # hi "But there were bad times, too. When my friends slowly stopped visiting, I began to realize how grave my situation was. It reminded me that this wasn't just a broken limb, but that I was now a different person than before."
    hi "でも辛いときもあった。友達がだんだん見舞いにこなくなって、自分がどんなに深刻な状況に置かれてるかを悟り始めたんだ。これはただの骨折とは違うんだ、自分が前とは違う人間になってしまったんだってな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3242
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_1938cd07:

    # hi "Even the times Iwanako would spend with me became torturous. By the end, we were reduced to silence, whereas before, she'd be talking constantly."
    hi "岩魚子と一緒にいる時間でさえ苦痛になってきた。それまでは岩魚子はずっと喋ってたのに、最後のほうには何も会話がなくなった"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3244
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_b86d509f:

    # "But that's how Iwanako always was. She may have been a fragile person, but she would talk constantly to try and hide that fact. Not about anything in particular, just… talk."
    "でも岩魚子はずっとそうだったんだと思う。か弱い人だったのかも知れないけど、それを隠すためにいつも何かをしゃべっていた。何をってわけじゃなくて、ただ……しゃべっていた。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3246
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_cd92cdd7:

    # hi "I think the three lowest points would have been when my parents told me I wouldn't be going to my old school any more, my birthday passing while in the hospital, and… when Iwanako left for the last time."
    hi "一番落ち込んだときを３つあげるとするなら、俺がもう前の学校には行けないって親に言われたときと、病院にいる間に誕生日を過ぎてしまったとき、それと……岩魚子が来なくなったときかな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3251
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_42e9c9c2:

    # "We leave the school buildings behind us as we begin to follow the main path through the gardens. There may have been the odd bystander in the school buildings, but outside, we're practically alone."
    "俺たちは校舎をあとにすると、中庭を抜ける道をたどり始める。校舎の中では他人もいたかもしれないけど、外に出ればもう俺たちは二人きりといっていい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3256
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_0d8731d0:

    # ha "What was your middle school like?"
    ha "中学校はどんなところだったの？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3258
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_97b45063:

    # hi "I liked it. I grew up in a really metropolitan area, and the middle school was nearby, so it was pretty crowded. I didn't mind it, probably because I'm used to being in crowds and around lots of other people."
    hi "楽しかったよ。本当に大きな都会で育ったんだけど、中学校は近所で、生徒も多くてぎゅうぎゅう詰めだった。でも全然気にならなかったな、雑踏や人に囲まれた生活に慣れてたからかな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3260
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_56b84836:

    # hi "I got good grades, and I played soccer with my friends. I spent a fair bit of time hanging out with them after school as well. Did get teased a bit over my hair, though."
    hi "成績はよかったし、友達とサッカーをやってた。放課後もかなり一緒に遊んでたな。髪のことでちょっとからかわれたりもしたけどね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3265
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9baa9c0a:

    # ha "Your hair?"
    ha "髪のこと？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3267
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_42ea8ae1:

    # "I grimace a little as I put a hand over my hair to cover it."
    "俺は少し顔をしかめながら、片手で髪を押さえる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3269
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_ffd2b217:

    # hi "I'd keep getting tufts and strands that refused to flatten or stay where I wanted them, and my mother wouldn't let me just get my hair shaved. It had a habit of popping out, no matter how much I tried to brush it down."
    hi "どうしても平らにならない髪の房があって、全然思い通りになってくれなくてさ。坊主にするのは母さんが許してくれないし。どんなにブラシでといても勝手に飛び出す癖毛だったんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3274
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_4ee7fd16:

    # ha "It still does, a little."
    ha "今もまだちょっとあるね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3276
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_23ff7c3d:

    # hi "I was worried I'd get that reply."
    hi "そう言われないかとびくびくしてたんだけどな"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3281
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_583f807a:

    # ha "S-sorry, I didn't mean to…!"
    ha "ご、ごめん、そんなつもりじゃ……！"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3283
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9bb86060:

    # "I give a mild laugh and wave it off."
    "俺はその発言をおだやかに一笑に付す。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3285
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9fd2e00f:

    # hi "It's fine, I know it still does."
    hi "大丈夫だよ。今でも直ってないのは知ってるしね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3287
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_cf798ee9:

    # "It feels strange to have someone act so interested in my past. If it were anyone else I'd think they were just acting polite, but that's something I really don't think Hanako would do. Or if she did, she'd do it so badly that it would be obvious."
    "俺の過去なんかにこんなに興味を持たれるというのは変な感じだ。これが華子じゃなかったらただの社交辞令だと考えるだろうけど、華子がそういうことをするとは思えない。 もし華子が実際にそうしたとしても、うまくいかずに見え見えのお世辞になるに違いない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3293
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_e38d5120:

    # "There are a number of girls in the common room on the ground floor, and Hanako presses herself to my side once more as we pass them. I expect her to break off, but instead she continues to cling onto me as we walk towards the stairway."
    "一階の共有スペースには何人か女の子がいて、そこを通り過ぎるときに華子はまた俺にしがみついてくる。俺はすぐに離れるだろうと思ったけど、廊下へ歩き出しても華子はくっついたままだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3297
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_f43cd7db:

    # "Something about the way she's holding onto me feels… different from the usual."
    "華子のしがみつき方はどこか……いつもと違う感じがする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3302
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9ef6b074:

    # "I'm left deep in thought as we walk up the stairs and down the hallway. It's only when we stop that I look up and realize that I've been following her without question."
    "俺は深く考え込んだまま、一緒に階段を上がり廊下を歩いて行く。やがて立ち止まってようやく、頭を上げて俺は自分が何の疑問もいだかずに華子のあとをついてきていたことに気づく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3304
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_4e2167c1:

    # hi "Why did we come to your dormitory room?"
    hi "なんで二人で華子の部屋まで来ちゃったんだろうな？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3309
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_613d6af4:

    # "She looks straight at the door, without so much as a glance in my direction."
    "華子はこちらをチラリとも見ようとせずに、ドアをまっすぐ見つめている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3311
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_eea78bab:

    # hi "Hanako?"
    hi "華子？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3316
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_7ec15538:

    # "She moves to answer, but stops herself."
    "華子はなにか答えようとして、やっぱりやめる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3323
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_58d24d44:

    # "Instead, she silently breaks from my side, opens her door, and steps inside."
    "代わりに、静かに俺の隣を離れてドアを開けると、中に足を踏み入れる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3325
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_59688595:

    # "I look up and down the hallway, a bit lost as to exactly what I should do. Shrugging, I decide to follow her since I don't have any reason to do otherwise."
    "俺はどうするべきかわからずに廊下を見渡す。やれやれと肩をすくめると、そうしない理由もないしそのまま華子についていくことにする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3331
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_b7205b07:

    # "Hanako stands in the middle of her room and looks straight at me. It's unnerving when she does this, as it's such an unusual action for her. I open my mouth to speak, but she preempts me."
    "華子は部屋の真ん中に立ってまっすぐ俺を見る。いつもとぜんぜん違う行動に、ドキドキしてしまう。何か喋ろうと口を開くけど、華子に先手を打たれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3333
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_82b46368:

    # ha "Could you… close and lock the door?"
    ha "ドア閉めて、鍵かけてもらっても……いいかな？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3335
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_775a2c72:

    # "Hanako's hand reaches for her chest, grabbing her blouse at her heart."
    "華子は自分の胸元に手を伸ばすと、ブラウスをぎゅっと掴む。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3346
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_9a4dcf9d:

    # "I turn and lock the door shut, then freeze."
    "俺は振り向いてドアを閉めると、そのまま固まってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3348
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_21f1e2e5:

    # "The atmosphere is beginning to feel quite strange. This feeling is only made more profound when I hear the curtains being pulled behind me."
    "変な雰囲気になりつつある。背後でカーテンの閉まる音が聞こえて、変な感じはさらに深まる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3350
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_17fe8550:

    # "It's going to be night soon. We're a guy, and a girl, in a bedroom. She's closing the curtains, and I'm shutting and locking the door. She can't… she can't really have that in mind… can she?"
    "もうすぐ夜になろうとしている。俺たちは男子と、女子とで、ここは寝室だ。華子はカーテンを閉めてて、俺はドアを閉めて鍵を掛けてる。いや、華子が……華子がそんなことを考えているはずが……ないだろ？"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3352
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_32b8f786:

    # "I gulp and turn around very, very slowly. Hanako is in the center of the room, but hasn't turned back to face me."
    "俺はゴクリと唾を飲み込むと、とても、とてもゆっくりと振り返る。華子は部屋の真ん中にいるけど、まだ俺のほうに向き直っていない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3357
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_baa5369d:

    # ha "You told me about your past, so I have to tell you mine."
    ha "久夫くんは昔のことを教えてくれたから、私も教えないといけないよね"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3359
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_f7658527:

    # "She takes a deep, shuddering breath, and pauses for a number of seconds. Her hands move to her ribbon and begin to tug, all but confirming my thoughts."
    "華子は深く震えながら息を吸って、そのまますこし固まる。華子の手が首元へ動くとリボンを引っ張り始めて、俺の考えが正しかったことがわかってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3361
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_7a60fef6:

    # hi "H-Hanako…"
    hi "は、華子……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3366
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d6678792:

    # ha "P-please… don't say anything."
    ha "お、お願い……何も言わないで"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3368
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d9a1902d:

    # "I obediently stay hushed as she slips off her ribbon and continues to unbutton her blouse, before working the clip on her bra. The process is slow. Perhaps it just feels slow because of what she's doing. I'm not sure."
    "俺が素直に黙っていると、華子はリボンをするすると外す。そのままブラウスのボタンを外して、次はブラジャーのホックをいじる。ゆっくりと外している。 いや、わからないけど、華子の行為のせいでゆっくりと感じられるだけなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3370
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_ab144115:

    # "Frozen to the spot, all I can do is watch as Hanako, hands trembling, unclips her skirt and lets it drop to the ground."
    "その場で凍りついたままの俺がただ見ていることしか出来ないなか、華子が震える手でホックを外したスカートが床に落ちる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3377
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_b588588e:

    # "Finally, she takes her blouse in her hands and draws it off, her bra falling from her shoulders. And so, Hanako stands in the middle of the room all but bared, save for her stockings and underwear."
    "そしてついに華子はブラウスを手に取って脱ぎ捨てる。華子の肩からブラジャーが落ちる。そうして部屋の真ん中には、ストッキングと下着以外何も身に着けていない華子が立っている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3379
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_0ff7858d:

    # ha "This is me. All… of me."
    ha "これが私。私の……すべて"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3386
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_310ddbe0:

    # "My eyes are immediately drawn to the scarring on her back. The skin on her right side is of a similar texture to that of her face, but it's also stretched taut and covering a much larger area. The scarring is by far the worst on the shoulder, buttock, and thigh."
    "俺の目はすぐさま背中のやけど跡に引き寄せられる。右側の肌は顔の肌の質感に近いけど、ピンと張り詰めていてはるかに大きな範囲にわたっている。肩とお尻と腿のやけどが一番ひどい。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3388
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_ed864f6a:

    # "Just as my heart attack redefined my life… this is the event that redefined Hanako's."
    "心臓発作が俺の人生を塗り替えたように……華子もこのやけどに人生を塗り替えられたんだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3390
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_51173d24:

    # "If I'd seen this when I first met her, I'd have been shocked. Not only at the sight, but also at the idea that something like this was survivable."
    "もし華子に最初に会った時にこの体を見ていたら、俺はショックを受けていただろう。驚くのは見た目だけじゃない。こんなやけどを負っても生き残れるのだということにもだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3392
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d86271e8:

    # "But after having had time to get used to the idea, and after seeing the scars on her face, hands and collar, my reaction is more measured. My reaction right now is not due to her scarring, but to her body."
    "だけどそのことに慣れるだけの時間もあったし、華子の顔や手や襟元のやけど跡を見てきたこともあって、俺の反応はもっと落ち着いたものだった。 その反応というのも、華子のやけど跡に対するものではなく、華子の肢体そのものに対するものだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3394
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_1c12c5cf:

    # ha "The fire happened when I was eight years old. It was night, and we were sleeping when it started."
    ha "火事があったのは８歳のとき。夜だった。私たちが寝てる時に出火したんだ"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3396
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_4fccdaf4:

    # "Hanako's voice trembles, the shaking of her blouse giving away the fact that her hands are doing just the same."
    "華子の声が震える。ブラウスの震えが、華子の手も同じように震えているんだということを教えてくれる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3398
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_ea087453:

    # ha "I… curled up into a ball… when the fire swept over me. My mother… tried to shield me. Th-that's the only reason… I lived…"
    ha "炎が……押し寄せてきて……体をぎゅっと丸めてた。お母さんが……私を守ろうとしてくれた。そ、そうじゃなかったら……今生きてないの……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3400
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_19548185:

    # "Hanako's eyes begin to moisten, her voice cracking under the combined pressure of exposing herself to me like this, and reliving those painful memories from so long ago."
    "華子の目が潤いはじめる。こんな風に自分をさらけ出すプレッシャーと、ずっと昔の痛ましい記憶を呼び起こすプレッシャーで声も震えている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3402
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_1f71bf0e:

    # "I want to say something, anything, to make her feel better. I can't, though. I feel completely useless when faced with a situation like this. She's forcing herself to come so close, yet it's at times like this that I feel most distant to her."
    "何か言いたい。何でもいいから、華子を慰められるようなことを。でもできない。こんな状況では自分が完全に役立たずになった気分になる。 華子が頑張って近づいてきてくれているのに、しかし華子との距離を一番感じてしまうのはこういう時だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3404
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_48390028:

    # ha "I'm sorry… for making you see this."
    ha "こ、こんなの見せて……ごめんね……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3406
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_d81a77bb:

    # "There's no point in denying the obvious. I think what I should say now, and what Hanako wants me to say now, is the truth. What I genuinely, honestly, believe."
    "明らかな事実を否定しても意味がない。俺が今言うべきことは、そして華子が今言って欲しいことは、嘘じゃなくて真実だと思う。俺が心から正直に、信じられることを。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3408
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_7232de8f:

    # hi "It doesn't matter. You're a wonderful person, Hanako. Your body doesn't change that."
    hi "関係ないよ。華子は素敵な人だ。体がどうだろうと変わらない"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3410
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_f52aaf0d:

    # "She looks at me for a long time, her breathing uneven as she tries to remain steady amidst the emotions we're both feeling. It feels less like she's looking at me than she's looking through me."
    "華子は俺をじっと見つめる。その息は不規則で、俺たちの共有する感情のなかで心の揺れを抑えようとしている。華子は俺を見ているというよりも、俺の向こうを見ているように感じられる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3412
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_099bcc62:

    # "I slowly walk towards her, and gently place my hands on her shoulders as she lets go of her blouse. She gasps a little; not in fright, but in simple startlement."
    "俺はゆっくりと華子に近づくと、その両肩をやさしくつかむ。華子は小さく息をのんで、ブラウスを手放してしまう。恐れではなく、単純な驚きで。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3414
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_655d4392:

    # "Being so close to her causes my mind to become a jumble of feelings. The scarring on her shoulder, plain to see and leather-like to the touch, conflicts strangely with her otherwise soft skin and silky dark hair."
    "華子のすぐそばにいたことで、俺のなかでは色んな気持ちがごちゃまぜになっている。肩のやけど跡がはっきりと見える。触ると革のような感じで、そこを除けばやわらかな肌や絹のような黒髪とは妙に対照的だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3416
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_3303df91:

    # "Hanako is a girl, with all that entails. She's taller than usual for a woman, but still has curves in all the right places. The nape of her neck, just visible thanks to her hair slung over her shoulder, is alluring."
    "華子は女の子で、女の子らしさもちゃんとある。女の子にしては背が高いけど、それでもあるべきところに女性らしい曲線がある。髪の毛が肩にかかっているおかげで見えるうなじは、とても魅力的だ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3418
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_e3334daa:

    # ha "I know… that I'm not pretty… like Lilly. I just… wanted you… to see me. The real me."
    ha "リリーみたいに……かわいくないのは……わかってる。私はただ……私を……見て欲しかったの。本当の私を"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3420
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_bb1befee:

    # hi "I've already seen the real you, though. You didn't need to take off your clothes for that."
    hi "でも、本当の華子ならもうこれまでに見てきたさ。服を脱ぐ必要なんてなかったのに"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3423
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_27005eb4:

    # "The following scene is disabled based on your accessibility options. By proceeding forward, you'll skip to the next day. "
    "次のシーンは、アクセシビリティ設定により無効になっています。先に進むと、次の日に進みます。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3441
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_168faa6e:

    # "Her lips are open, just a little. She lets out a sharp breath as, without thinking, I breathlessly lean forwards and press my lips to hers."
    "華子の唇が、ほんの少しだけ開く。華子がはっと息を漏らすと、考えるより先に、呼吸を忘れて身を乗り出し、俺はそのまま唇を合わせる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3443
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_78e18afb:

    # "The kiss only lasts for a fleeting moment before our faces part, our breathing quick and nervous. The feeling of Hanako's mouth lingers, and her eyes remain locked to mine."
    "キスはほんの一瞬のことで、俺たちはすぐに顔を離す。荒く、緊張した呼吸。俺の唇には華子の感触が残っている。華子の目は俺を見つめ続けたままだ。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3448
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_0c56b002:

    # "Trembling a little myself, I remove my tie and begin undoing the buttons of my shirt. Hanako remains standing where she is, looking at the ground in front of her rather than watching me undress."
    "俺は少し震えながらも、ネクタイを解いてシャツのボタンを外し始める。華子はその場に立ち尽くしたまま、俺が服を脱いでいるところを見ないように目の前の床を見つめている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3450
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_0fe51a73:

    # "On the one hand, I'm thankful for that. I've always been somewhat self-conscious of my body, but my scarring has made that quite a lot worse. On the other, though, this atmosphere feels very strange."
    "これはありがたいことだと思う。自分の体のことはいつも気恥ずかしく思っていたけど、胸の傷跡のせいでその羞恥心はひどく悪化してしまった。その一方で、この雰囲気はとても変な感じがする。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3455
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_3c5dee5d:

    # "My shirt falls to the floor in a heap, as untidy and crumpled as Hanako's blouse and skirt. Hanako's entire body visibly flinches at the sound of the zipper on my trousers being pulled down."
    "シャツがばさりと床に落ち、華子のブラウスやスカートと同じように乱雑なしわくちゃのかたまりに変わる。俺がズボンのチャックを下げる音に、華子の全身がビクリとするのが見える。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3457
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_6455a35d:

    # "My trousers join my shirt on Hanako's floor next to the bed, as do my socks in short measure. I hesitate before taking off my boxers, and end up leaving them on."
    "ベッドの隣の床でシャツにズボンが合流して、靴下もすぐに後を追う。俺はボクサーパンツを脱ごうかためらって、結局履いたままにしておく。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3459
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_e49730a3:

    # "They represent one last hurdle I don't think I can overcome quite yet. Sheer embarrassment stops me, along with not wanting Hanako getting even more worked up. My unease about the situation has also left me needing my own stimulation."
    "このパンツは、まだ乗り越えられそうにない最後のハードルだ。恥ずかしさだけでもそうだし、華子にこれ以上どぎまぎさせたくないというのもある。この状況への不安から、俺自身も刺激を必要としている。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3464
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_6f5dad09:

    # hi "Hanako…"
    hi "華子……"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3469
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_a96b0929:

    # "She gives a nod without so much as glancing at me, and makes her way to the bed as I do. She walks as if her legs were wooden sticks. I'd find it amusing if I weren't doing exactly the same thing."
    "華子はこちらを見ようともせずに、ただうなずく。そのまま俺たちはベッドに向かう。華子の歩き方は足が棒になったかのようにぎこちない。これで俺も同じ有様でさえなかったら、面白がることもできただろうに。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3471
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_db4534cf:

    # "I take the initiative, turning around and sitting on the side of the bed. I look to her face to invite her to take a seat either next to me or in front of me, but end up awkwardly looking down to stop myself from staring at her body."
    "俺は先手を取り、振り返ってベッドに腰掛ける。そのまま華子の顔を見つめ、俺の隣か前に座るように誘おうとするけど、結局華子の体を見るのを止めてぎこちなく視線を落としてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3476
translate jp a4_hanako_whispered_touch_fd4abdfa:

    # "Nevertheless, she takes her cue and reluctantly sits between my legs. As she does, a rush of sensations hits me all at once."
    "でもそれで意図が伝わったのか、華子はためらいながら俺の足の間に腰掛ける。華子が座ると、あらゆる感覚がいっせいに押し寄せてくる。"

# game/script-a4-hanako.rpy:3478
